Iilqayuneghllugutemneng whanga.
Meghnughnanighwaaghlunga, tenmaawingwaaghlunga.
Angtanghhamtestun igleghtaqelghiikut, enkaam meghnughnanighwaaghluta.
Enmis uteghmun aqfaatutaqluku quyngighput lliighaghput tughwaanemta, ivaghiyanemta.
