Puvallat
Puvallat tamaakut entaqun yugwem kitum sangwaa esghaghluku puvallangughtekayuguuq taawa puvallaliitkayuguuq, entaqun gift-tengaqelghiit yugwet taakut sameng nani.
Puvallaneghmeggni tawaten, elngaatall party-lghiistun katam ayuqut, amalka core-elget iwernga akulget.
Sangwaa tawaten aanghutelleghteng liisimakegkangat.
Pinigh atughaqaat puvallaneghmeggni.
Neqenghaghqeghllakayuguut.
Uzivniiqegkangitlu tapghaat whaten aghveghaqetakun petugluki.
Aghnat tuguluki yugwet paamken inglunganeng tunutngitnilluteng.
Dance-estun legan tawaten uzivngwaaghuteghllakayugwennguq nenglaghqiquteghllakayugwet.
Seghleq sangwaanguq puygaaqegkangat puvallami tawaten qerngughulluteng.
Allaaghiinaagughnguq puvalla tamaana, kitum yugwem pinga allangwaaqluni pattern-nga.
Saayat
Ilangita saayaaniiqegkangit puvallangit.
Saayat tamaakut taxidermistestun ulimaaghistun ayuqut.
Naqamnguq kana sagneghet, qayuutaghhaat neqmeng imighluki qukaani tawani kenghhwam saaghwani lliluteng.
Kiiwhken kiwa, nallukaqegkangit maakut ilangita anglinghhat, yugwet aqumluteng piighhameng entaqun amelengestaghhaghmeng ivalumeng paaggun pizitetgun piluki.
Qawaagemnguq amighqwaaghi, sangwaat entaqun alngunak qawaaget, iwhani esghaqateng taakut qawaaget akuqaqayugukangit.
Amighqwaaghennguq aftaneghmegteki seglluki kevighluki.
Kinenghata kevighluki unguvalghiistun legan whaten ulimaluki.
Nagun paamggun kakitaqiit qiipat.
Pikanguq qawaaget nalugluteng iteghaanneghmeggni esghaghaqiit.
Esghapagngaaghmegtekinguq qawaaget, yaquteng whaten saaglluki, neqmun kanavek piluteng, puvuglutenguq, aga quulvaghaghtaqut.
Teskigum esghapagsaqneghmini elngaatall, esgha party-estun ayuqelghiit puvallallghit.
Puvallannguq tamaakut seghleghitut quyanaghllaaguut, quyaqayuguteghllakayuguut.
Eghqwaaq
Eghqwaaghet maakut angyam piinlilleghqaani elngaatali nangllegsiisit, tungsighraasit elngaatall taakut.
Year round entaqun neqa sangwaa unakegkaghteng, part-sa taana saveekayugwat.
Angyaq piinlighyaghtunghani ateghqughluku, tunuq tamaana pugniighluku, kaapelqiluteng nunivagmeng, sangwaa akuutaqlu piluku.
Aghveghaqetam uvitangakun nekeghqughluki tawaten, alqimaghyukaghpenaki, saafsukaghpenaki naten itakeghllagluki.
Angyalgem nuliighhiinaan qepghaqayugwi akuusaghqat tamaakut.
Tanpeghmeng uligluki qavaghtekayuguut.
Unugwem qukanghani angyalgenkuk, sivuyagtenkuk nulighhallu taana ivaghullugwaqut ilagaghaqut.
Taaqneghmegni sivuyagtekullghiik aanlutek tuuniyaghtughaquk.
Taawa eghqwaaghaqut, eghwaaghluteng qayuutasquvegaghhaat sangwaat, sagnengestaq uglaapigtuq.
Eghqwaaghyaghtuneghmeggni tuuniyaghtughnaqniiqut.
Yearly catch-eyeng taana angyaghnaq pinaqenghani tungsighwaaneghmeggni entaqun taana tuunegkayugwaat.
Iqugwa amalka veghullghiistun amalka pikayugwaat.
Elngaatall tawani tungsiqayugwet.
Taawa uligiuki unaami aghhneghaniqun samavek esnamun enraq angyateng kelluki eghqwaaghaqelghiit.
Taakut elngaatall eghqwaaghutkegkateng taglaneghmeggni, taawa qaagken neghyaghtum neghaqegkangi.
Taawa qagavek enraq taana mingilatkayugwat angefqaghhaan tawaten qamaglluku taagken ikuulluki awalightughtaakayugwiit Tesqagegkut enraq temngi tugugpenaki awalinghisteng sangiighhaghmeng imiitaqluki.
Amalka naveghtevleghaghaqluki.
Kingulighpigaq qepghalleq nagatkaqegkegka whangkunni eghqwaaghaqngameng.
Tawani unugmi ivaghulluneghmeng Ugwetelen taaqluni aanluni tuuniyaghtughluni iteghluni, taawanguq pugneghatlu, kaapelqaatlu tuguvikumakangat Pingayuggaagunnguq tuguvikneghmeggteki.
Eskimo-t ugpeqeghllagluki ayuqegkangit, tughneghaannguq pingayuwhaghneng ighneghwaaqut.
Taawanguq iqugwaneng tugusimalghii tawaten tugutaataamalghii.
Kii alingyalghiimek, Wamiiyaq alingruughyalghiimi.
Tuqiinaqnginanghatanguq neqangitneng tesamanlluki tawaten tuguvikegkayugwii tughneghaam, taghnegham saam.
Alingruughllakaq, ellnga tuqukaaguq.
Entaqun alingeghllagem tuqutkaqaa.
Alingigasaqumeng entaqun passaaqnayalghiit.
Ugpeqeghllagem, respect-eghllagem taawa ipa aatestekayugwaa.
Taana esgha puygunghilkegka whaa.
Pingayuneng tughneghaat ighneghwaaqniiqegkangit.
Uyvasaghqa
Uyvasaghqa allaaghhiinaaguq.
Taana amenqun tapeeni qikmimeng pilghiit uyvasaghqengnguuq tamaana, tawaten aneghlleq qamaglluni aatgha alngunak.
Amalka alignalghiimllu kina kayagsaqumigu qinuyugtiilghiit, tusigaghluni sangameng tawaten aneghtutseng alignalghiikun liigiknaqluku, alignalghiim kayagsaqumiki apeghtughyaqumiki tawaten pisqelluki uyvasaghqennayalghiit.
Taana qikmiq tapemi Uuyghaankut iwhaningat.
Qikmit tamaakut ngiigaqiit qinuyugllagnun tamaakunun ngiigtesluki tuqutaqiit.
Naavghusaqaqiit.
Qikmiinaanghitut, sangughlluwhaghteng pivakeghllakaghteng taakut qinuyugwet naalghutesqeqaghlluki ngiigluki egtaqiit.
Suflugwaq sangwaa.
Uyvasaghqa tamaana allanguuq.
Uglaghtuq ateq.
Qani
Tamaakut ama suicide-ekat qaniniiqegkangit.
Suicide taana qaninguuq, yugtaanghilnguq yugtaq allakaghmetuq.
Tamaakunnguq qanikat seghlelleghpigaqii yugwem elngaatall, umyugwiitelleghpigaannguq qanikayuguut.
Qinuyuneghmeggni, kiyanguq yuuk pinilghii qaniperewaaq ellmeggneng tuqutaqut.
Naqamenraq liisimakistelighluteng tawaten entaqun nanevgaghtameggnun, nuyeklightameggnun akuzingwaaghluteng, explain-nengwaaghluteng, naallghusaghqaanghitelleteng liigikneghmeggni.
Taawa amenqun nem tunutangani uyghagllak irregular side-tawansalghii.
Neghqutmun uyghakniiqegkangat.
Neghqutemnguq naken tagitkaa entaqun ulapnguluni tawaten qaniviguluku.
Piyugmenguq taglaghaqut qaninaqelghiit tamaakut yugwennguq kiyang pinighikat iilqayugyugumaghllagtut.
Piiqegkangi Ugwetelem, “Tamaakunnguq pinighipigesnaghluteng qateghyiighaam umyugwaaneng umyugwalget ellmeggneng tuqutaqut naallghutelleghqaghteng iilqayukneghmegteggu.”
Taawanguq taglaghluteng uyghagnguq taana akitkelluku, ilanginguq legan guunneghmeggni, esghaghhunguq uyghak taana iilquvleghaghllaguyaghtuq.
Ilanginguq legan kenuqaghaqut ellmeggneng tuqutaqut.
Entaqun esghapagtelighluteng maliglluteng.
Entaqunllunguq ilangi piiqegkangi, naallghusaghqaghlluwhaat.
Naqamnguq ilangi tamaakut pinighikaanghilnguut umyugwaghtuqat neghqwaaghit ukiqluteng kemgim angtalanganeng, naavluteng.
Piniightaqiinguq naallghutaqut igleghsagutaqut.
Meregtemeng Tumet Sivuqamun
Tapiisagem Apellgha
Neghqunnguq taana akmaneghpalluq, aglaghnaqneghmeggni mangteghasqwaaghet sanguut entaqun naten angkaqaghllit, tanpeghhek tawaten.
Esgha mangteghasqwaaq iingunaan akmagumakanga maaken taamavek aglaneghmeggni Sivugnaghmun.
Ayakitaatet sangit, naten angkaan sakusimaat imani.
Esghaghhu atiiqusaghngaaghmeng, aghsaan tawaten.
Enkaangam Ayuqliq sangan ilughaqesteggu whangkuta sameng apalluqluku.
Nanevgaghtama taam angayuqama sakaat entaqun.
Tanemwhaqun Yaaghu Ugwaliitlu pikegkangat, taamengwha apalluqluku pimanghita.
Esghaghhu maaken amavek akmakayugumalghiit
Meregtemeng Piinlillgha
Entaqun tazingani aamnanguyaghtuq neghpigaa Meregta.
Tevlegham qulangani tazinga nenglut ayumightaneghqesiighet esghaghaqegkenka tamaa naghughtaqegkenka.
Aghveghem elqunevragi, angtughhaam elqunevrakumaaqegkangi esghaghhu.
Tawaten uyghagestun qaltetutkalighluteng lliiqat, ayumightaneghqesiighem entaqun angtalnganeng.
Kinkungaawat imani.
Esgha yulgem kenlenganeng ukavek tagisnaqegkegka.
Taawa tazingavek piiwaghluteng enraq Qayilleghnun.
Qayillghet ama nenglullullgaawaqut tamaa nenglurraaggaghmeng.
Naqam taamna Meregta neghllaak elngaatall uglapestaaghmeng.
Uglalghii nenga elngaatall yugwa.
Mengyalleq
Esghaghhu repall tawaten ayuqelghii.
Navek ugwavek qerngughfigllagmun, nenglughnagllak sangwaa qerngughfik.
Ayuqlit qarginguninayaqangat Taawavek uksaaghmi puvallayaghtuutkayugumalghiit.
Elngaatall puvallanghani yaywaalilek tamaa elngaatall ellnginaghhaghmeng kezemaghhaghmeng.
Nayughistekluku, kelengastekluku, taghnughhalghuteghllak taana.
Neghllagem taghnughhalghutni, taana aflengakistekluku, tawavek tagiqughllagluki.
Elngaatall taawavek piiwaghtuuteghllagluteng taana nayughistekluku.
Legan tanqighllugllak aliineghllugllak.
Siiqaataghtekayugwi qayughllaklu sanghata tawaten.
Puvalla kitum pinga taana efqughhneghminigu, atughlaataquneghminigu, kaa, leganqun.
Elngaatall sangwaa pinaqlaataghyalghiimi, taghnughhaat teghhwaaghiitkat.
Taakut elngaatall taghnughhalghuteghllak teghhwaaghiitut paayngunaqsalghiimi entaqun.
Mekelghiighhaq yuqeghraghtaghtuq saaq elngaatall, egtugyugtuq, ugmelliquq saaq.
Qenwatlu alla yuqeghsalghiimi, kii, kavighhalaak keneghllak uka unegken.
Entaqun paaynganeng kanakena mengyat esgha tawatesimalghiit.
“Seghleghhalek qenwatlu mengyaghnaqiinkutaa, heng elngaatall araghtek!”
Esghaghyaghtuneghminigu uka taglaq aliighinaq naken teskanaken paaynganeng.
“Seghleghhalekaa qenwatlu mengyaghnaqiisi, elngaatall pineghlliqitek, araghteki”
Alla piyalghiimi, whaa kaasaghtuumalghii legan keneghllak.
Tughneghaat keneghmeng atkugniiqegkangit Tughneghaq aamtayaghhaq allaaghhiinatun igleghnegha ayuqelghii.
Kii, alla piyalghiimi kana maallgumalghii.
“Seghleghhalekaa, taawa pinaqiisi, elngaatall araghtek!”
Piyalghiimi, iik sangwaa aanuq tesqamaken uka mayughtuq.
Elngaatall iitqaqiinaghluni, amenqun aglughat esghaqeput nenglulluk iikna ulimaaqngamegteggu.
Mekelghiighhaq tamaavek uughqaghlluni elngaatall tawanii, “Heng, elngaatall araghtek!”
Kii, piyalghiimi qakma saaygutgun elpekesaqsalghiimi, elpeksaqmegteggu, kii nenglu, nuna iggagtuq teskanavek, sunglugtuq amigmun.
Kii, supughraghyaqminigu, sayalghiimi aneghziigyalghiimi teskanavekaa iggagllagumaghmi.
Elngaatall pimegteggun taaggun, tatamaataatut, kakavniighutut, saluteng pilit leganqun estulaghaatut tesqamavek naaki.
Taghnughhaqsa palaghhaawa, qamakaghii.
Seghleghalek mekelghiiq alinguq.
Amen-a imgaghalghiini salghiini tughneghaat pineghmeggni entaqun kenghiqengegkayugulghiit.
Aga keneq mayughtuq, aga qenwat qaamaqluni, tawaten aneghlluni.
Nasiqulluku ukigluni agigsaghtughyalghiimi aga.
Pimakanga, “Maalliqun whanga piiqaghhnaaghyukaghpenga.”
Ii, aghuliiqaghlluni uutqaghtuq.
Tespikavek neminun maaten mayughaghtuq.
Elngaatall aneghpaghquyalghiimi allanqiggaghmeng iteghluni, ii peskugwaghtevzighaqluni, ifkavzighaqluni palaghhaghmeng sakun eltughluni.
Hiik, naghighluni aga igleghtuq.
Legan allanqiggaghmeng taawa piiqegkanga.
Saaq, nagneghtuq uteghninghituq.
Atghaghtuq Aqeftapagem taanʼgavek paaynganun.
Tawatetaqiinkutlu, naniqengyat sangwaatlu pikayuguut, naken meghmeng, quutmeng.
Kenengyaqayugwet sakayugwet, enkaam meq keneghmeng itakepiglluku ayuqsaqangat, nunaaghni whaten.
Tagilaghaateghllagluteng taghnughhateng piyaqmegteki, naannaaghtat, taakut angayuqiit puvallayaqat.
Elngaatallaa aghyuughmigaat saat, pegnem akuzisluku.
Qenwat pimakangi, “Elngaatallaa elpesillu araghtek, pineghlliqitek.
Tawaten piiqnaaghtusi ineghhnemsi, elpekqun naagpek, atagpek mengyaghlleqiinkuti!”
Yulqusighllaget anglikat angtaniitkat, sangwaa allaaghhiinaq tawaten ineghneghlliqut neghyukluku uteghhnaluki taghnughhateng, pingulghiit.
Wetku tawatenginaq piyaghqaanayukata.
Qineghsaghtughyalghiimi ii-uka.
“Heng, wata araghtegaa, qenwatlu taakwa piqaghhnaqiisi, legan tawaten pilleghmitun piqaghnaqiisi.”
Elngaatall, Meregtemiinguut tazimanirugllak Meregtem yugwa.
Entaqun nenglullugughtekam Dr. Bundi-nkut iiggaqluki lliiqiit.
Amum yugwi.
Yuksuwhaaghita qukaa waran entaqun.
Elngaatall kinkuk taakuk maalghuk taaggun amigem qulangakun guututelighlutek utaqaak, sameng imani guututkak.
Tawateghpigaq maaten pilleghtun, aneghziigaataneghmini legan teskanagun.
Iiwenllu estulaghaannaqluni lliighaquq, ii, uuhuukaaqaghluki samakangat, guusimakangat.
Pakregpagteghllagumalghii.
Aanziighllagyalghiimi sayalghiimi, mighyaghllagyalghiimi taghnughhaam akileghteghllagluku, qiyateghllaget.
Esgha sallghisimalghii taghnughhaq, sangwaa hour-mi sami tughneghaam aqsangani.
Maatnegha temperaturenga kayaasimaaq.
Kii, elngaatall uteghtestekataghllakiit taawa.
Ugwatmun Piinlilleq
Taakwavek tagiit, tagiit ii, kingunghit maaten esgha entaqun Ungalaankut, Nekregutenkut, Waamseghaatenkut, Yuungaaghaankut, kinkut taakut Meregtem yugwi Mangenankut.
Enraqluqun esghaghhu maavek lliighyaghluteng entaqun maantekestaghngaaghmeng taamagun nenglungllaamalghiit Meregtekun, nenglungiighhaq Mangenankut ulimaaghat Meregtemiingulghiit qayughllak.
Taamaken legan aglaghluteng sakmavek Sivuqamun siqlugwaghqumaaqelghii Aghnalqwaaq.
Legan sagneghek uyamiklukek whavek nemun tagipiglleghhiistun taaga aglaghaqelghii siqlugwaghqu amavek Meregtemun.
Taakwa Aghviqaghfiget esghaghhu Mangenankut tumangit.
Aghsughalghem kiwatangani taawa qenngumsak sangwaa Nangupagameng aatquq.
Enkaangam yugwi kinkut taakut Nangupagaghmiinguniiqegkangit Esghaghhu taawavek piiwaqestaangumalghiit, tagikestaq entaqun Sivuqamun whaa.
Nulam mingitekestaghyalghiimi Meregtem yugwa.
Taawa taakwagun tumetgun piiwalghiini Sanivleghet.
Sanivleghni taakwavek.
Aghsughaleq taana kitulghiini taakwegkut tumet taakwa.
Esghaghhu nekun tuumliluteng ayuqumaaqelghiit Taakwa nenglut, nenglungiighhaat ingangiighhaq uyghaget tamaakut minglengitni qulighneghitni.
Nenglulluwhaat kaataqanka maalghugwaaqluteng.
Tazinganiqaaghaq kitumi tawani ilangi taawa.
Sigasini tawani taawa ilangi.
Sanivleghet legan tumeghllalget, ayumiim Meregtem yugwita tumangit qellighllagluteng ugwavek.
Uyghagani tamaani uyghak nekeghqughaqluni tuumlingwaaghluni.
Taawavek esnevanemni whanga esghalqa aapghaqa, qayughllak yugtuyaghniluki ugpeqaqegkegka.
Taawavek piyalghiinga, teskigwken, taakwa nenglaaghaatat, nenglaaghaatat Ayvigteghmun tawavek.
Ayvigteghmi taawa elngaatall nenglut sangwaat.
Nenglutuftuq Ayvigteqlu taana.
Tespikani quulvani, sanivleghni taakwani, tazingani inglunganun aghvighaghlleghhiini paninang nenglut taawa.
Ngiigtekaankut
Ayakinkut tawani, Ayakim ungipamsugwani, Sikaghhaam ungipaani, aghqesaghtutuqat, satuqat eghqwaatuqat entaqun.
Ngiigtekaankut tawanniiqiit.
Ngiigtekameng aatqeftut nenglughllaget, elngaatall neghllak entaqun uglaghyagaghllaget.
Qilughaaghet legan siklaateghllagluteng ngiigsimakangit yugtuumaan.
Enkaangam aatqelghiit Ngiigtekameng.
Ngiigtekaankut atineghllugsigalkangit taakut ellngit Ugwaliit.
Meregtem nalighneqnaluki entaqun Iirgum esgha Qavalghaam eltuughaa ataasiq taana Ngiigtekaq.
Uyuqliq aghnaghaghllak taana.
Awalqam paniga Ngiigtekaq.
Esgha tawaten pikaamalghiit
Taagken aghvighluta sanivleghet kukragnaghqwaagii, entaqun qaayngakun aagumaaqut, lliighumaaqut.
Taawa iwernga ivgalghiini sanivleghiilluni.
Taawa nenglulluwhaq tawani Ayakinkuni, Sivugnaghmi.
Nenglu aangelqusiiguq.
Elngaatall taakut amaken Meregtemeng qaygeghlluteng amalka tumet qaayngitgun.
Taagken tanemwhaqa tesamaveklu ukigvilguuq, Sivugnaghmi tawani.
Entaqun nalighneghmeggnun sameggnun ukikaqayuguut Taana nenglulluk elngaatall, Qenaaghaankut kinkut nenglumun tawavek pikayugumalghiit.
Taagken enraq Sivugnaghmeng taakwa tumet ugwavek Akulkegnekun qaygeghtekayugwet tuumliluteng taam nenglullugwem yugwita tuumlillghi.
Nekeghqughwaaghluteng elngaatall ukavek Akulkegnun qavimun ukigluteng.
Taam nenglullugwem yugwan tuumlillghi.
Taakwavek Ayakinkunun, Neghqutenkunun, Qenaaghaankunun kaalluteng ayuqelghiit
Mayughwaaghmiit
Entaqun esgha 1600-mi nani nelikaamalghii maani.
Tagiyalghiimeng esgha Mayughaaghmi tespikani.
Uuknaqun mangteghat aagkut manungat housing-et, esnaayalghii entaqun.
Tapeghameng aatqelghii esgha.
Mayughaaghqun esgha taamaken tagit nelimalghiit.
Salghiimengllu esgha Ayveghyagteggun neliluteng ayuqelghiit taamaken tagikestam angtalanganeng.
Sivuqaq yungekestaghyalghiimi.
Entaqun kana qiighqami sami tawani Neghqutenkut.
Taghnughhaghmun Atighilleq Sivuqami
Iyaakankuk, Kepelgunkuk Apellghat
Kitum Atighaqaki Taghnughhaat
Taghnughhateng atighnaqneghmegteki sivukluki ateghqameng siivanlleteng aapluki, ateghqameng tuunkaaneng atighaqut.
Nalighmeng kitumeng taagken atighnaqniluki siivanlleteng ungipaataqiit, nallukesigatiit.
Ilangita aatghit ataasiiwaqut, ilangi naqam maalghugwaaqluteng, pingayugwaaqluteng.
Naten ilangi wata uglaghaqluteng.
Laluramkestun whaten ayuqenghilnguugut first name, last name-kunneghilnguugut, John Paul Henry Jones-etun tawaten.
Aatghet uglaghngiita kiyang ataasit aatghet atuqaqiit.
Katam Kaavam pillghatun igangllaqammni kitum taam aatghan legan nalikek atughqaq.
Ilangita ramkem taghnughhateng aanestegpenaki ateghqameng yataaghqutkayugwiit.
Sivuneghneng
Taagegken ima ellmeng sivuneghmeng aatghit atiitkayugwiit kingumun ukavek aviighutkat.
Enkaam puygungigalkangit sivuneteng kinkungutangi.
Taagani Sivuqam akuzillgha igaqnganghisaghngaan.
Wiin kiyaghlluki, unguvaluki atiiqigalkangit, entaqun taagegken ima qelghusaq.
Iwernga esgha aghnaghaam ighneni qantaghaqun atiimayaghtagu atami aatghaneng salin kiyaghlluku, atangan efququmangitkaa, piyukumangitkaa.
Naten Aatghet Aglaghaqat Ramkem Ilanganun
Kiyang yugwem, atam tunganganeng taghnughhaat allgenghata atiqayugukangit.
Iwernga nuliiteng ellngita pingitneng atiiqistekayugwit, akileghtuqayugukangit.
Tawaten esgha aatghet ramkem ilanganeng tagikayugwet, aglaqayugwet.
Aghnam ateq igleghutkayugwa.
Ugwiighluni tuquyaqan, ugwingan pingita atiiqsaghqaa.
Nalighmeng aghnam ellngan ramkengan atiiqsaghqaa.
Ilangi aatghem tawatengwaaq akuuraatulluteng ayuqaqut kinkut ramkengitni nalighmeng nani nunami.
Aatghet whani igaqelleghmi atuqegkat temnginguut.
Aatghukata akuuram pisleqii.
Nunameng, Nunaaghmun Atightulleq
Kiyang ramkem ilangan taghnughhateng atightughaqiit pennam, nunam, saam tekegham aatghaneng.
Katam “Quliqaq” taana nunalgem legan atiinnayaqanga.
Nalighmeng taghnughhaat tawani allgeghvigitneng atighnayaqangat nalighmeng aviighutfiganeng nunameng.
Taagken nalighmeng lliveghviganeng, qungughviganeng.
Aatghet Teghikusat, Qawaaget, Piitesighaat
Allaaghhiinaq ateq nagaqughaqegkefut, qawaagem aatgha, teghikusam aatgha saamllu piitesigham, atelek tamaakenllu uglaghtuq.
Akuzilleghmeng Atilleq
Kiyaghlluteng sameng pituqat.
Yuuk taana sameng pitukan, taana akuzillgha taghnughhaghmunnguq atiisaghngaaghmi.
Amalka yuuk, Mukaq, kiyaghlluni pituqaq, “Kguugg!”
Atiiqsaqmegteggu, taghnughhaq “Kguuggmeng” (“Kguugg”) atiighaat.
Samun Elqughaghutkamun Atilleq
Aghnaq aqsalek salleghmun elqughuskan legan taana atiisimaat, nalighmeng qavangulleq, esghaghwaalleq.
Amalka yugwem unaghsim qaayghunga makregsaqminigu, qaayghum asinganiteftuq yungllaqaghhaq.
Enkaam taana atiisimakanga “Makregtekaq”.
Allangughhnaluteng Atiiqilleq
Taagani agha, aghalighvik aviilluku, taghnughhangneghmeng aghtulghiit, natenneghatallu qinuyutunghata, qiyatunghata, alla atinqigtaqegkangit atelgughngiita allaneng.
Amalka taana, Tuumti, alla atiimakangat qiyatutanganeng, Seghleghmeng.
Meghmi Aviighutkat
Kiyang ayumighhaaneng meghmi yugwet peleghqegkat atiiqaqiit aghnaghhaaluki.
Aatghet Takestaaghsaqatlu Allatunllu Atiqat
Kiyang aatghet yeghrat taakeghllalghiit takelliluki ateliitkayugwiit.
Amalka Makimingaawen, taaksagulluku Makimeng tuqlughaatam qenwat ateliitaa taana ateq, Maki.
Taghnughhaatlu salin akuziyaaghtegpenateng atillghit ilangita ramkem nagneghtaqegkangit tawaten.
Katam Saapugha ateq.
Taghnughhaam atillgha “Puugwa,” ateliitkaa.
Naqamllu ayghiitaqegkangit.
Pingayaa
Ayumiim ungipaghaatangi
Ayngaghlingaawetenkuk, Qilakaghiilaankuk
Puughhutem Ungipaghaa
Ungipaghaninguq imani taakugnguq aghnaghaghhaak ilughaqutalghiik.
Kugwelestaghhiinaak, yaywaalingiighhaat.
Aatghik Ayngaghlingaawetenkuk, Qilakaghiilaankuk.
Ayngaghlingaawen taana natetalghii, nallaalghii, ighsanitaghalghi.
Ilughaghhaa Qilakaghiilaq nekeggmetalghii, aatkaqegtaq, pinitun kiyaghtaaq kakighllak quunpeng.
Taana Ayngaghlingaawen itghiighnaqeghllak, anʼgighnaqeghllak sagpenani.
Alla tawaten kakimaluku Qilakaghiilaq, kuuggʼghaa ughluvghwaangllaamalghii.
Iiwen taaqsaghtughluku ughsaghtuutkelluku qineghsaghtuumalghii, taana ughluvghwaaghhani napaghluku minglekun.
Aga aanumaan aghnaghaghhaam naten tekeni petgeghllaataquluku, tekivikluku ughluvghwaagha ayemkaamakanga.
Alingruughumalghii, iitqumi aghyuughnayukangatni, ughnegmi asinganun iighumakanga.
Iteghluni kuuggʼghaan ivaamakanga ughluveni, “Naagu ughluvghwaaqa whaansalghii navek pizigu?”
Amenam aghnaghaghhaam ivasighwaaghaa elnganllu.
Mekelghiighhaam sagiqulluku ivaghaa elngaatall.
Qenwat ughneggaa ikighaghluku piyaqminigu whaa ayemngwaaghluni.
Mekelghiighhaq nutaan qefliquq elngaatall pingigasalghii.
Nayaggani pimakanga, “Sangan aksaqsigu ayemlluku?”
Taagken ayemellghaneng yaakestaaghhaan anagumayaqanga, aghnaghaghhaq uniighmiqluni qiyaaghwaamalghii.
Nutaan kuuggʼghaan tawaten pikanga.
Aghnaghaq kagpagluni nengaamalghii aanluni navek taagavek aghulaqumalghii.
Tawaten igleghteghngaaghmi, iiwen aghtaghaghaqaa inga sangwaat iimneghem ilungani esghaghii.
Kaalluki piyaqminiki iimqaghneghem ilungani kamulugwalghun ukiqeghllakat.
Aqumluni aqeftaghaaghhani nusugluku amsighquughteghumakangi qamagtengngwaaghluki.
Taaqluki neghluni qavaamalghii saaghwitni.
Qavaghngaaghmi taghtughyalghiimi mevluugtet nagatii, piiqunnguq whaa, “Kii, aghnaghaghhaqsa una nanglegtapigta.
Elngaatall taghtughsaqunaan meghnaalili.”
Nepiighyata aqumyalghiimi aviitut, kaamgetlu taakut aviitut.
Taagken igleghllaataghtuq esghaghlaataghii sangwaat, enraq naayvam esnengani.
Piyaqminiki kii iqallulghun, aftallghilnguq qenwat asiliit uniighlluteng.
Aqumluni aftalaghteghumakangi agaghtaqluki qamagtengngwaaghluki.
Taaqluki neghluni qavaghlaataghtuq.
Tawaten mem taghtughtaqegkanga, piiqegkangat “Kii, aghnaghaghhaq una igamsiqanaghhalek nangllegtapigta.”
Nepiinghata aqumneghmini paaghqiilluni.
Aqumluni igleghllaataghtuq.
Mangteghat inga esghaghii, tazingavek aglaghtuq.
Kaalluni qineghsalghiimi aghnaghhaq qama nateghmi qepghiilugtaqeftuq elngaatall.
Aghnam esghaghluku upuutkaa, aaptaa, “Kaay, aghnaghaq uyuq naken pizin?”
Uniighyuglunga nemneng ukavek aghulaqunga.
Wasi kuuggʼghaghma saaghtaqaanga ughluvghwaaghmineng qivghuviklunga anagukanganga, tekemneng petgeghvikluku ayemsamkun.
Aghnam pii, “Aa, naqam tagi iitghi.”
Aghnaghaq iteghyan aghnam tunuq tuuna, “Ang, pugniighi elngaatall.
Iiggeten alqimaghyaqunaki, legan alqimaghtequfki pugneghen mekellilleqan.”
Aghnaghaq pugniightuq peghqiqaalghii legan kukriqenghituq.
Iiggeni alqimyukaghpenaki taaqaa.
Taagken taaqsagu aghnam pii, “Iingkunun aglaatigu, wataghllak qiinqiisqegkangaten qineghsaqunang pilghaaten.
Nateghmi utaqiilghaaten.
Legan kanaghluku aqupileghnaghqeghngaata wata qineghsaqunang.”
Awalighiiq sagneghpagek pugneghmeng ulevaghaghllukek.
Iteghyan qamaken aagraneng upughasaghaat legan iitghesqumaan, aghnaghaq legan ighsangwaaghtuq.
Kii, legannguq qama lengaatun sagneghek piyaqmegtekek.
Taaqlukek qama ketet ikighlluki piyaqminikek sagneghllagek sungaghmeng allaaghiinaghmeng imighllaglutek.
Aghnaghaam tugulukek aanuq.
Taagken itghusakek aghnam tuunlaataghaa enraq ivalulghutmeng.
“Ang, piighhiki nuvagsukaghpenaki qamaglluki.”
Aghnaghaq temngi kiyaghsugwigalnguq legan aqumluni talluluki piighhii nuvagsukaghpenaki taaqaa piighhaghrugllak.
Aghnam taaqsagu sagneghek sungaghllagmeng imalgek taakuk tuunaak, “Ang, taagken nuvaa.”
Aghnaghaq legan teghigniquq nuvughtuq, nuvughaa uyaqughhmik, qukaghutkaghqaq, qenleghwaaghqaq, tangyeghun, tukughun iwerngaqun sungaghllak qamagtaa qiipiighutegpenani.
Taaqsaki aghnam aatesqughwii ellnganun.
Aghnam pimakanga, “Allakaghhaghpek tesqamani ungavigni qavaghhaaten legan egtugyugpenang qavaghhaaten saam pinaanghitaaten.”
Aghnaghaq iteghluni qavaghtuq.
Qavaghngaaghmi elpekaghsalghiimi mengeghaallghiit llangaqanguq napit katelghaallghiit ama nagatii.
Piiqunnguq “Kii, sangwaa nangllegtaghllak ukavek kaasimaaq.
Legan kamelghuteput kiinghwaaghluteng amsighqughwaaghluteng, iqallulghuteput aftalaghwaaghluteng.”
Legan elpekaghlluni qavaghlaataghtuq.
Qavaamaluku aghnam teghtughtaa.
“Aghnaghaq aamyuq aqumingam, tagi ketfaa.”
Maketqaghlluni ungavigmineng aanyalghiimi aghnam yataaghqutngwaaghluku.
Legan aghnaghaq neqiinaghtuq.
Taaqsan aghnam pimakanga, “Enta yataaghqi atghaangam.
Aanegkuvek tamaana esghaqan alikegpenaan pinaaghan, legan atghaghhaaten negpenun qiivyaqunang qugwinayugngaaghpek uteghmun, legan avelghaqiinaghluki igleghlleghaaten.
Iwerngaqun legan kaasaghtuquvek anengaghhaan tuqlughwaghnaken.
Pinaken whaten, ‘taawa anguyagkameng tagitamken’.
Ugwikaghqaghpek takunaaghaaten alingegpenang atghaa.”
Taagken mengatun aanyalghiimi uvitmi tamaa kayngevaghqu ilangi qavaatet.
Legan atghaghtuq mengatun alingaghtegpenani.
Pama legan saam malighqaghaa tunutanganeng kavletun, siingaqluku.
Legan aghnam pillgha neqamikluku kakavegpenani atghaghtuq.
Qemimeng agiglluni kaasaghtughyami tuqlughaghaa anengani, “Taawa anguyagkameng elngaatall tagitamken.”
Kii, ukanguq yulghun ketanquteghllak ellnganun, panameng, pitegseghameng tugumiighluteng.
Uteghmun qiivyalghiimi uka kayngeghlagem malighqaghaqeftaa.
Kaalluteng pitegsaqmegteggu kayngeghllak tuqutaat.
Uullghaghlluni, kiinganeng yuuk nukalpigaq aanyalghiimi nangaghalqegllak, yuukegteghllak, iknaqeghllak.
Uka aghnaghaghmun tagiiq.
Taawa taananuftuq ugwikaghqaa.
Qilakaghiilaq ugwiiqaghtuq.
Yuuk neqengyughllak, aghvengyughllak tawani kiyaghtut kugweghmini.
Aga navek pinghata mughunneghata ilughaghhaan Ayngaghlingaawetem iteghvikaqegkanga.
Siqnighllak ellngallu ugwiighyugllak pinighllagmeng.
Aapqughwaaghaqegkanga naten naqamalla ugwiighumatanga.
Qenwat Qilakaghiilaam ungipamsugusimakanga, pimakanga, “Imatughngam ugwiillemtun ugwiighlleqsin ighsanitalghiiten.
Talwa kakingigalnguuten.
Waran piillghaghten amsighqigalketen.
Nalqigangilnguuten.”
Amenam aglaghluni, iitqiinaghluni anengaghhani qinuyugtaa ughluvghaanglliisqelluku, weni qinuyugtaa.
Qenwat anengaghhaan mengilegyagulluku amenam yataaghqutuq.
“Qinunaghhalek una, wasiin taana atama ulimaagha sallghilnguq salin.”
Pimsiighluku pegtaa.
Aghnaghaam qinuyugtaa enraq qineghsaghtiisqaa.
Qenwat aga aanuq.
Kingunganeng tekeni petgeghnaqutkaa petgeghsaneghminigu anaglluku qenwat iteghyaghtughtuq.
Upuupeng aghtughyamigu tuguluku ketngigluku ayemtaa enraqlu ayemlluku ughnellegaghmi asinganun iighaa.
Iighluku kakisighwaaghtuq.
Anengaghhaa iteghluni nemikun aqumuq.
Waakenghitaa ughluvengllaqani.
Qenwat Ayngaghlingaawetem pii, “Enta ughluvghen ivaghhu ukanillu ughnegma asingani.”
Mekelghiighhaam pii, “Tagivaghhu liisimakan.”
“Enta nekevluten ivaghhu.”
Qenwat nekevluni ivaghaa ughnellegaa ikighlluku tugwaa ayemluni.
“Una aghnaghaq.
Ayemmnaluku ulimatesqughwaaghsinga awii, sanguluku.”
Eggnaqsaghaa, aghnaghaam pii, “Enta qivghukigu, anagunga.”
“Sangan sapiglleghiistun ulimatesqughwaaghlunga ayemtan, enraqlu anagusqesin?”
“Legan anagunga.”
Qenwat mekelghiighhaam yaakestaaghhaan aagullughaa temngi.
Qiyaghllagtuq aqniimaghmi.
Kagparagkiighluni aga aanuq nengaghtuq.
Iitek piyaghaa kuuggʼghaan.
Aanluni taakwagun Qilakaghiilaam apellghakun igleghtuq.
Igleghteghngaaghmi kamelghun kaataa nunam iimqaghlleghani lliluteng aghipaghllaget, piigaqluteng, naatghighquutaqluteng.
Aqumluni esghapaggiinaq qinuyagutii.
Sivughtumsiighluki, amsighquvyiighluki taaqegpenaki pegtaqluki wata naafqii.
Naafqeghllagluki qavaghtuq.
Qavaghngaaghmi tawaten elpeksalghiimi mengeghaallghiit.
“Kii, aghnaghaghhaq una qepghallaagmetuq.
Ima kameput wata naafqumii.” Nepiighyata aqumyalghiimi paaghqiteftuq.
Aqumluni igleghtuq.
Inga sangwaat esghaghii, piyaqminiki iqallulghun aftamangilnguut ilangi asiliit uniighlluteng repall.
Kaalluni sivukluni uniightekameng neghughtaaguq.
Taaqluni aftavyiighluki qinuyagulluki mingughhuteghllagnaqngamiki taaqii.
Qavaamalghi.
Taghtughyalghiimi akuziteghllaget “Kii, aghnaghaq una nalqigangituq elngaatall naqam naangteghllagumii iqalluput.”
Nepiighyata aghnaghaq aqumyalghiimi paaghqiteftuq.
Igleghllaataghtuq.
Mangteghat aliighluki kaatii, kaalluni mangteghamun qineghsalghiimi aghnaq qama qepghaghaqeftuq nateghmi.
Aghnam esghaghluku pii, “Kay, aghnaghaq uyuq naken pizin? Kinanguzin?”
Aghnaghaam pii, “Ayngaghlingaawetnguunga, nengaagunga qayughllak kugweghma anaguleghyanga ukavek nengaghtunga.
Tekemneng ughluvgha ayemtekegka.”
“Naqam iteghluteng una tunuq kagimlluku pugniighhu.”
Amenam iitqiinaghluni tunuq kagimtaa.
Aghnam pii, “Iiggeten alqimaghyaqunaki pugneghen mekelliighaghllequq.”
Amenam kelengaaghsaghluni iiggeni alqimaqiinaghaqluki legan akuutaa.
Taaqsaqminigu pugnesqughhaq sagneghpagem qukaghhaani.
Aghnam pimakanga, “Aatak iingkunun awalighi.
Kepsuutngunaanghituq, legan iitquvek upughalleqaaten, iitghesqughwaaghlleqaaten aagranun.
Wataghllak avelghaqiinaghnaaghaten.
Wata talwa qineghsaqunang.
Legan pugneghen kanaghlluku utaqiilghaaten.”
Amenam aghnaghaam pugnellegani aglaataa.
Itghutaa legan aqupileghnaghhaghmeng upughasaqmegteggu, iitghesqaat waran qiinqiisqelluku.
Iitegiiguq pugneni kanaghlluku ighsamllegaghyaghtuq, enraq legan upughasaqmegteggu, waran qiinqiisqelluku.
Qenwat qiinghaghsalghiimi mamlegllak paaghqilnguq.
Naqam sivugwaghsalghiimi qama legan uglaghllaget Sagneghqek kavletun.
Maateqwaaqun whaa sagneghqek nuugtestagket.
Sungaghpak ataasighllak sagneghan qukaani.
Tagiluni iteghtuq.
Iteghyan aghnam tuuna ivalumeng, “Ang, piighhangllaa.
Nuvagsukaghpenaan mekegraghyukaghpenaan.”
Amenam Ayngaghlingaawen aqumluni talluluku ivaluni piighhaa nuvagraqaghaqluku.
Taaqsaqminigu piighhasqughhaq takelengestaghhaq.
Aghnam sagneghek tuunaak.
“Ang, nuvaa sungaghmeng.”
Tuguluku sungaghpak nuuvutaa qiipamikun ataasighllak.
Aghnam tuunaa ellnganun, pimakanga, “Taamani ayagyuni qavaghhaaten.
Legan alingegpenang, egtugyugpenang saam pinaanghitaaten.”
Aghnaghaq ivgaghluni qavaghtuq.
Qavaghngaaghmi tawaten akuzillghiit taghtughtaat.
Amanguq piiqut, “Kii sangwaa ukavek kaasimaa elngaatall nallekaghnilnguq, pikraghniilnguq, ighsanitalghii, nalqigangilnguq.
Amanguq aghnam piiqii, “Kaa kaa, ama qavaaguq.”
Tawaten qavaamaluku aghnam ama tuqlughaa, “Ayngaghlingaawen qakun taghtughnaqsin?
Aqumluten tagi.”
Aqumqaghlluni ivgaghyalghiimi aghnam yataaghqutngwaaghluku.
“Enta neghlutenngam aglaa negpenun.”
Taaqsan aghnam yataaghqelluku pimakanga, “Enta aanluteng aglaa negpenun.
Wataghllak alingegpenang aanegkuvek pilghaaten.
Legan aglaghhaaten uteghmun qiivyaqunang saam maligteghngaaten.
Siingeghngaaten avelghaqiinaghluku legan igleghlleghhaaten.”
Aanyalghiimi tamaa kayngeghllaguftuq elngaatall.
Esghaghluki tamaakut ilangi nekevghalghiit qugwinayukii elngaatall.
Enraq aghnam alingesnaniqanga.
Aghtughtuq nuqenneghmeng.
Alinguq, uuvganeng araamaghmi ketanqusnaq qimagtuq.
Legan kingunganeng uka saam malighqaghaa, qeteghqelluni anagniightuq.
Araghaataamaghmi legannguq taklaghmi tekinneghmini.
Aaghhwaaragkiighumaghmi nekefqaghlluni anagniighaqelghii.
Qemimeng agigaghteqaghsami, araghaataghllagumalghii.
Kugweni tuqlughwaghllagumaan elngaatall, “Taawa anguyagkaq.”
Ukanguq legan pitegseghalget yugwet, panalget ketanqusnaq ellnganun uka.
Uteghmun qiivneghmini uka kayngeghllagem malighqaghaqegkanga.
Yugwet kaalluku pitegtaat, aga tuquluni ulleghyan kiinganeng nanevgallegaghhaq aanuq.
Uka tagiiq Ayngaghlingaawetmun, kaasan tawateteghngaan atghaataa neminun, ugwikaa.
Ayngaghlingaawen ighsanitaghhaatmineng tawatetaghhaaghngaan nanevgallegaghhaghmeng ugwiightuq ima.
Tefaay naanguq.
Aliineghsiisiq Yagesgu
Aasam Ungipaghaa
Sangwaanguq taana aghnaq, wallu yuwhaawa, pimalghii, “Yeqaytuq aliineghsiqegka.”
Legan aklaaghtegpenani whaa aanqutiyalghiimi:
“Yagesguuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Yagesguuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Aapaa yagesgu, aapaa yagesgu,
Ghhughhughhiiya.”
Legannguq nepiightuq aliighyaqminigu.
Tawatennguq kiyaghsimaluku, nakennguq akuzighllaget nagaqughii.
Tamaani esghaquyalghiimi avangituq.
Pagavek esghaghyalghiimi, angyannguq paga.
Tespagavegnguq esghapagii elngaatall.
Imaninguq, “Sivuyagta uugyuq elqiighen ateghtigu.”
Llaaghannguq legan sivuyagtem elqiini aga ateghlluku, uka ukigtuq, ukigtuq, tuusan tazingavek takwaa.
Piyaqminigu pinighhalek.
Tuguluku legan taaggun aatesfigakun tallighmigumakanga.
Igleghllaataghtuq.
Iiwen uyavaghqaaghtuq, eslallugughteghllagumakanga.
Maatennguq aatkii kiinghwaaqaayalghiit, whaa eslallugughteghllagyaqminigu aghitqeghllagluni.
Legannguq taakwna suumqaataqegkanga aliineghsiisiq.
“Yagesguuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Yagesguuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Aapaa yagesgu, aapaa yagesgu,
Ghhughhughhiiya.”
Leganqunnguq aliighlaataghyaqminigu, aghvaghllugllak siqineghllugllak.
Legan aatkii kineghlaataghii.
Tawaten pilleghtun akuziteghllaget taakut ataasit angyat.
Pimakanga angyallightem, “Qukaghqughta uugyuq, elqiighen ateghtigu.”
Legan elqiini mataghlluku ifkaghliaataghaa.
Uka ukiglaataghtuq, ukiglaataghtuq, tazingagun tekillaataghtuq.
Tazingavek takwaa.
Piyaqminigu maateghniineng pinighataghaq, uuknanga qelmeghllak.
Legan tuguneghminiki aataqegkangi tallimikun.
Taawa igleghllaataghtuq, nemineng uyavaghllagtuq.
Legannguq palaghhaghmeng kiyaghtuq, eslalluk kaallaataghtuq, maateghniineng elngaatall yaagtughllak eslalluk.
Legannguq suumqaataqegkanga aliineghsiisiq,
“Yagesgiiuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Yagesguuuu, yagesgu, yagesgu.
Aapaayagesgu, aapaa yagesgu,
Ghhughhughhiya.”
Legannguq aliighaghllaataghyaqminigu siqineghluuk, maaten sivulighmeng aagken elngaatall siqineq uguqnaghataghaghluni.
Elngaatall kiinghwaaghii aatkii whaa legan.
Legannguq pilaataghtuq meraaghinaq naken.
Sivuyagtemnguq taagwum angyallighteni pii, “Angyallighta kiiwyuq elpeklu elqiighen ateghtigu.”
Angyallightemnguq pikestamikun taaggun ateghsimakanga, aga ifkaghtuq.
Aay, pinighataghatun uka ukigyalghiimi elqiiq.
Elngaatall utaqalaataghaa uukna ukilghii.
Uka ukigtuq, ukigtuq, tekisan tazingavek piyaqminigu, pinighataghaq elqiiq elngaatall.
Satuqaq qughalkutaghtuqaq elngaatall.
Pinighataghaq taakugneng maaten, legan tuguluku tallighmiglaataghaa.
Tallighmigluki sumeghtaghaghtuq, “Aglaghyaquma esgha nemnun.”
Legan taakut qerngiita tugumiiqluki aglaghtuq, aglaghtuq, aglaghtuq.
Entaqun unuk ataasiq atughluku, aallghani whanikumaan kaatuq neminun.
Eslallugughhnaniqaq, quunpeng aliiqaq elngaatall.
Allameng eslallugughtegpenani neminun kaatkaq.
Aneghrengighllak elqiighneng.
Tefaay!
Iiyaghhiinalek
Elqiilaam Apellgha
Ungipaghaninguq imani, mekelghiighhaankugnguq taakuk nengyuqutalghiik nenglumi kiyaghtaaghek.
Mekelghiighhaq aanigalnguq saluni aanli aatkiilnguq.
Quunpenguq aghnelqusiq atkuwhani aalluku maghuyuglluni kiyaghtaaghaqelghii.
Maghuyugtaaghneng sivuggneghmini iiyani taananguq aghulalluku taawa almesimitun nekegtaqelghii tawaten.
Quunpeng tawaten kiyaghtaaq elngaatall.
Sangan naqam iiyani qelpeghtaqagu.
Allanguq tawaten, umiilelguunnguq, maalghuk umiilgegket Aallgha aklungilnguq, aallgha akluumalghii.
Angyaghuunnaqennguq upenghami, ellngallu mekelghiighhaq qakiqniqumalghii.
Qaywanguq nengyughhaan ighleksaghaa, “Sameng aalluten angyaghnaqsin?”
Mekelghiighhaam pimakanga nengyuni, “Aatkaghten tagivaghqi aannaqanka.”
Legannguq nengyughhaghmi aatkaghhii aalluki mengakun taaggun aanumalghii.
Tawavek iquklighpigaghnun esnevaamalghii, yaywaalingiighhaq, “Ukughsi angyanga qaa?”
“Weninguq angyaghllequten nenglum yugkwaagha uyuq.”
Siinglukunguq aganguq ketaqut
Tuunglighhitnun tawavek, “Ukughsi angyanga qaa?
Enkaam qaa iguyaanga.”
Weniqrugnguq angyaghllequten aghnalqwaaghem aatkaaneng aatkalek.
Legannguq aga unitaqaat
Umiilegllagmun tawavek kaasimalghii, aklungilngughmun.
Kaalluninguq pii, “Ukughsi angyanga qaa, enkaam qaa iguyaanga!”
Legannguq yugwem taawa pii, “I-ii sivuyagtekaghqaghlluwhaq!
Elpek aghnalqwaaghem aatkaaneng aalluten qallevagluten weninguq sivuyagtekelleqamken.”
Legan miluusaqminigunguq kelutmun.
Mekelghiighhaq qiyamalghii.
Taakwna angyaq tawaten qamagtaa.
Iwerngaqun iquklighpigaat tazinga, umiilgem aallgha aghnaghaperugwaaghmeng panikelghii.
Aghnaghaperugwaaghmeng yukluni ketaqelghii.
Tawavek kaalluni pimakangi, “Ukughsi angyanga qaa, enkaam qaa iguyaanga?”
“Legan angyaghnaqelghiiten.
Taawa yuknaqamken, sivuyagteknaqamken.”
Ketiiqut qaakluku, aghvengyiiteghllak.
Taana aklungilnguq aghvengyughlak.
Iiwennguq ketfaghqaaghaqut kaay, aghveghem puugyaqminikinguq legan tuunluni.
Legan yaywaalingiighhaam aghveqsaqminigunguq tuqunneqegsaghluku.
Aawallunguq taana aghvengyiiteghllak umiilek aghvengaghtuq.
Ii, angyam qetgeghusimakangi elngaatall.
Iiwennguq kaalguutat apeghiighaqiit legan paagkennguq anuqa atghaghsalghiimi uka legan eftutun, kii anuqlighllagyaqminigu.
“Aa, sangulukumi taana yukllaataamazigu.
Leganqunqun tuqulaghannaqukut whaa meghmi seghleghmi.”
Avelghaqiinaghluku legan analghuvagteggun tugulaghalluni angyaq.
Paagken anuqlighllagyaqminigu legan elngaatall pikayuwhaq sakayuwhaq tamaana naghpaghsiqayuwhaq qamaggutuq, aghtughaat
Mekelghiighhaghnguq taana maamtawha piiq, “Ilengtuq ima.”
Naliita nagaquqaghlaataghluku.
“Aa, uumnguq piligu, uumnguq piligu!”
Taamnguq aklungilnguum piiqegkanga, “Aa, piligu ellnganpilleqaa whaa amsanaghtesleqaa pikayugwaaghhaat maakut mataawitaat.”
Mekelghiighhaq qepuughyalghiiminguq.
Qalivlugwaghhaghqek nengyughhaghmi atuqlukek.
Qepuughwaaghluni tayeghqaghluninguq ayapghaataghhaak aallukek aanqutimalghii tallighhaani quulmun ayuqluku aghulasimaan,
“A-nuq-li-ii, na-nge-llu-gu-ngu,
Si-la-mi-ngi, u-ki-i-nange-llu-gu-ngu,
A-i-ya-i-ya-nga, ya-i-ya-i-yi-ya, i-ya-iyi-ya-nga,
Silamit ukinaghningit aghnit payugha,
Uq-ugh-taq, uq-ugh-taq.”
Meq paatgumakanga inglunganeng -- “Uqughtaq!” -- maalghugegneng.
Maateqwaaqunnguq legan kaay qilaga kaagkaa piiknanguq ukitaghlluku legan ukigteghiiyaqminigu.
Aay, amsanaghqwaaluni naagunguq maaten anuqllighllak.
Qateghllugllagnguq taglaamalghiit aghvengluteng taakut.
Taam umiilgem taana umiilek aklungilnguq piiqaa, “Qayugham esghaghhu yaywaalit esghapagtelegllaget Yaywaalimllu aghnalqwaaghem aatkaaneng aatkalgem yakuqaa.”
Taananguq qallemsuwhaq qemall umiilek.
Taawa taglaamalghiit elngaatall aghvengluteng.
Impisigalkanga yugwem taam aghvenguqam, avelghaqumtaaghan impisigalkanga qamagtengngwaaghluku impiquumakanga.
Apeghiighlutenguq taana nengyughhaa ighsangakun nenglungiighhaq ifkaghlluku atghaalluku taana mekelghiiq aatkangllaghyaqmegteggunguq mekelghiiq pinighhalek.
Taana uyuqliq panini aga nulighqestengnginaamaan.
Taawanguq aghvengyughighllagtuq taana aghvengyiitepaaghruk yuuk.
Mekelghiiperewaaghmeng avaqutalighluni.
Taawa naanguq.
Meteghllugllagenkuk Anipaghllagenkuk
Iteghyaghaam Anagutaghmun Neghighluku Apellgha
Ungipaghaninguq imani meteghllugwet, anipat qateperewaaghuyalghiit.
Anipankuk meteghllugwenkuk piniqutepigsalghiik, quunpeng qerngaghmetaqelghiik.
Tawaten kiyaghteghngaagmek anipam meteghlluk pimakanga, “Yeqay igaqraghwaaghuteltung, pinighnaghsaateltung.”
“A-aa!” meteghllugllagem angghaghsimakanga.
“Elpek sivuklaken.”
Anipaghruk aangghumalghii.
Igaasitaq ketfaamakangak silugkaaghhaghmengllu.
Igaasitaq taana nanim ellngaatanganeng, qulmesiitem puyaaneng akuutkameng imalek tagnepiglleghhiimeng.
Anipaghllagnguq aghuliighwaaghluni igaghtesimalghii, repalnguq qavaamalghii.
Meteghllugllagemnguq pinighsapiglluku elngaatall igaqraamakanga.
Taaqluku taghtughsimakanga.
Anipaghrugwem taghneghani meghaaghhaghmi esghaghyaqminigu imaninguq pinightuq.
Taagkennguq ima anipat igaghrakguughtekaaftut.
Anipam meteghlluk pimakanga “Heng, elpegngam.”
“A-aa”, meteghlluk angghumalghii.
Anipam siluk igaasitamun nepluku meteghlluk agtuqaamayaqanga aganguq nalukaatuq qalghiqaamaghmi, “Qung!”
Anipam pimakanga, “Uuk, aghuliiluten seghletun pislequteni” Amawhanguq agtuqanghatni tamaani naluumsituq qalghiimaghmi, “Qung, qung, qung!”
Anipaghllagemnguq piiqaa, “Aghuliilluten qenwat naafqestan igaqralqa!”
Taawanguq meteghllugllak qapragllak qalghiqaqumaghmi nalughqutaghllak tamaani.
Qenwatlunguq anipaghlagem ugumiyagulluku igaasitamineng meteghllugllak kuuveghllagumakanga.
Aganguq qalghighrugumaghmi tengqaghtuq, “Qghwaaq, qghwaaq, qghwaaq!”
Taagkennguq ima meteghllugwet tagneghtekaaftut.
Enkaamnguq allamengllu ilakunnaniimaftunnguq.
Ivisangiighhaq
Wamiiyaam Ungipaghaa
Ungipaghaninguq imani.
Neminguq tawani, quunpenguq angyaghuutaqelghiit, neqengllaataqelghiit.
Taawanguq tamaanteftuq nemi tamaani yuuk ataasiq ighneghilnguq.
Taawanguq nulighha, panikluku ataasiq.
Angyaghuuteghllanghatanguq yugwisagaqelghii qayughllak ighneghilnguq.
Nuliinillu, panigganillu yuklukek angyaghaqelghii.
Ketaqelghiit paniggani taghtuqaghhneghani.
Kingulighpigaghhaaluteng kelluteng, aga angyat uplegutaqelghiit nunavagmeng elngaatall, ukanguq tagilaghaanneghata, taawa ellngit aglat.
Ayveghallghitanguq siipneghqwaaghhiitneng saghnaaqelghiit ellngit.
Iwernganguq tawaten neqengevleghaghaqelghiit.
Enkaangamnguq uteghnighaqelghiit unugtaaghllanghani.
Pegnemnguq neqeteregaghaqelghiit.
Ataasimenguq aghneghmi, nunavagpaghqughllagnguq nani imani, aruughyaghluteng esghaghluku uplegunneqegsaallaataghaat.
Leganqunnguq-aa, atghaghteghurragkiighusalghiimeng, ellnginnguq kingulighpigaghhaalaataghtut.
Iwernganguq tawateteghngaan paniggani taghtuqaghsan, naqamllunguq taghtughsugwigalkanga, atghaghteghluteng ellngitlunguq ketut.
Tawatennguq amsanaghllugllak, qutanguq qantaghanlluku wiin nallangighnaqaqegkangi teghiget, angyat saamkut anuqliitqaghtekangatni quta qantaghantesqeluku.
Sakan, tagitugughuskangatni quta qantaghantesqelluku.
Taagkennguq tawatennguq-aa, amsanaghllugllak-aa, quta paga qantaghanlluku, aagkulghutet upleguuteghllaget uyavaghllakat nallangitnun igleghteregaamaluku, sameng nagaquusimalghiit
Taagkennguq yugwemnguq taam pii, “Kaa-kaa, yaavuquneghmeng uyuq aghnaghaq taaqaghten, kaa-kaa nagataghtek sangaawa?”
Yaavuquutni qaakluki nasiighluteng nagasalghiimeng, sangwaanguq.
“Unegkughsii, nengaakitengngaa, qaakitengngaa,” legannguq nagaqughaat.
Sunanguq yugwem aquutani qiiftagu kelutmun.
Aghnam taam nulighhan qiifqaghlluku pimakanga, “Sanguluku pinaqlaataghsigu amyughaaghwaaqsaaghtuq.”
Avelghaqiinaghlukunguq kelutmunnguq piluteng, quutmun tenpelluteng, kayagsimakanga, “Enta esghaghyaghtuqaghhu sangaawa uuglluten,” nuliini pimakanga.
Nulighhanguq uuglluni, tawavek pengugneghwaaghanun qaasqam, yugsughwamalghii.
Yugsughwaluni pimakanga, “Paaghqituq.”
Uuggnaqsaghtughnguq angyamun, nakennguq pilaataghaa, “Whaantunga, whaantunga!” qaghingiteghllak.
Taakwavegnguq yugsughwaaghaghtaatut, ivaghiragkiighutut.
“Whaantunga meghzeghaaghhaghmi.”
“Aatak meghhaq tazigna esghaghyaghtuqaghhu.”
Aganguq aghnaq aglaghluni, meghaaghmunnguq piyalghiimi, avangituq, iwerngaqunnguq taawa ivisangiighhaq.
Taagken pimakanga, “Sangituq, avangituq iwerngaqun ivisangiighhaq taawa.”
“Seghleghhaghmeng, taana naqam qaakelteggu.”
Aghnaghaghnguq saaq agniqsuugtuq, “Kimaawighllagtukut.”
Aghnamnguq tugulukunguq qugwaklaaghpenaan, angyam aqumvigakun aqnighhnaqepiglluku miluutaa, mesaaqguulluku.
Taagken tawaten pugleghluteng igleghsimalghiit.
Igleghsimalukinguq.
“Nuliing, nuliing, angyam meghaaghhanun kanaghtaghtinga.”
Avelghaqiinaamakanga.
Iwernganguq atangan nagaqughluku pimakanga, “Aa, seghleghhalek sameng taana piiqa weni, piighesnaghaqluku piightigu.
Sameng piiqa?”
“Esghaghhu angyam meghaaghanun kanaghtesqelluni pilghii.”
“Kanaghtigu.”
Tugulukunguq miluutaa angyam meghzeghaaghanun.
Taagkenaa, imaninguq meghmelluni kana enraq.
“Nuliing, nuliing, yaavuquuteten taakut qaakiki.” Avelghaqiinaghlukunguq aghnaghaam ugumiyagutepigtekanga.
Imaninguq, “Nuliing, nuliing, yaavuquuteten taakut qaakiki.”
Avelghaqiinaghyaghluku atangan aghyuughlaataghaa.
Aga yaavuquutegni agniqepiglluni qaakumakek unaknaqepiglluku taana ivisangiighhaq.
Legannguq qaakii, suqsughhalegnguq, suqsughhalek, tawatennguq piyalghiimeng sukerakestaghaqeftut.
Legannguq yuuk nangllaghqelluni, aghnaghaqlu, aghnaqlu nangllaghqelluteng elngaatall, upumyeghaamaghmeng, quyaghllagumaghmenguq.
Sukeraghllagyalghiimenguq, legannguq angyalghun kaatqaghiluki naghughaghtaqiit.
Teghigmun kaalluteng, ayveghaleghtaaghllagluteng taglaamalukinguq, taawanguq angyalghun taagna upleguta taagavek igleghtaq.
Legannguq nangllaghqulluteng naghughaghhneghata esghapaneghmegteki.
Saghiighayugllaget, allaaghlluwhaghyugllaget, “Aagkut sukatepigtat!”
Imanguq yuuk tahna ighneghitalghii unangyuughqwaaghllagaa, aklungighighllagtuq, ayvengyuughqwaaghllagaa.
Quunpenguq ivisangiighhaq taana aflengakaqegkangat.
Tefaay!
Sikughaaghenkut, Kaviighhaankut, Meteghllugllagenkut 
Iyaakam Apellgha 
Uksuum neqangisagani, Kaviighhaq pirughsaghtuumalghii Sikughaaghet umiilgitnun.
Akmagtaghhani akmakluku igleghsimalghii.
Kaasalghiimi Sikughaaghet umiilgita nenglunganun, imani saaygungan amiga kagpestaaghhaaguq.
Kaviighhaq nenglaghyugumaghmi sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Sikughwaaghet umiilgat qaamna uaten eslegkakaa.” 
Akmagtaghhani mataghlluku pegnem kangsughngaan amigkun ilutmun kanaghsimakanga.
Aatkani mataghtaqluki kanaghquusimakangi.
Taagken iitghumalghii kangsughngaaghmi.
Iteghluni saaygut ilungitni ilepghaaghegni aasimakek.
Atkunillu, temkaagnillu agaghsimakangi.
Taaqluni aagranun iitghumalghii.
Sikughaaghet umiilgannguq pika kelutangani aqumluni, qenngulliqeghllagluni.
Imaninguq amestaaghhaaguq.
Tamaanguq sikughaaghet aghnaghiit qepghaateghllaget, qapraguteghllaget naqam qaalkaghpenateng.
Upughataghhneghitaannguq Kaviighhaq.
Kaviighhaq qaalkaghpenani alingesighwaaghumalghii.
Sikughaaghet umiilgat qiighumalghii, “Ughhu-ghhuu.”
Kaviighhaq upusighwaaghumalghii tupagpagsimaghmi.
Umiilek aga aanuq sameng piightegpenani.
Taawa Kaviighhaq tawantuq nalighhiiniita aleghquqaghpenaan.
Maateqwaaqun Sikughaaghet umiilgat iteghyalghiimi, Kaviighhaam atkugwa atuqluku, nuqutulkeghllagluku.
Kaviighhaq nenglaghyugllaghngaaghmi pegnem nuqesimalghii elngaatall.
Umiilek qiighwlaataamalghii, “Ughhu-ghhuu.”
Kaviighhaq tupagpagtesighwaaghaqelghii.
Umiilek nutaan akuziiq, “Aqelqaq, qayuq ggaatfaka?” 
Kaviighhaq nenglaghyugllaghngaaghmi pimakanga qusevegtepiglluni, “Uuk, sangantuq-aa atkuwhaqa aallaataghsigu, keluwhii avleghruuggnaluki.”
Umiilegnguq temsiyaaghaghtuq, aga aanuq.
Alla iteghyalghiimi enraq Kaviighhaam temkakek atuqlukek, nuqutulkeghllaglukek.
Sikughaaghhaq qiighwllaglaataghtuq, “Ughhu-ghhuu.”
Pilaataghtuq, “Aqelqaq, qayuq ighuvagegka?” 
Kaviighhaam pilaataghaa meni alingesugninnaqepiglluku, “Uuk-aa, sangantuq qulliggaagka aallaataghsikek keluwhii sevuutesqelluki.”
Umiilek aga aanlaataghtuq iqemyaaghaamaghmi.
Alla iteghyalghiimi iqlighmi, pinighhalek elngaatall.
“Aghnaghaat, aqelqaq upughateggu, neqlightughteggu!”
Umiilgem kayagtii.
Nutaan upughataat Kaviighhaq.
Neqmeng allaaghiinaghmeng ketfaataat.
Kaviighhaankuk umiilgenkuk neghtuk.
Neghutkelluku umiilgem aaptaa, “Saam ukagun-aa aagtestaten?” 
Kaviighhaam pii, “Avaqutaghhaanka neghesqelluki neqellgaanayukavek enankin, aagvikamken.” 
Umiilgem araghii, “Aghnaghaat, yataaghqunnakesi pirughtiisaghqameng.”
Taagken Kaviighhaq pii, “Qavaghluten unaami wetku aglaghhaaten, pirughtilleqaaten.” 
Unaami Kaviighhaq piyalghiimi akmagtaghhaa allaaghhiinaghmeng neqmeng imighluni.
Akmagtani aanestaa.
Ellngallu Kaviighhaq aanuq, kangsunghituq.
Kaalluni iiwenllu akmagtani mataghtaqaa, Meteghllugllak whaa tagiiq.
Kaviighhaq pii Meteghllugllagem, “Kii, naqamalla naken neqesiighsin.” 
Kaviighhaam pii, “Sikughaaghet umiilgitnun pirughsaghtughlunga, llaaghanwha taawa.”
Meteghllugllak imani, “Aa, whangallu unaami pirughsaghtuqaghllequnga.”
Kaviighham pii, “Ii-ii pigpengang, qayngunwhaa igiiterugnaanghituten.
Whaken tuunelleqamken.” 
Imaninguq Meteghllugllak, “Aa, tunusat kemniitut.” 
Unaami Meteghllugllak akmagtaghpagllani akmakluku sikughaaghenkunun piiq.
Kaasalghlimi imaninguq amigat kagpestaaghhaaguq.
Meteghllugllak pimalghii, “Aa, natenllaam qaamna umiilek eslegkakaa?”
Amigem paaynga naafqelluku, nuqutughlluku iitghumalghii.
Nateghqun atkuni, temkaagnillu mataghlluki, agaghlluki iitghumalghii aagranun.
Iteghyalghiimi sikughaaghet umiilgat pika kelutangani aqumlunl, imani amestaaghhaaguq, naqam qenngughllaga, nulglighllagluni.
Upughataghhneghitaat.
Qaalkaghpenateng naqam tamaa ilangl qapraguteghllaget.
Sameng piightegpenaan Meteghllugllak, umiilek aga aanuq.
Meteghllugllak sumeghtaghaghtuq, “Aliknaanghitanka, akmagtaqa whangamneng imighlleqaqa.” 
Umiilek iteghyalghiimi Meteghllugwem atkugwa atuqluku, angelkeghllagluku, nuqutulkeghllagluku.
Meteghllugwem esghaghluku, nenglaghllagumalghii, elngaatall tuqutngwaaghumalghii.
Umiilgem pii, “Aqelqaq, qayuq ggaatfaka?” 
Meteghllugwem kiimsighaa, “Aa-ha-ha-haa, sangantuq-aa akugllaka aallaataghsigu.
Llangaqa atkuka, nemni inga pellugutaaghmeng nuuvegkaq.
Aa-ha-ha-haa.” 
“Uguminaqruwhaghmeng!” pimaghmi aanuq umiilek.
Alla iteghyalghiimi, Meteghllugwem temkakek atuqlukek.
Legan Meteghllugwem esghaneghminigu tuqutngwaaghaqelghii.
Umiilgem pilaataghaa, “Aqelqaq, qayuq ighuvagegka?”
Meteghlugwem pii, “Aa-ha-ha-haa, sangan qulligegka aallaataghsikek?
Llangaqa qulligegka nemni inga nguulghutmeng nuuvegkak!”
Umiilek eggmillghamaghmi aga aanuq.
Iteghyalghiimi gginaq seghleq, qenngughnaggaa.
Aleghquutaghtegpenateng ingaghquutut.
Meteghllugllak ingaghlluni qavaghtuq.
Qavaghngaaghmi isekinam, suqsum teghtughaghsalghiimi, qungyaghagneng eslatmun saayguneng maaqutaqeftaa.
Meghqun nalugwigalnguq, alingruughtuq.
Sanitmun patimllaluni quutmun uugtuq.
Kaamngunani, atkungunani, ilepghaaqiinaghluni aghipaghllak aglaghtuq neminun.
Kaviighhaq taawa manughami aqumgaaqeftuq.
Kaviighhaam pii, “Kii-ii, qayugham sikughaaghet umiilgita pirughtitaaten?” 
Meteghllugwem pii, “Sikughaaghet umiilgat inglungunghituq.” 
Kaviighhaam pii, “Qayngunqun igiiterugumangillaataghtuten!” 
Tefaay.
Piinlilleq
Petuwaam igallgha
Ungipaghaatet ukuni igani apeghtughistem linguist-em Georgiy A. Menovshchikov-em igaqsuwhaaqaqii apeghtughistenguluni Pamani 1930-ni.
Ukuni igani qula akimigaq siipneqluku ungipaghata Menovshchikovem igaquqii whangkuta Sivuqamelngughnim atightullemnnu mumighqughanka ama Laluramketimun mumighqughanka.
Qamaglluki ungipaghaatet ukut Menovshchikov-em 1988-em igaaneng, Materialy i issledovaniia po iazyku i folʼkloru chaplinskikh eskimosov (Materials and Analysis Concerning the Language and Folklore of the Chaplinski Eskimos), pinguut publishekat Ruusemi.
Una qepghaqaq allgeqaaguq maningyama grantmeng University of Alaska Fairbanks-em Provost-anganeng.
Allgeghutelleghqun Sivuqaghtunga Ruuseghmiit atightullghitneng mumighqughanka whangkunnun atightughyugnaghtesqelluki Kaneghyengesim tanqiini 2001-mi.
Piyuwhaaghmun 45 ungipaghaatet 49-eneng 1988-em igaaneng.
Iwernga piyalghiinga ilangi ungipaghaatem siingenllu aapqat, ilangillu aghsaan ayuqelghiit.
Pinghisaqenka, yuginaq akimigaq siipneqluku siiptuq mumighqughyaghqanka.
Igleghutkelluku tawaten nanqigsimanginaamiita piinka.
Anagngatupiglleghhii Menovshchikov-em igallghani.
Ilangi atightuneghllugllaget repall Ruuseghmistun ayuqelghiikun mumiglluki wetku liigikngwaaghanka sangutangi ipa.
Paamkughmiit akuzillghat allakaniq (katam ellngita ukiniwhangkutestun kaki-, ama ellngitni enngaatall whangtutestun elngaatall), tespamkughmiistun ayuqut ukuni igani.
Ilangakun Paamkughmiit akuzillghat igallgha anagngasugnillequq (katam wengteghaq nakaan mangteghaq).
Enkaam ilangi akuzitem whanga nallukegkenka, sivukluki angayuqamnun Nayghwaaghmiinkugnun June-enkugnun aaptagka sangutangi.
Enkaam ellngita nallukegkiit siivanlleghnun aapsaghtughanka sangutangi.
Igamsiqayugvikanka kayusiqaangatnga Kepelgunkut, Anaggutenkut, Iyaakankut, Uuzagenkut, Avaalagenkut, enkaam kiyang Rosa.
Rosa-m aapqii sangutangi naten atullghi Quyillget akuzitngit.
UAF-mun uteghnighyama Qaluvigem tanqiini 2002-mi Yupigem Prufisernga Steven Jacobson-llu yuvghiighaghpung qepghallghenka Yupigestunllu Laluramkestunllu.
Amalleqa tawani upenghaani recordaanka CD-mun maligutngalghii igatgun.
Ama nimam apellghi Igor Krupnigmeng Smithsonian Institution-meng allgeghtaput tuunii Sivuqaghhmiini nallukegkaput pamanlenguut nunat.
Ama map-a tuunaa tespamum nunam naantulngi apeghluteng Yupiget ama Sighinegmiit kiyaghfikegkii.
UAF College of Liberal Arts-em umiilgan John Leipzig-em ama ANLC-m umiilgan Lawrence Kaplan-em mani piyaqlegginaaghtaak teruwistemeng muutiyaghqaalunga Qakginkugneng Apughitenkugnun Chefaghnaghmeng ungipaghaatenun ilasaghqaluki.
David Koester UAF-em Anthropology Department-meng qepghaghteghyagneng kayutkesaghaqa Undergraduate Research Opportunity Program-em maningviganeng.
Taagken esgha una qepghaqaq allgeqaq.
Ama igamsiqayugvikanka Nauka Publishing House-enkut St. Petersburg, Russia-melnguut aangghutkaangi ANLC-nkut ukut ungipaghaatet publish-enkaluki whatelluki.
Ukut igat ama CD neghyukulluki akuzipillemnnun Yupigetlu kiyaghtaallghanun nagneghusaghqaaluku igleghallemnnun iknaqughisaalukullu, pamanlliimta ungipaghaatngitneng.
Ungipaghaghtet: (Menovshchikov-meng Valentina (Yata) Kunukam mumighquqii, enkaam Igor Krupnigem nallghughqegkii).
1. Ayveghhaq (1914-1947).
Ungazighmii.
Ungazimi allgeqaq.
Ayaangaghmi alleqaq, enkaam yaywaalingughtegkaq, nunalgutangan anglistekaa kayusiqaa.
Ayveghhaq ungipaghaallegllaguyalghii ama ilagallegllaguyalghii nunalgutangan pinganeng.
1940-mi ukut ungipaghatet allgeghtaqngameng 26 year-ngughtuq.
Mekelghiighhaatmineng nagasuneghtughllagyaghtuq ungipaghaatmengllu, ilagaatmengllu alignalghiitlu ungipaghiitneng.
Maakut umyugaanun piluteng sumeghtaghaghqelluku repall.
Ayveghhaq ungipaghaneghmini apaqughaqelghiinguq.
Menovshchikov-em igaquqaqii ama mumighqughii 30-t ungipaghatet Ayveghhaghmeng Ungazimi 1940/41em uksughani, Ekaterina S. Rubstov-am 50 ungipaghata igaquuluku 1940-mi.
Pingayuneng inglulekAyveghhaam ungipagatngi ukunitut igani 18-eni.
2. Peter Tagikaq (1926-1941)
Ungazighmii mekelghiiq.
Mughunniightem ungipaghaghtem Galmugyim (nani 1880-1957) ighnegha.
Takigaam suilughtekaqaa igaghyam sivulighnegha, taagken mughuunnightengughsukaq.
Angayuqaakek Ruuseghmiitingigasaghtuk.
Tagikaam atangan Galmugyim uglaq sangwaa yuginaq sangwaa siipngaan ungipaghaata liisimaksaghaa.
Avaqutaminun ilaminun nunalgutaminun ungipaghaghaqelghii sanghinneghmini mughunniinghinneghmini.
Tagikaam nagatkii neqamikuqii atami ungipaghatangi.
Ilangitnunllu laalighqwaaghaqelghii ununghagu vuvallanghatallu ungipaghaghyaghtughaqelghii, atumaghmeng aghulamaghmeng.
Tagikaam piniqumtaagha ineghlaghllaga Ayveghhaq, yuuk nagatngwaaqayuk ama ungipaghallegllak.
1940/41 em uksughani Menovshchikovem igaaghaqsaghii sivuliit igii akuzipigem grammarngi igaghviget sivulighneghitnun ayuqelghiit.
Kayusingegkaq Ungazim igleghutistengitneng, Chukotkam aaghtistengi Mayngankugneng Mallunkugneng.
Tagikaq tagiiqelghii elkegnun igalgusighyaghtughaqegkangek.
Ataasimeng igagni kelqellukek ungipaghatem ilangi igaqumakangi.
Taagken ima Menovshchikov-enkuk qepghalgutkusimalghiik 30-t ungipaghatet taaqusimakangak.
Nukalpigaq quyamaghllakTagikaq.
Takestaghhaghmini kiyaghtaalleghmini liisimakegkani qamaglluki apellghitii.
Palighvigem tanqiini 1941-mi peleghqegkaaftuq suflugameng pi 11 gilliqluni 15 year-ngughsimaghmi.
Tagikaam ungipaghii ukuni igani 920-metut.
3. Asuya Olga Mumigtekaq (1930-2001) Ungazimi allgeqaq.
Ugimini kiyaghtekaq Sighinegmi.
Pingayuneng inglulegneng avaqutkikak.
Menovshchikov qepghaluni Ungazimi 1954-mi Asuya, atightuqayuk pinaqnelghii, kayutkegkaqeftaa akuzipigem grammarnganeng igaquuluni.
Tamanillu Naayvaghvigem tanqiineng Kaneghyengesim tanqiinun igaquqaqii tawaten pillemtun tallimat ungipaghatet, Menovshchikov-em mumighqughaghtekii.
1970-nillu 1980-nillunursenguluniqepghaaqaaftuq Sighingem clinicngani, ama aflengakegkii avaqutani.
Ama Sighinegmi aghulameng sameng alngunak Yupigem igleghneghaaneng apeghtughiikaq.
Asuyam ungipaghatngi 21-enkuk 22-nkunguuk.
4. Alghalek (1920-1965).
Ungazimi allgeqaq.
Atightuqayuk ama igaqayuglluggaq yuuk.
Ruuseghiitikayuk ama qitevegkayuk ama akuzipikayuk.
1955-mun kenlanga mughunniightengukaq ama ivenruutkegsaghtengukaq Ungazimi “nutaghami kiyaghtaalleghmi”.
Kingungani Egeghaghmun nuugtekaaguq pinighsaghistenguluni ama savikenghaaghmeng ulimastenguluni.
Provideniyam seaportngani ama qepghaqaq.
Rubstova kayusiqaa Yupik-Ruuseghmii dictorary-ngllalleghmeng.
1960-mi Alghalgem 14 ungipaghaata igaqegkaa Provideniya-mi
Alghalgem ungipaghatngi 23-31-nguut ukuni igani.
5. Nanughhaq (1911-1990?).
Ungazimi allgeqaq.
Igallgilnguq atightullgilnguq natengiighhaq Ruuseghmiitikayuk.
4 year-nguluni ayaakaq trachomaluni.
Nanughhaam uglaq ungipaghaata ama ilaagaata liisimaksaghaa, enkaam ungipaghaallegllaguyalghii.
Ungipaghaatngi ilaagaatmeng ilatkat.
15 imgipaghatet allgeghquqat Nanughhaghmeng.
Nanughhaam ukunun iganun ilatkat 3234-nguut.
6. Valentina Viri (Wiri) (1942-mi allgeqaq).
Imtugmii Sighinegmeng.
Liitngwaaqaq Ruuseghmiitellegllalghii.
Ima aghnaaghaghhaatmineng nagatngwaaqaq, ungipaghaatkegkii igaquqii ungipaghaatet.
Ukuni igani ungipaghaatnga Pista 35-nguuq.
Ukamangaan
Iimnanguq Ungazighmiit Sivuqamun atghaamalghiit.
Ilameng Sivuqaghmiit taghnughhaghqiit wayaamaqegket maalghuknayakullghiik.
Aglaasimakegket Ungazimun.
Mekelghiighhaam aatgha Kaanghu, uyuqlighpigaq.
Aghnaghaghllagem aatgha Ukamangaan.
Aghnaghaghllak ugighyaghqastun angkaliikaq.
Ungazimun kaalluteng maalghugegneng qavaamalghiit.
Aqimalghiit Uvingemun1 taghnughhaak tuunyaghtuumakegket quyngilegnun.
Kaasameng Uvingemun esghaamakangit Quyillegllaget.
Aapsimakangi Quyillgem, “Sangafsi tagistek?”
Akisimakangat Ungazighmiit, “Whangkuta tagiikut inqunamen taghnughhaak tukfiisqellukek quyngimeng.”
Quyillek sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Naqam ighnelek aangelghiimeng.”
Pimakanga, “Itupilqun ighneqa nulightughyaquni yuginakaghnayaghamsi quyngimeng.”
Llaaghanwha tuunaqaat Ukamangaan aghnaghaghllak.
Kaanghu tuunenghitaat mekelghiighhaq.
Uteghsimalghii Ungazimun.
Ukamangaan ugiightuq Quyillegmun Uvingeghmiimeng.
Uginga yuukegtepiglleghhii ama sukatepiglleghhii ama iknaqepiglleghhii.
Ukamangaan ineqsunapiglleghhii ama sungaghatepiglleghhii.
Ukamangaan meghtaghaqelghii ama ukiniiqelghii.
Meghtaghnaqneghmini ugkemeng qugtuqagni keviighaqegkek.
Kiiwegnun kaanneghmini tamaghhaan aghneq ugkemeng miluqutaghaqelghii inglunganun.
Tawatestaghhiinaq.
Ilangani kamengllaghtaamalghii.
Uglapiglleghhii kamelghun ulimamakanga.
Taaqegkani ugkemeng imighaqluku.
Kamek taaqumakanga yuginaq qula siipneqluku tumangani inqunamen aasaghqaluku.
Maaten ilangani metngeghumalghii.
Kamelghun akmagluku aqeftaghaghmun kanaghlluku igleghsimalghii.
Igataneghmini kaamget tuguluki ugkemeng tugulluni neghaqelghii.
Qavaghyimeghmini nunami temngi qavaghaqelghii.
Kaamgi naavenghata allaneng kaamgaqelghii.
Maaten ilangani kaasimalghii mengteghaghllagkun paaghqilngughqun.
Mengteghaq neqetupiglleghhii, mangtagmeng ayveghmeng neghsameng ama quyngimeng.
Amigem saaghwani saghumigneghem tungangani yugem neqanga.
Ukamangaan aqumgaamaluku iitghumalghii aghnaghrukutaaghllak mataqeltaghhaq.
Uvin’ga qatepiglleghhii qugintapiglleghhii.
Pimakanga Ukamangaan, “Kakumiy, naken pizin?”
Ukamangatem akisimakanga, “Quyillegneng piinga.”
Aghnaghrukutaaghllak aleghqughtuq, “Nakumiinguzin?”
“Sivuqaghmiinguunga.”
“Saqumazin Uvingemun?”
“Ungazighmiit akikumaatnga Quyillegnun.”
“Neghelta!
Neneghmeng taaqegkumta ingaghquullghaakut.
Whanga qavaneghtughllagtunga.
Unaami taghsaghnaaghaghpenga.
Taakuta ayveghem elqunghek akitma asingani tugunakegken taagken anagunakevnga naasqumkun.
Taghtughnaaghtunga.”
Llaaghanwha neghusimalghiik mangtagmeng Ukamangaatenkuk aghnaghrukutaaghenkuk.
Neneghmeng taaqlutek ingaghquullutek qavaasimalghiik.
Unaami unanguluku taghtuumalghii Ukamangaan.
Taghsaamakanga aghnaghrukutaaq, “Uyuq, uyuq taghtaa!”
Nagaquumangisimalghii.
Qaywa naasqwa kevgusimaaqsaqanga aghulasimakanga wanlegi nagaquumangisimalghii.
Ayveghem naasqukek tugulukek uqliisimaaqsaqanga Ukamangaan alingumaaqelghii.
Qenwat utaqiiluni lliightuq.
Aghuliightuq taghsaghineghmeng.
Iiwenllu aghneghem qukaanun lliighaquq aghnaghrukutaaghllak taghtuumalghii.
Taghtughluni agniiquq, “Ii-ik, ii-ik, ii-ik, aghnaghaghhaghmi whani allameng taghsanghilkuvnga neghelleqamken!”
Aghnaghrukutaaq aqumumalghii.
Pimakanga Ukamangaan, “Igataghtunga!
Tuuninga taagken yugem neqanganeng.”
Ukamangaatem tuunumakanga.
Aghnaghrukutaaghllak neghumalghii.
Neneghmeng taaqluni aanumalghii.
Ukamangaatem nallukumakanga natmun pimatanga.
Tagiyalghiimi unangumalghii neghsameng.
Pimakanga Ukamangaan, “Enta neghelta!
Unaami anagunakevnga taawanginaq wata.
Iiwen anagunghilkuvnga neghelleqamken!”
Neqaghlutek qavaamalghiik.
Unaami unanguluku taghtuumalghii Ukamangaan.
Ukamangaatem elqunghek tugumakek.
Sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Qaywa tuqulanga!”
Anagumakanga naasqwakun qevuulluku.
Aghnaghrukutaaghllak aqumumalghii nenglaamaghmi, “Hahahaha!
Tawaten tawaten tawaten!
Uveghllunga anagunayaqevnga aglaaghhaatenngam atkuka una aalluku.
Yugunghitunga, kayngenguunga.”
Llaaghanwha aghulaqumalghii Ukamangaan Ungazimun.
Igleghsimalghii kaasaghtuumalghii Ungazimun sukalluni.
Igleghsimaluku yuggaam esghaamakanga mengteghaam saaghwaneng.
Araamalghii, “Maakughsiiy kayngeghllak taakwa!”
Yulghutet ughluveteng panateng tugulaghluki malighqaghaat.
Ukamangaan araghtuq, “Kayngengunghitunga, aghnaghhaguunga!”
Yaghlegi mulaaghtuq kayngestun.
Ukamangaan aghuliightuq.
Nasani mataghtaa.
Gginaa aliightuq.
Yuget esghaghluku liisuqaat llaaghan Ukamangaan.
Awenralengan pimakanga, “Tagipigesnaghtuten.
Ayumiqun itagnatun tuunyaghtughlleqamken quyngilegnun.”
Aghnaghaam atkuni mataghlluku taglaamalghii.
Tawani neghtuq mangunameng.
Qavanghituq.
Esnamun piyaaguq.
Tawani qiyamalghii nuna tukeghraamaan.
Enkaamam iiwenllu mamlegtaqaa Ukamangaan qiyakestaghngaaghmi qavaamalghii.
Iwernga qavanguumalghii.
Angyat tagiqeftut.
Angyat kaatut.
Araamakangat, “Ukamangaatnguzin?”
“Ipapik.”
“Quneghlluten angyamun uugten!”
Llaaghanwha uugtuq Ukamangaan angyamun esghaghpenani.
Suqsughtaghtut suqsughtaghtut.
Sivuqamun kaatut.
Qenaghpallaatut.
“Esghaghhaatenngamnalugullghaaten quutmun!”
Llaaghanwha sivukluni nalugutuq Ukamangaan esghaghpenani.
Saaghhwaakun miluusimakangat nengik maalghuk mangtak.
Ukamangaan pimakangat, “Esgha taana angyaataghqaghhaan!
Aglaghnaqegkuvek tugunaken!”
Qavaqestaghngaaghmi taghtughyalghiimi angyat aviitut.
Piyalghiimi nunami allami liisuqaa llangaqa Sivuqami.
Naqam saaghwani aghveghllagek maalghuk malluk.
Taglaamalghii mengteghamun Ukamangaan.
Pimalghii, “Ipapik Sivuqamun kaasimaftunga, u-u-u-u!”
Quyaghllagumalghii mengteghamun kaatuq.
Araamalghii ilutmun, “Qamaay kenghhaghmeng kumaghhutaghtek.”
Sivukluku nagaqunghitaat.
Qavaataqut.
Araghlaataghii, “Sukallusi!”
Atanga taghtughtuq.
Aapsimakanga, “Kinanguzin?”
Ukamangaan akisimakanga, “Whangangunga!”
Nuliini taghsaghaa, “Uyuq uyuq, taghtaa sukalluten!
Llangaqa Ukamangaatem menga nagaqughaqa.”
Naanga nuugtuq.
Aapsimakanga, “Kinanguzin?”
“Sanaqestek whangangunga.”
Naangan atanga pimakanga, “Llangaqa Ukamangaatem menga.”
Atanga pimalghii, “Llangaqa llangaqa.”
Ukamangaanpimalghii “Entaqun taananguunga!”
Iitghumalghii aagramun.
Atani pimakanga, “Neneghmeng taaqegkufsi yuuk qaagna kelgughluku angyaataghhaanka saamkut pilagyaghtughnakesi!”
Atangan aapsimakanga, “Sakun tagimazin?”
“Qavangughlunga Ungazimi esnami qavanguqanka angyat Sivuqaghhmiit.
Taaggun uugllunga taginga.”
Atanga ugpeghtuq panigmineng.
Neneghmeng taaqluteng kelgughaat yuuk qamaglluku.
Aghveghek maalghuk pilagumakegket.
Taawa nengightuusimakangit taawanginaq.
Tefaay.
Ungipaghaan Ukiivagmiit
Iimnanguq Ukiivagmii nuliilek, avaqutiilnguq.
Nuliini awen iiwleng qiitghaqegkanga.
Ama nunalgutetuqat.
Maaten ilangani aghnaq aanumalghii uginga mughusimaluku.
Aanluni, anigusighaqluni, meghek anigumeng keviimakek.
Llaaghanwha itegaan asingi aghimakangi.
Taagken apeghiighyami iitghumalghii.
Iteghyami, qulmesiitni meghmeng imiimakanga.
Ama ugkellimalghii.
Apeghiighyami ugkellineghmeng, qulmesiitni agaghsimakanga.
Ama nanit qetngighqumakangi.
Taagken ugimineng utaqiimalghii.
Llaaghanwha uginga mulunghituq taglaamalghn.
Kaalluni, iitghumalghii.
Iteghyalghiimi unangumalghii.
Taagken yugem nuliini tuqluumakanga, “Neghsaq taawa!”
Nulighha aangghumalghii, “Aa-a!”
Aghnam neghsaq itghusimakanga.
Uginga efsughluni, iitghumalghii.
Iteghyami, nuliini pimakanga, “Enta, iteganka malliighqi!”
Llaaghanwha aghnam ugimi itegii aallgumakangi.
Yuuk ayavisitamun aaghhumalghii.
Kaasami atkuni mataghsimakanga.
Taagken amsikaghtuq.
Nulighhan pilugugi agaghqughii.
Apeghiighyami, qayuutaq saaglluku, ugini neqlightuumakanga.
Neneghmeng taaqluni, nuliighmi kamegkek saafsimakek.
Saafsaqegni, aghipateftuk.
Yugem pimakanga, “Sangamek kaamgegken aghipatak?
Awituwaq yugneng allaneng ugiighaquten!”
“Waniwanllu, ugiighigatunga!
Taawanginaq meghek anigumeng kevighlukek, iteghtunga.”
Ugingan wanlegi nuliini qiitghumakanga.
Apeghiighyamigu ingaghqulluteng qavaasimalghiit.
Unaami unaanguluku taghtuumalghiit.
Taghtughluteng yuuk tungtuquyaamalghii.
Kingunganeng aghnaq pilugugumalghii.
Pilugugluni, aghulaqumalghii sikugnun.
Ama sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Entaqun meghmi tuquyaquma, pinighnayaghtunga.”
Taagken igleghsimalghii.
Meghnuneghmini aqfaataqluni, qenwat puqlayaaghqumalghii.
Puqlayaqesami aghuliighumalghii.
Meghnaalitkelluku uteghmun esghaghyalghiimi mengteghamllu esnamllu akulangani.
Tawani meghnaalimalghii.
Meghnaaliyami, igleghllaataghtuq tumangani aqfaataqluni.
Qenwat unugyaghtughaa.
Taagken aghuliighlaataghtuq.
Esghaghyalghiimi neminitaqeftuq.
Aghnaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Entaqun kiyaghneghem meghmi tuqusnegha ighlekaanga.
Itupill quutmi tuqusqesimakanganga.”
Taagken sumeghtaghaneghmeng taaqluni, Ukiivagmun mayuumalghii.
Naqam alla sukatepiglluni Ukiivagem qaaynganun uugsimalghii.
Uuglluni esghaamakanga uyghagrukutaaghllak sagleghaghllak.
Taaggun aghnaq aqumumalghii.
Tawani qiyaamalghii, nuna tukeghraamaan.
Nutaan ugini qitelquvinghaa neqaata.
Qiyam angtalanganeng repall araamalghii.
Qiyamaluku sagleghaghllak sivutmun aghelqutqaghsimalghii.
Qiyaqestaghngaaghmi aghuliighaghsimalghii.
Uteghmun esghaghyalghiimi payek esghaghaak.
Aghnaq nekevluni payegnun qineghsimalghii.
Qineghlluni esghaghyaqenni qaamnanga mamlegllagpetuq.
Tawani esghapagumalghii ama sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Entaqun qamavek ifkaghyaquma, tuqunayaghtunga.”
Aghnaq aqumluni payegnun ighugni kanaghquusimakek.
Tesqamani saafunnaqutkesaghtuq minglenganeng.
Aghtughyami pimalghii, “Entaqun ifkaghlanga!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq ifkaamalghii.
Ifkaghyalghiimi kuyapegakun tuusimalghii.
Ifkaghviga taana nenglughllaguftuq.
Taagken aghnaq kiwatmiighsimalghii, talligni saagtaghllukek.aqfaataqluni.
Qenwat egkwaanun kaanneghmeng aghtughyami sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Una nenglukuniqegkegka entaqun nunaghllaguuq.”
Taagken igleghsimalghii.
Nighuggaq aliighumakanga.
Taagken igleghsimalghii.
Nighuggaq taana takumakanga.
Nighuggaq anglimalghii.
Qenwat mengteghaqlu aliighumalghii.
Kaasimalghii aghnaq mengteghaghrukutaaghllagmun.
Taagken iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni nateghmi qiighwumalghii.
Ungavigllagneng nukalpigaq nuugumalghii.
Nuugluni pimalghii, “Saam aghnaqaten?”
“Ukiivagmiinguunga!”
“Qaywa tughneghaanghisiin?”
“Tughneghaanghitunga, yupiguunga!
Elpeg yeqay entaqun tughneghaaguten.”
Yugem akitaa, “Tughneghaanghitunga yupiggaagunga, yupiggaagunga!
Elpegngam saquzin ukavek?”
“Ugima qiitqanganga uglapiglluku ipagfigun tuqunalunga piyaghtunga.
Tuquneghmeng aghtughtunga.
Qenwat whaa tukughqalegnun ivaghiiqunga.”
Yugem pimakanga, “Walenqakun, taawa nulighqelleqamken!
Enta iitghi!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan yugem pimakanga, “Amsikaghlluten neqmeng avegtaa!
Negheltung!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq amsikaghtuq.
Amsikaghhneghmeng taaqluni qayuutaq ketfaghaa.
Taagken neqmeng avegtughtuq.
Apeghiighluni avegtughat miluusimakangi.
Neghumalghiik.
Neneghmeng taaqlutek, yugem aghnaq pii, “Enta allighat saagtiki!”
Llaaghanwha aghnam allighat saagsimakangi.
Taagken ingaghquusimalghiik.
Ingaghquullutek qavaasimalghiik.
Unaami unaanguluku taghtughyamek, aghnaq ugingan pimakanga, “Mughutaghhnaqunga qayakun aghvelegnun.
Aghvenglunga tagillequnga.”
Yuuk nateghmun aatghumalghii.
Ateghluni qayani ukigsimakanga.
Ukiglluku, aqumumalghii qayaminun.
Uunghani tuguluku, mingla naghullegyaqenni mingla quupaghsimalghii.
Quupaghsalghiimi meghllak minglemeng iitghumalghii.
Yuuk kesimalghii, eslamun angwaaghumalghii.
Anqaghsan quupaghllak maamumalghii, ama nateq meghisimalghii.
Taagken aghnaq ugimi kingunganeng ukinimalghii kamegneng.
Iiwenllu aghneghem qukaghaqaa, kaamgek taaqumakek.
Taaqsamikek enraq ugkellimalghii.
Gaaghumalghii.
Ugket ugusaki aqumesimakangi.
Mulunghituq uvitanganeng mengqughusimalghii, ama meghllak iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aghnaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Awituwaq ugika taglaghtuq.”
Taagken aghuliighumalghii.
Llaaghanwha uginga quupaghllagkun nuugumalghii.
Nuugyalghiimi aghvengumalghii.
Aghveq iingunaghllagan nateghmun itghusimakanga.
Quupaghllak taana maamumalghii.
Nateghmi yugem aghveghllak kagimsimakanga.
Taagken tawani kiyaghsimalghii.
Maaten ilangani aghnaq aqsangumalghii.
Aqsangluni ighniyalghiimi mekelghiighhaghmeng, taagken taghnughhangumalghiit.
Yuuk tungtuquyaneghmini tungtungaqelghii.
Meghmun pineghmini meghem teghikusaa allaghhiinaq unakaqegkanga.
Ama awergha allaghhiinaq tawani kiyaghlleghhii.
Taghnughhaghhaq sukalluni anglimalghii.
Mulunghituq aghnaq aqsanglaataghtuq, ighniyalghiimi aghnaghaghhaghmeng.
Taawa maalghugegnengtaghnughhangumalghiik.
Maaten ilangani yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Entaqun whavek tagiighten.
Kinguneghten nagasaghtuqaghqi.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq ugimi saaghwanun aglaamalghii.
Tawani nagasimalghii.
Nagaquunneghmeng aghtughtuq.
Yugem aapsimakanga, “Qayugham sameng nagaquutaghhneghisin?”
“Nakaa nagaquutaghneghhitunga.”
“Aa-a!”
Yugem nuliighmi sigutkek suupataghaak.
Pimakanga, “Enta allamengminglemun sigutegken mategllukek nagaten.”
Llaaghanwha aghnam sigutegni minglemun mategsaqegni kinguneni atughllalghiit nagasimakangi.
Aghnaq qiyamalghii ama araamalghiit kingunghi eslallugughunniluteng.
Taagken tawani qiyaneghmeng taaqumalghii.
Taaqluni sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Amen nunamnun aglaghnaanghitunga.
Luuraqlu nunamnun kaaskuma ugima tuqulleqanga.”
Ugingan aapsimakanga “Aghyuqaghsigasiin?”
Akisimakanga, “Aghyuqeghngaaghma salunga pilanga?
Tumanga whangamni nallunaghtekanga.”
“Enta kalngaggaak kumlugpetun angkalghiik maalghuk ulimakek.”
Llaaghanwha aghnam kalngaggaak maalghuk ulimamakek.
Apeghiighyakek, ugiminun kelgusimakek.
Llaaghanwha ugingan tugumakek.
Tugulukek awergham allaghhiinam melqwaaneng imiimakek.
Imineghmeng taaqsamikek aghnaq pimakanga, “Enta piighhangllaa.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq piighhangllaamalghii.
Taaqsami ugiminun kelgullaataghaa.
Ugingan piighhaghqun kalngaggaak maalghuk petugumakek ama aghnaqlu aghnaghaghhaqlu.
Apeghiighyamiki pimakanga, “Whagun naatghem qukaanun ukiggnaqamken.
Enan kinguvneng mengteghaqlu maligunnaaghtuq.”
Taagken naatghem qukaanilnguq sagleghaghllak awisimakanga.
Awisaqenni payeghllagek aliighumalghiik.
Qaamnanga nighupiglleghhii.
Yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Enta pinitun neghelta aghulaqfagilgavek.”
Llaaghanwha neghumalghiik.
Neghutkelluku yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Taana aghnaghaghhaq elpek kevgaqelleqan.
Whanga mekelghiighhaq taana kevgaqelleqaqa.
Ama ungipaannaqamken, Ukiivagmi saama ugin nulightuumaaq aghnaghaghneng maalghugegneng ineqsunapiglleghhiineng.
Enekiitek vuvallaaqut, esghaghlleqaten.
Entaqunngam ukiggnaqamken.
Enan mengteghaq kinguvneng maligunnaaghtuq.
Iiwen ugivek aapnaaghaaten, avelghaqiinaghnaken.
Sagiqegkan pinaken, ‘Enan unaami ungipaannaghamken.’
Iiwen naatghanun kaaskuvek uteghmun esghaghnaaghtuten.
Mengteghaq esghaghlleqan.
Esghaquvgu piighhaq ilemqughluku panikullghiitek aglaghhaatek mengteghamun.
Aglaquftek mengteghaq qelpeghtekufsigu, iitquftek signeghet maalghugneghet tugulleqaten.
Tugukufki ilakek signeghek mangtagmeng avegtuutaqlukek imighlleqagken.
Ilakek quyngimeng avegtuutaqlukek imighlleqagken.
Ugivek mengteghaanun aglaalleqagken.
Llaaghanwha nanevgaat neghelleqiit.
Taawa qamagtunga.
Ukiggnaqamsi.”
Llaaghanwha yugem payek suupsaqegni anglighaataamalghiik.
Taakwagun payegnekun ukigsimakangit.
Nunamun tuusimalghiik.
Tuusamek kalngak esghaghyaqeseng anglighllagumalghii.
Mengteghaq tunutangitnun ifkaamalghii.
Aghnakpanikullghiik, qiivlutekaglaamalghiik.
Kaallutek iitghumalghiik.
Iteghlutek aghnam signeghet maalghugneghet tugumakangek.
Tuguluki ilakek quyngimeng imiimakek, ilakek mangtagmeng.
Apeghiighyamikek paniggani pimakanga, “Enta tawani utaqanga.
Ugika payuggnaqaqa, naten kiyaghtaqa.”
Panigan aangghumakanga.
Llaaghanwha aghnaq ugiminun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Taawa vuvallaaqeftut ama yugtughllaguftuq.
Atughaqeftut aghulamaghmeng.
Aghnaq aagramun nuugyan qallegnanighwaaghusimalghiit.
Taagken tawani esghapagumalghii.
Ugini esghaghyaqenni quulqitem qaayngani nuliigqek maalghuk ingaghtaaghutaqeftuk.
Aghnam ugiminun signeghek quyngimeng imaqelghiik tuunumakek.
“Ang, ukuk naasiighqek!”
Llaaghanwha ugingan signeghegneng ataasiq avegtughaq neghumakanga.
Taaqsamigu nuliighminun tuunumakek.
Sivukluku nuliini liisuqumangisimakanga.
Nulighhan signeghek tugumakek.
Tugulukek yugnun tamaghhaanun uyegsimakek avegtughat ataasikaghtaan.
Taawateghpigaq naamamalghiik signeghek.
Ilakeklu signeghek tugumakek mantagmeng imaqelghiik.
Tanemwha ugiminun tuunlaataghaak.
Pilaataghaa, “Enta ukuklu naasighqek.”
Llaaghanwha ugingan signeghek mangtagmeng imaqelghiik tugaak naasighlaataghaak.
Avegtughaq ataasiq neghaa.
Taaqsamigu nuliighminun signeghek tuunumakek.
Nulighhan sughukanun tamaghhaanun uyegsimakek.
Tanemwha signeghem imaa naamalaataghtuq.
Signeghet imiighusata aanumalghii.
Aanluni mengteghaminun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Taagken ugingan yulghun tamana pimakanga, “Ukughsiy, entaqun aagna nulighqaqa!”
Nuliini aallgha ineqsunalleghpigaa tugumakanga.
Pimakanga, “Elpek ataveknaavek enngaatall paniknakangaten!”
Uwatmun ayagaghsimakanga.
Aghnaq quulqitmeng asitmun ifkaamalghii.
Pilugugluni aanumalghii.
Aanyan yuuk pilaataghtuq, “Ukughsiy, entaqun aagna nulighqaqa, llangaqa nulighqa.”
Ilangallu nuliini tugumakanga.
Pilaataghaa, “Uyuq elpeklu naavnun atavnun aglaghhaaten!”
Yugem siingumakanga quulqitem qaaynganeng asitmun.
Ifkaghllaataghaa.
Aghnaq pilugugluni aanumalghii.
Yuuk pilugugumalghii enkaam aanumalghii.
Nutaghaq mengteghaq esghaamakanga.
Tazingavek aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyalghiimi nuliini esghaamakanga.
Nulighhan quyakumakanga aapsimakanga, “Sangaawagmi taakuk aghnaghaak?”
Yugem akisimakanga, “Whanga nulighqesaghagka.”
Yugem aaptaa, “Elpek naken pizin?”
“Unaami ungipaannaaghamken.”
Taagken aghnam qayuutaq ketfaghluku ugini neqlightuumakanga.
Uginga neghumalghii quyngimeng.
Neneghmeng taaqsan nulighha allighimalghii nutaghaastaghhiinaghmeng.
Allighineghmeng taaqsan ingaghqulluteng qavaasimalghiit.
Unaami taghtughluteng nulighhan ugini pimakanga, “Pilugugi ungipaannaqamken.”
Llaaghanwha yuuk pilugugumalghii.
Enkaam nulighqullghiik aanleghaasimalghiik.
Aanleghaallutek Ukiivagmun mayuumalghiik.
Qaaynganun uugsalghiimek sagleghaghllak esghaamakangat saglegham saaghwani mayeghllaget.
Aghnam pimakanga, “Taawa ungipaannaqamken, mayet ukut angeghquulteki mengteghamun.”
Ugingan aangghumakanga.
Llaaghanwha angeghqughiit mengteghamun.
Awergha allaghhiinaq amiq ilakunneghilnguq melqwa.
Unaghhaaneng angaghqughaat unullghem kenlanganun.
Apeghiighyameng aghnam ugini pimakanga, “Unaami nunalgutfut tamaghhaan awerghameng tallimakaghtaan uyeggnaken amilighaqluku ataasikaghtaan.”
Llaaghanwha yuuk aangghumalghii.
Taagken iteghaatuk.
Iteghaallutek neghtuk.
Taagken ingaghquullutek qavaasimalghiik.
Unaami taghtughlutek, yugem nunalgutni qamaglluku tuqlughteghumakanga.
Taagken uyegsimakanga amimeng ataasikaghtaan awerghaneng tallimakaghtaan.
Qamagsimakanga mengteghaq tamaghhaan.
Taagken kenlanga yugem nuliini pillugaghnanighaa ama pinitun kiyaghsagutut.
Yuuk neqengyughighllagtuq, ama aklungighimalghiit.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay!
Yaywaalingiighhaak
Iimnanguq, aghnaghaghhaqlu mekelghiighhaqlu nayakutalghiik.
Nayagan aatgha Taykengaawen, mekelghiighhaam aatgha Taykegergen.
Nunami kiyaghlleghhiit Nuutqami.
Nunalgutetuqat ama umiilelget.
Umiilgita yaywaalingiighhaak piniqepigtekek.
Maaten ilangani igatiqumalghiit nunalgutangit.
Katamqun umiilgat neqelek.
Taagken umiilgem nuliini pimaqegkanga, “Yaywaalingiighhaak neqaghhaghmeng tuunaghtaaqikek, salin esghaghhu kayaalnguuk.”
Llaaghanwha nulighhan neqmeng aglaasimakek.
Llaaghanwha neqayugumalghiik igatiqumangisimalghiik.
Nunalgutangit paneghaasimalghiit.
Maaten ilangani mekelghiighhaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Naten piyaquma neqmeng tugunnayaghsinga.”
Mekelghiiq unaghsighwaaghmeng itghusimalghii.
Taagken savighhumakanga.
Tullumkeghlluku taaqumakanga.
Taaqsamigu neghqwaaghhaq tugutkuvinghaghhaq ulimamakanga tugeghpaggaq.
Taaqumakanga.
Taagken tapghaghhaghmeng ivaghimalghii.
Naalkusami unaghsighwaaghem iqugakun petugumakanga.
Enkaam asinganun uyghaggaq petugumakanga.
Taagken Taykegergen yataaghqumalghii.
Nayani pimakanga, “Qiiptaasimeng taaqutunga.
Qiiptaghyaghnaqunga.
Aghulaqegkuma elpek siklaghyaghnaaghtuten mengtegham saaghwanun piitutelegnun.”
Taagken Taykegergen esnamun atghaamalghii.
Sigugneghmun uugsimalghii.
Uuglluni anglaaq ukinnaqumakanga.
Ukisamigu qiiptaasini ateghlluku qiiptaamalghii elqwaaghmeng.
Nayaga Taykengaawen aanumalghii.
Alungutellghem asingani siklaamalghii.
Siklaghluni piitutmeng akuquusimalghii.
Taagken saghnaamaluku yuuk tagimalghii.
Ratamiirakek qatelghiik.
Kaalluni Taykengaawen tuqluumakanga, “Taykung, Taykung, whanga tuguyugaqsaghamken!”
Taykengaawem akisimakanga, “Elpenun sumeghtaghanghitunganulighqesqellunga.
Enmis aghulaqi!”
Llaaghanwha yuuk aghulaqumalghii.
Piyalghiimi qatelghiinguftuq.
Taagken yuuk ilanga tagimalghii.
Ratamiirakek kavilnguuk.
Kaalluni yugem tuqluumakanga, “Taykuung, Taykuung, tugunaluten piiqsaghamken!”
Taykengaawem akisimakanga, “Sumeghtaghanghitunga elpenun nulightuulunga!
Enmis aghulaqi!”
Llaaghanwha yuuk aghulaqumalghii.
Piyalghiimi kaviipiggaaftuq.
Taagken tawani kiyaghsimalghii.
Kiyaghsimaluku yuuk tagimalghii tagneqegtameng atkukelghii.
Yugem tuqluumakanga, “Taykung, Taykung, esghaqaqun ukavek!”
Llaaghanwha Taykengaawem esghaamakanga.
Esghaghluku iqlighsimalghii.
Allameng tuqluumakanga, “Taykung, Taykung, ugiksukanghisinga?”
Taykengaawen yaghlegi nenglaamalghii, “Ete, ete.”
Yugem pimakanga, “Nengliisqenghitamken ipapik piimken.”
Taykengaawem pimakanga, “Taawanginaq whanganginanghitunga, anengalguunga.
Aamtaam ighlekegkaanganga ugiighnaanghitunga.
Aamtaam aangqanganga ugiighllequnga.”
Yugem pimakanga, “Wiin aghulaqnaqunga.
Enan anengaan tagikan whangallu taginaaghtunga.”
Llaaghanwha yuuk aghulaqumalghii.
Taykengaawen piitutmeng allaghhiinaghmeng saghnaamalghii.
Taaqluni iitghumalghii.
Mulunghituq Taykegergen esnameng taglaamalghii mengteghaminun.
Qiiptaqengumalghii elqwaaghmeng.
Elqwaaghet qungangitgun maklak kanaghsimakanga.
Iteghluni nayani pimakanga, “Qiiptaqengumanga elqwaaghmeng.
Elqwaaghet qungangitgun maklagmeng qiiptaqengumanga.”
Nayagan pimakanga, “Kay, walenqakun!
Neghellequkung ighivgaghhaq ataasighhaq.”
Taagken Taykengaawem maklak aflaamakanga.
Taykegergempimakanga, “Umiilegput neqmeng aglaatigu, elqwaaghmeng unatameng.”
Llaaghanwha Taykengaawem sagneghni neqmeng imiimakek elqwaaghmeng ama unatameng.
Taagken aglaasimakek umiilgem nulighhanun.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan qamaken aapsimakangat, “Kinangaawa?”
Taykengaawem akisimakangi, “Whanganguunga, taawa neghyaghqaghhaat.”
Umiilgem nulighhan nuugvikumakanga.
Aapsimakanga, “Kinkut neqengat?”
“Taykegergen maklagmeng qiiptaqengumalghii.”
Taagken aghnam sagneghek tugumakek.
Tugulukek niivlukek Taykenaawemun tuunumakek.
Llaaghanwha Taykengaawem aglaasimakek.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni amsikaghsimalghii.
Mulunghituq nateghmeng kavlegusimalghii.
Taykegergem aapsimakanga, “Kinangaawa?”
Yugem nateghmeng akisimakanga, “Whanganguunga.”
“Iitqaalten!”
Llaaghanwha yuuk iitghumalghii.
Iteghyalghiimi aghneghniimnanguftuq.
Iteghyan Taykegergem aapsimakanga, “Saqughllagsin?”
Yugem akisimakanga, “Nayagen tuguyaghtughaqaqa.
Iiteg’qun ighlekenghilkuvgu enan nayaka tugunayaghan.”
Taykengaawem Taykegergen aksaqluku pimakanga, “Taykegur, angeghnakevnga!”
Taagken yuuk Taykegergem pimakanga, “Aghnaghaq umyugalgulghii angeghyukuni ugiighlleqelghii.”
Taagken Taykengaawen pimalghii, “Taawa ugiightunga, ighsanghitunga!”
Llaaghanwha yugem Taykengaawen aglaannaqaa.
Taykegergen pimalghii, “Wiin ataasimeng qavaa.
Unaami aglaghhaaten.”
Llaaghanwha yuuk tawani qavaamalghii.
Unaami unaanguluku nuliini aglaasimakanga.
Yugem nayaga Taykegergemun tagimalghii.
Taykegergen nulightughtuq.
Taykegergen enngaatall unangyupiglleghii.
Maaten ilangani yuuk tagimalghii Taykegergemun.
Pimakanga, “Taykegur, seghleghunayanghista mengteghaput qerngughusaqumteki.”
Taykegergem akisimakanga, “Entaqun pinighnayaghtukut.”
Unaami taghtughluteng mengteghateng naafqumakangat.
Naafqelluku mesungesagem saaghwanun aglaamalghiit.
Taagken mesungesaget tunuqiitgun mengteghaamalghiit.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghiit.
Maaten ilangani yuuk tagimalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Taykegergen tuqluumakanga, “Taykegur, whangkunnun aglaqaa, esghapagyaghtuqaghnga!”
Llaaghanwha Taykegergen ellngitnun aglaamalghii.
Iteghyan Taykengaawem pimakanga, “Ugika esghapaggu mughunnaqelghii.”
Yugem kameni tugumakanga.
Tuguluku nuliighminun tuunumakanga.
“Taykengaay, kaamka piginighhu!”
Llaaghanwha Taykengaawem maklagem ungalghunganeng kaamga kanaghfikumakanga.
Inglunga neghsam ungalghunganeng kanaghfikumakanga.
Taagken yuuk kaamgumalghii.
Kamegluni nekevyalghiimi aghenqignegha itegaa maklagestun puugumalghii.
Inglunga neghsastun puugumalghii.
Taagken esnamun atghaamalghii.
Kaalluni aqumuq.
Aqumyan maklak neghsaq nuugleghasimalghii.
Taagken yugem savigmineng kenuqaamakanga tuqulluku.
Llaaghanwha maklagmeng neghsameng taglaquusimalghiik mengteghamegnun.
Taagken tawani kiyaghsimalghiik.
Taykegergenllu llitiyalghiimi enngaatall unangyuughsimakanga.
Teghikusameng tamaghhaaneng aghtughnaniimalghii.
Maaten ilangani yugem tagiluni ungipaasimakanga, “Unaami vuvallallequkut.
Ingluklighhamnneng kayaalqiiraghyaghtut tagillequt sanqutetuumaghmeng.
Tagillequt atungagmeng tanpeghhmeng temkagmeng tapghaghmeng.
Ellngita aghulastekaqaat amiqluggaq.
Aghulaneghmini taawanginaq ilagaatnginaghqun nalughqutaghaquq.
Kayaalqegkunikut sanqutamnneng wayaghlleqiinkut.”
Taagken yuuk mengteghaminun aglaamalghn.
Enngaatall Taykegergen nagaqughluni qevuulluni alingumalghii inqun wayaghnayukangisteng.
Unugyagu Taykegergen aanumalghii.
Aanluni uughqanun esghaghyaamalghii.
Agepsughtaaghet esghaamakangi.
Takumakangi.
Kaasaqenni nenglunguftuq.
Iitghumalghii.
Taawa nanevgaghllaklu aghnalwaaghllaklu esghaamakangek.
Nanevghaghllagem pimakanga, “Saquzin?”
Taykegergem akisimakanga, “Apeghtiisqellunga taginga.”
Nanevgaghllakpimalghii, “Enta apeghtughlaken!
Taawanginaq aapnaqamken, ingluklighhaghpesi aghulastengat naten piyaghqaawa?”
“Taawanginaq amiqluggaq nalughqutaghyaghqaaguq.”
Nanevgaghllagem nuliini pimakanga, “Aghnalqwaay, enta saguyagka tagivaghqek!”
Llaaghanwha aghnalqwaam saguyaknanevgamun tuunumakek.
Nanevgam tugumakek.
Taagken pimalghii, “Nagu teghlaghllak?
Tagi whavek.
Ilagaannaqamken!”
Teghlaghllak nanevgam kaagkaakun nalugumalghii.
Nanevgaam ilagaasimakanga, “Ayangiyaa, yangiyangaa, ayangingii yangiyaa!”
Teghlaghllagem yaqugni saagtaatamaagkenka tuyegni qapragsimakek.
Ilagaan naangyan qetgeqaamaghmi qalghiqaamalghi.
Taagkennanevgaampimakanga, “Taawa apeghtughamken!
Aglaghhaaten!”
Llaaghanwha Taykegergen aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghluni amsikaghlluni qavaamalghii.
Unaami unanguluku nayagan aqfaamakanga.
Qineghlluni aapsimakanga, “Nagu Taykegergen?”
Taykegergem akisimakanga, “Whaantunga!”
Nayagan pimakanga, “Whangkunnun aglaaqaa!
Ugika vuvallanaquq.”
Llaaghanwha Taykegergen pilugugluni aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Mulunghituq inglunganeng qimugsilghun kaatqusimalghii atungagmeng tapghaghmeng temkagmeng tanpeghhmeng usiluteng.
Taagken tukiita itghuusimakangit.
Vuvallalghiit sivukluteng ilagaamalghiit.
Taaqsata aqelqiit ilagaamalghiit.
Llaaghanwha amiqluggaq keftaghluni nalughqutaghyalghiimi tamaani aqelqat kayaalqiimalghiit.
Taykegergen ugumiyugumalghii.
Taagken pimalghii, “Enta saguyak tagivaghtekek!
Whangallu ilagaqaghlanga!”
Llaaghanwha saguyak tuunumakegket.
Taykegergen kallagsimalghii.
Ilagaatni puygumakanga.
Pimalghii, “Uuk, ilagaatka puywaaqa!
Natungaawalli?”
Nayagan aanqusimakanga.
Liisimakeftaa, “Ayangiyaa, yangiyanga, ayangingii, yangiyaa!”
Taykegergen pimalghii, “Aa, taawa taawa!
Nagu aghulastekaghqaqa teghla?”
Teghlaghllak Taykegergem kaagkaakun nalugumalghii.
Taykegergen aanqusimalghii, “Ayangiyaa, yangiyangaa, ayangingii, yangiyaa!”
Aga tuyegni qapragsimakek.
Ilagaan naangyan qetgeqaamaghmi qalghiimalghii.
Nanevgaat araasimalghiit.
“Taykegergen kayaalqiiguq!”
Taagken Taykegergen pinitun kiyaghsagusimalghii ama aklungighighllagumalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay!
Aghhaghhangaawraq
Iimnanguq, yuget tallimat anglegutkullghiit atalget ama naalget.
Maalghuk mughullutek iilaamalghiik.
Ilanga nunivagmun aghulaqluni iflaamalghii.
Ilanga qayaghtuluni iflaamalghii.
Aminaqumalghii ataasiq Aghhaghhangaawraq.
Maaten ilangani Aghhaghhangaawraq unugmi qayangllaamalghii.
Qayaq taaqluku amiirighpenaan qavaghniyami iteghluni qavaamalghii.
Qavaghluni taghtughyalghiimi nutaan nighuugtaghaghaqeftaa.
Atani taghsasmakanga.
Atanga taghtuumalghii.
Taghtughyan pimakanga, “Qayaghhaqa amiiriqaghhu!”
Atangan yaghlegi qayaa ayemqughtaamakanga.
Aghhaghhangaawraam qayani qiyakumakanga.
Aghhaghhangaawraq uyuqlighpigaq.
Atangan natmun pisqigalkanga, qayughllag’qun ataasighhaaghlleghhii ilangi iflalaghaallghiit.
Aghhaghhangaawraq ellnginaghhaghmi lliilghii.
Maaten ilangani allameng unugyagu qayangllaamalghiil.
Qayaq taaqluku amiirighaa.
Amiirineghmeng taaqluku atami uunghii awataghpagi teglegluki kesimalghii.
Kelluni angwaaghumalghii.
Iiwenllu uyavaghqaaghaquq tagitugughteghllagumakanga.
Ketmun angwaaghumalghii.
Taagken igleghsimalghii.
Tumangani tagitugisimakanga.
Tagitugisaqenni pennaghllak alighumakanga.
Pennam qaayngani yugrukutaaghllak ighugni kulngaghllukek, meghmun itegani nepluki, aqumgaraghaqeftuq.
Yugrukutaaghllagem yuggaq esghaamakanga tuqlumakanga, “Aagyuq tagiighten!”
Yuggaam akitaghsimangisimakanga.
Yugrukutaghllagem pilaataamakanga, “Iiwen evlugughtesleqaqa!”
Yugrukutaaghllagem ighugni aghulasaqegni evlugughsimakanga.
Enkaam yuggaq alingluni yugrukutaaghllagmeng aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni uugsimalghii.
Uugsan yugrukutaaghllagem pimakanga.
“Yeqay iighariighaallutung!”
Yuggaam akisimakanga, “A-aa-aa!”
Yugrukutaaghllagem yuggaq pimakanga, “Enta quneghten!”
Yuggaq quneghsimalghii.
Yugrukutaaghllak neveghsimalghii.
Neveghsan yuggaam ivamakanga.
“Nagu naantaqsin?”
Yuggaq aqsanganun yugrukutaaghllagem uugsimalghii.
Uuglluni tukaamalghii.
Yuggaq pimalghii, “Naqam aqsaasugnitaqaa.”
Yuggaq ukigumalghii.
Iiwenllu ukigaquq, yugrukutaaghllak aqumumalghii.
Pimalghii, “Whaantunga.”
Yuggaam yugrukutaaghllak pimakanga, “Enta quneghten.”
Yugrukutaaghllak quneghsimalghii.
Quneghsan yuggaq yugrukutaaghllagem kaamganun iitghumalghii.
Yugrukutaaghllagem pimakanga, “Yeqay tenguput neghelteki!”
Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakanga “Wiintaku qayaghhaqa tugmaghsaghtuqaghlakun!”
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraq qayaghhaghminun atghaamalghii.
Ellnga tumangani neghsaghtekalghii.
Neghsaghtami tengugi ighneghii nusugumakangi.
Nusugluki atkuni mataghlluku qalighhaagni aallukek atkuni aalluku tafsimalghii.
Tafsiluni neghsam ighneghaghhii qumigumakangi.
Qumigluki taglaamalghii.
Taglaghyan yugrukutaaghllagem pimakanga, “Enta neveghten.”
Yuggaq neveghsimalghii.
Neveghlluni utaqiimalghii.
Yugrukutaaghllagem savini nusugumakanga.
Nusugluku yuggaam aqsanga seggumakanga.
Tengugi aliighsimakangi.
Yuggaam atkugmi ilunganun tenguget qumikaqegkangi.
Yugrukutaaghllagem liigikumangisimakanga.
Yugrukutaaghllak tengugmeng neghumalghii.
Taaqluni yuggaq pimakanga, “Tengugten llangaqa neghsam tengugi.”
Yuggaam pimakanga, “Whangkuta tenguput tawatetut neghsaghpagnitaqut.
Enta elpeklu neveghten!
“Llaaghanwha yugrukutaaghllak neveghsimalghii.
Neveghsan yuggaam savini nusugumakanga.
Yugrukutaaghllagem aqsanga seggumakanga.
Yugrukutaaghllagem ighneghii aliighumalghiit.
Ighsaqghwa kukeghqwaaqeftuq.
Yuggaam ighsaqghwa kenuqaghyaqenni tuqusimakanga yugrukutaaghllak.
Maatenwha meghem evlugughsimangisimakanga.
Tuqusamigu qayaghhaghminun aglaamalghii.
Qayaghhaghminun aglaghluni wata taagavek aghulaqumalghii.
Sukalluni qiighqakun tamlagumalghii.
Tamlagluni qayaghhani sayugumakanga.
Sayugluku uunghaghhani awataghpani tugulaghluki aglaamalghii.
Tumangani eslami nanighhaq kumangalghii esghaamakanga.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghii.
Kiyaghsimaluku nunam asinganeng tughneghaghllak araamaghmi tagimalghii.
Nanighhaghqun tughneghaghllak nughqaghsimalghii.
Aghhaghhangaawraq tuqluumakanga, “Aghhaghhangaawraay, Aghhaghhangaawraay qiluten tagivaghqi sukalluki!”
Aghhaghhangaawraam neghsam qilungi tuunumakangi.
Tughneghaq agitaghsalghiimi talwa qamaverugllak gguteghllak.
Qilut neghluki tughneghaghllak kalefkaghsimalghii.
Kalefkaghlluni allameng nughqaghsimalghii.
Nughqaghsan Aghhaghhangaawraam kemagnat miluusimakangi.
Tughneghaghllak kalefkaghsimalghii allamengnuugumalghii.
Nuugluni Aghhaghhangaawraq tuqluumakanga, “Aghhaghhangaawraay, Aghhaghhangaawraay, ighsaqun tagivaghhu.”
Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakanga, “Sangan, ighsaquqa tuunaanghitaqa!
Ighsaquqa unguvasiqaqa, kiyaghtaaghusiqaqa sumeghtaghaasiqaqa!”
Tughneghaam pimakanga, “Aghhaghhangaawraay,
Aghhaghhangaawraay iiwen neghelleqamken!”
Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakanga, “Agitaghten, agitaghten!”
Aghhaghhangaawraam uunghamineng naghullgumakanga.
Tughneghaghllak kalefkaghsimalghii.
Awataghpagetlu kalefkaghsimalghiit nunamun.
Aghhaghhangaawraam tumangakun maligsimakangi.
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraam malighqaamakangi awataghpaget nuughqaghlluteng kalefkaghtaqluteng.
Suna tughneghaghllak mengteghaghmun itqaghta.
Aghhaghhangaawraam amigem saaghwani utaqamakanga.
Aagramun tughneghaghllak iitghumalghii.
Awataghpaget amigem eslatangani.
Iteghluni tughneghaghllak ngillegsimalghii.
Qama nulighhan aapsimakanga, “Natu aqnighaqa?”
Tughneghaghllagem pimakanga, “Entaqun aqsaquqa agrepemaa.”
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraq ilangitnun mengteghaanun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iightumalghii.
Iteghyalghiimi tughneghaghhagek maalghuk esghaamakek.
Aghnalqwaaghhaak iiyngitalghiik.
Aghnalqwaaghhaak aapsimakangak, “Kaay!
Kinanguzin?”
“Whanganguunga.”
“Kina elpek?”
“Aghhaghhangaawraq.”
“Aaa weni inga umiilegput aqnighaquq aqsamineng.
Langetaq aqfalleqaatnga.”
Nepiighyan Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakanga,
“Sangaawa taana uyaqughpeni kumagllaguyengalghii?”
Aghnalqwaaghem pimakanga, “Enta esghaqaghhu.”
Llaaghanwha Aghhaghhangaawraam takumakanga.
Kaalluku pimakanga, “Enta qeteghten!”
Aghnalqwaaq qeteghsimalghii.
Qeteghsan Aghhaghhangaawraam ighsalqagkenkun nunughyaqenni aghnalqwaaghhaq tuqusimakanga.
Tuqusamigu amiiraghhaa qapiimakanga.
Qapighyamigu Aghhaghhangaawraam aasimakanga.
Aalluku ellngatun qiipimsugumalghii ilagaamalghii.
Ilagaamaluku yuuk qineghsimalghii.
Pimalghii, “Naagu taana aghnalqwaaq?”
Aghhaghhangaawraam akisimakanga, “Taawa!”
Yugem pimakanga, “Aqfaamken.
Umiilegput inga aqnighaquq.
Aglaqaa.”
“Aglaghnayaghtunga taawanginaq kayatepigtunga.”
“Amaghlaken.”
“Aa-a!”
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraq nekevumalghii.
Nekevyan yugem amaamakanga.
Amaghyaqenni uqigtuftuq.
Yugem aapsimakanga, “Sangavek uqigtughqaagaten?”
“Qayughllak qugilighllalghiinga, saama alignam.”
Yugem kaatusimakanga mengteghaghllagmun.
Itghusimakanga.
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraam tukuni pimakangi, “Aghnami whani enta qaagna kelgughhu.
Qamaglluni taghnughhaqulluni tagilaghalli.”
Llaaghanwha aghnam kelgughaa qamaglluku.
“Taawaa qamagtaqa.”
Aghhaghhangaawraam aqnilghii esghaghyaqenni qaanghani uunghaq ama aneghtaqeftuq keneghmeng.
Mulunghituq qamaglluteng nunalgutangit tagilaghaasimalghiit.
Taagken iteghaatut nanevgaqulluteng aghnalqwaaqulluteng taghnughhaqulluteng leganqun qamaglluteng nunalgutangit.
Aghhaghhanaawraampimakangi, “Entananiqqaamteggu.”
Llaaghanwha aghnam naniq qaamlluku nateghmun ateghsimakanga.
Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakangi, “Enta kayusightengnga.
Kina ilagaatelek ilagaatmineng ilagaghli.
Iiwen ilagaatangilnguq temngi araghli.
Iiwen aanquskuma aanqullghasi.”
Taagken Aghhaghhangaawraq ilagaatmeng aanqutuq.
Tamana ellmeng ilagaatmeggneng aanqutuq.
Ilagaatangilnguq araateghllagtuq.
Araasimaluki Aghhaghhaawraam tughneghaq aqnilghii kenuqaghyaqenni tuqusimakanga.
Tuqusamigu uunghani nusugumakanga.
Nusugluku aanqaghsimalghii eslatmun.
Aanqaghlluni taagken qimagumalghii.
Tughneghaat nepiighaghtaasimalghiit.
Nepiighaghtaasata tughneghaam nulighhan naniq itghusimakanga.
Itghulluku kumaghsimakanga.
Ugini esghaghyaqenni tuqumalghii.
Anqaghlluteng Aghhaghhangawraq malighqaamakangat.
Pimakangat, “iitegʼun kaaskumken neghelleqegkemken.
Sangavek iqlengiqumazin?”
Iwemga Aghhaghhangaawraam unisimakangi.
Qayaghhani aliighumakanga, pimakanga, “Qayaghhaq, qayaghhaq meghmun piiften!”
Llaaghanwha qayaghhaq meghmun piifsimalghii.
Aghhaghhangaawraq qayaminun kaatuq.
Uuglluni ketuq.
Taagken tughneghaat esnamun kaatquusimalghiit.
Tughneghaat meghmun ateyiilnguut.
Ataasim tughneghaam meq meghumakanga.
Meghyaqenni Aghhaghhangaawraq tugneghaam qaanghanun tagimalghii.
Aghhaghhangaawraam qayaminilnguq tepluggaq tuguluku meq anagutaghyaqenni meq uteghsimalghii.
Llaaghanwha tughneghaam tugumangisimakanga.
Taagken nunamun aglaamalghii.
Tamlagluni qayani sayugumakanga.
Sayugluku mengteghaminun taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghluni angayuqagni esghaamakek.
Qagughmigullutek aqumgaaqeftuk.
Atangan pimakanga, “Qenwat tuquniluten piiqamken.”
Aghhaghhangaawraam pimakanga, “Nakaa, entaqun anglegutenka nalluutmeggneng tuqulaghaasimaat.
Maaten whanga uyavanun aghulaqeghngaaghma kitum tuqunnaanghitaanga.
Whanga nanevgaghlunga tuqullequnga.”
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Ungipaghaan Qigighhmiik
Iimnanguq, Qigighhmiik mekelghiighhaqlu aghnaghaghhaqlu anglegutkullghiikyaywaalingiighhaak.
Qigightaq mengteghaghtupiglleghhii.
Ama umiilelget.
Umiilgat aghvengyupiglleghhii.
Awen iiwleng aghvengaqelghiit.
Aghvengenghaani mekelghiighhaqlu aghnaghaghhaqlu esnamun atghaghaghaqelghiik.
Kaanneghata umiilgem uqumun siingwaaghataghaqegkek.
Llaaghanwha avangunatek taglaamaqelghiik taawanginaq mesiighmun angighullutek.
Wetku umiilek mengteghamun taglanghani esnamun yaywaalingiighhaak atghaamaqelghiik.
Kaanneghmeggni pilakameng mangtagmeng ikuqusimaaqelghiik ama kemekragmeng.
Taglaghlutek kaanneghmeggni nutaanneghumaaqelghiik.
Ilangani mekelghiighhaq aanenghani umiilgem siingwaaghataamaqegkanga.
Taagken tawani kiyaghsimalghiik.
Maaten ilangani mekelghiighhaq pimalghii, “Maantekumtung tuqulleqiinkung.
Upupeng qayangllaghlutung aghulaqelqung.”
Llaaghanwha nayagan aanghumakanga.
Taagken mekelghiighhaq qayangllaamalghii maalghugegneng paaskelghiineng.
Qayaq taaqsamigu tanpeghhaghhaghmeng qemgughtilutek nayakullghiik ilaghtuusimakangat.
Taaqsamegteki qayaghteng amiimakangat.
Qayaghrukutaaghllak maalghugegneng paaskelghii taaqumakanagt.
Mekelghiighhaamnayaggani pimakanga, “Wiin maani ataasimeng qavaaltung.
Unaami unanguluku mengteghaghput naafqelluku kellghakung.”
Nayagan aangghumakanga.
Unugyagu neghumalghiik.
Neneghmeng taaqlutek ingaghquullutek qavaasimalghiik.
Taagken unaami taghtughyamek mengteghaghteng naafqumakanat.
Unangupiglluku kesimalghiik.
Ukiivagem tunganganun angwaaghumalghiik aghnelqusiq.
Unugyagu qayaghteng maghqaalluku qavaamalghiik.
Unaami taghtughyamek qayaghteng qalpeghlluku angwaaghumalghiik Ukiivagmun.
Meghnughyamek qayaghteng uyghighluku angyataghquumalghiik.
Taagken neghumalghiik Neneghmeng taaqlutek aghnaghaghhaam uyughani atuusimakanga.
Mekelghiighhaq qayamini nalughqutaamalghii.
Meghnunghyami nayani pimakanga, “Enta ataasimeng angwaagheltung.”
Nayagan aangghumakanga.
Llaaghanwha angwaaghtuk.
Unugyagu uyghighlaataghtuk.
Uyghighlutek qayaghteng maghqaalluku qavaamalghiik.
Unaami taghtuneghmegni angwaaghaqelghiik aghnelqusiq.
Aghneghem qukaghyagu mekelghiighhaam nayani pilaataghaa, “Enta negheltung!”
Llaaghanwha aghuliighlutek qayaghtek uyghighluku neghtuk.
Taaqsamek nayani pilaataghaa, “Enta ataasimeng atuutinga, aghulanaqunga.”
Llaaghanwha atuulluku nayagan mekelghiighhaq aghulamalghii.
Meghnughyami taaqluni nayani pimakanga, “Enta uyghin amugu.
Angwaagheltung!”
Nayagan uyghin amumakanga, enkaam angwaaghtuk.
Iiwenllu unugyaghtughaqaa nuna aliighumakangat.
Taagken takumakangat.
Sukalluni nuna anglimalghii.
Taagken tamlagumalghiik.
Arekull Ukiivagmun kaataqeftuk.
Quutmun uglleghaasimalghiik.
Qayaghteng sayugumakangak.
Sayugluku aawghsimakangak.
Mengteghanun taglaamalghiik.
Sivulighpigaghteggun kaasimalghiik.
Iteghaasamekmekelghiighhaq qiighwumalghii.
Aghnaq ineqsunaghllalghii aagrameng nuugumalghii.
Aleghqughyalghiimi qaghitumraagllaguftuq, “Kaaay, saam taghnughhaqistek?
Maani aviitusi!”
Mekelghiighhaam akisimakanga, “Qigighhmiinguukung.”
“Aa, sakun tagistek?”
“Qayakun tagikung.
Qayughllaknunamnni seghletun kiyaghlleghhiikung, enngaatall umiilegput seghlepiguuq, naqam aghvengyupigtuq.
Aghvengenghani esnamun atghanemtung neqmun ama uqumun siingvagataghaqiinkung.
Llaaghanwha avangunaamtung taglaghaqukung mengteghamnnun.
Kaannemtung sameng negheltung.
Taawanginaq igataghlutung kiyaghtaqelghiikung.
Wetku umiilek taglanghani itagnatun esnamun atghaghaqelghiikung.
Pilakameng ikuqutaqelghiikung.
Enkaam taglaghaqelghiikung.
Taglanemtung wetku neghaqelghiikung.
Enkaamam tamaken ukavek tagikung tuqunnayukanginkung.”
Aghnaghllak qiyamalghii, enkaampimalghii, “Waranwha avaqutaqelleqamtek.
Qamavek aagramun iteghtek.
Asangsi ugika tagikuni qevuulluni quyallequq.”
Iteghasimalghiik aagramun.
Aghnam ugimineng utaqiitkelluku neqlightuumakek.
Neghumalukek sama uginga kavleguusimalghii.
Aghnam qelamakanga, “Av?”
“Whaantunga.”
Yuuk iitghumalghii.
Tawani taghnughhaghhaak esghapagumakek.
Yaghlegi nuliini aapsimakanga, “Saam ukuk taghnughhaqakek?”
Nulighhan akisimakanga, “Entaqun elpeneng aaptaghtikek.”
Llaaghanwha yugem aapsimakek, “Saam taghnughhaqistek” Mekelghiighhaam akisimakanga, “Qigighhmiinguukung, yaywaalinguukung, atangitukung, naangitukung.
Ukavek tukughqaghhalegnun ivaghingukung nani inqun pinitun kiyaghhnalutung.
Qayughllak nunamnni seghletun kiyaghlleghhiikung.
Umiilegput enngaatall seghlepiguuq.”
Yugem aapsimakanga, “Naten kiyaghtaqa?”
“Aghvengenghani esnamun atghanemtung neqmun mesiighmun siingwaaghataghaqiinkung.
Llaaghanwha avangunamtung taglaghaqukung.
Umiilek wetku taglanghani itagnatun esnamun atghaghaqukung.
Atghanemtung pilakameng ikuqullutung taglaghaqukung.
Taglanemtung wetku tawani neghaqukung.
Aanʼgiimalutungllu umiilgem esghaneghminikung siingwaaghataghaqiinkung.
Qenwat tuqunnayukanginkung tagiikung.”
Nepiighyan yuuklu nulighqullghiik qiyaghusimalghiik.
Yugem aaplataghii, “Atatangistek ama asagistek?”
“Avangitukung.
Taawanginaq nunalgutetukung, allanguut.”
Yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Enta waranwha avaqutangukut.
Elpek angayuqaghten aqfaki!”
Nulighhan aangghumakanga.
Taagken nulighha pilugugumalghii, aanluni angayuqaminun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni pimakangi, “Ugima aglaqiisqiisi, inqun ungipaghaghyaghtiisqellusi.”
Nanevgaam akisimakanga, “Aa, aglaghnaqukut.”
Aghnaq aanluni aglaamalghii mengteghameggnun.
Iteghyan ugingan aapsimakanga, “Qayugham?”
“Qaywa, taginaqut.”
Aghnaq amsikaghsimalghii.
Mulunghituk nanevgaghhavaklu aghnalqwaaghllaklu iteghaasimalghiik.
Iteghaasata yugem pimakangi, “Whanga tuqlughaqamsi inqun ungipaghiisqellusi.
Qigighhmiik kaasimaak taghnughhaak naangilnguuk, atangilnguuk.
Enngaatall pellaghyuglutek aqumgalghiik.”
Nanevgaghllak pimalghii, “Enta, ungipaghaghlanga.
Iimnanguq, ukuk taghnughhaghhaak naangit atangit whanga uyvalaluki tuququmaanka.
Tefaay!”
Enkaam nanevgaghllaklu aghnalqwaaghllaklu aanleghaasimalghiik.
Yaghlegi mekelghiighhaqlu aghnaghaghhaqlu milegpagtaasimalghiik.
Yugemnuliini pimakanga, “Awimam angayuqagken nangllekelleqegketen.”
Aghnam akisimakanga, “Whanga iitek angayuqanka nanglleknaanghitanka.
Talwa sangighhaghmeng mekestaaghhaaluku tuunaanghitanka.
Elpek awituwaq sakiten nangllekelleqegketen?”
Yugem pimakanga, “Asangsi whanga nanglleknaanghitanka!”
Nuliini pilataghaa, “Enta whanga angayuqanka aqfaaghtiki.
Tagighllinnguq ungipaghaghyaghtughlit.
Aqelqatnagasugtut.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq pilugugluni aanuq.
Ugimi angayuqaanun aglaamalghii.
Iteghluni ugimi angayuqakek ungipaasimakek, “Ugima aqfasqiisi aglaqaghtegnguq ungipaghaghyaghtughtek.”
Nanevgaghhaqlu aghnaghlqwaaghllaklu aangghumalghii, “Qaywa qaywa aglaghnaqukung!”
Aglaghyan aghnaq ugingan aapsimakanga, “Qayugham?”
“Taginaquk.”
Aghnaq amsikaghsimalghii.
Mulunghituq aghnalqwaaghhaqlu nanevgaghhaqlu iteghaasimalghiik.
Yugek pisimalghiik, “Whanga aqfastaqamsi inqun aqelqak pellaghyulghiik ungipaghaatesqellukek.
Nuliighma angayuqakek tagiyaghtuk.
Nanevgaghllagem yaghlegi taghnughhaghhaak milegmiqaak.
Ellngannguq uyvalalukek tuququmaftaak angayuqakek.”
Yuuk nepiighyan nanevgaghllak pimalghii, “Enta ungipaghaghlanga.”
“Iimnanguq, Nunataghmiit mengteghat malghugneghhaat.
Ataasimi mengteghami kiyaghlleghhiik yuuklu aghnaqlu nulighqutiinalghiik.
Ilangani mengteghani kiyaghlleghhiik aghnalqwaaghhaqlu mekelghiighhaqlu nengyuqullghiik eltughaqullghiik.
Yuuk unangyupiglleghii.
Naqam neqenneghmini aghnalqwaaghhaq neqmeng awalighaqegkanga.
Enngaatall aghnalwaaghhaqlu mekelghiighhaqlu pinitun yugem kiyaghtesimakek.
Maaten ilangani aghnalqwaaghhaq sumeghtaghaamalghii.
Eltughaghhani pimakanga, ‘Aqnighyaquma!’ Eltughaghhaan aapsimakanga ‘Sangavek?’ ‘Qayughllak unguvaneghmeng qinuyagutunga.
Qemall aqnighlunga tuquyaquma aghnaq iigna aqfanayaghan enkaam ughvughqennayaghanga.
Ughvughqinamalunga iiggaaneng taagken iflanayaghtunga.
Qemall aghnakun taginayaghtunga mekelghiighhaalunga.’ ‘Neghepigesnaghnaluten!’ Aghnalqwaaghhaam akisimakanga, ‘Qayughllakkiyaghhneghmeng qinuyagutunga!’ Nepiighluni aqniimalghii.
Aqniimalghi, aqniimalghii.
Maalghugegneng qavaghluni aghnalqwaaghhaq tuqumalghii.
Tuquyan mekelghiighhaam aghnaq aqfayaghtuumakanga.
Aanluni aglaamalghii nunalgutminun.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aagrameng aghnaq nuugumalghii.
Aapsimakanga mekelghiighhaq, ‘Saqwaaghsin?’
‘Nengyughhaqa tuqumaaq, inqun ughvughqaghtesqelluku aqfaamken.’
Aghnam pimakanga, ‘Qaywa aglaghnaqunga, utaqanga!’
Enkaam aglaamalghiik mengteghamun.
Taagken aghnalqwaaghhaq aghnam ughvughqumakanga.
Aghnalqwaaghhaq aghnam iiggaaneng kuuvumalghii.
Aghnam wata ughvughqumakanga.
Aghnalqwaaghhaq qenwat iiggestun angkaliightuq.
Taawa aghnam ughvughqaa.
Qenwat aghnalqwaaghhaq iiggaaneng iflaaq.
Iflayan aghnam signeghek kuuvyaghtuumakek.
Kuuvlukek mekelghiighhaghmun tuunumakek.
Aghnaq aglaamalghii mengteghameggnun.
Kaalluni iiteghluni uginga puuru aanluni mekelghiighhaam mengteghaanun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Taagken yugem mekelghiighhaq pimakanga, ‘Mengteghan naafqelluku whangkunnun aglaa.’ Mekelghiiq yugem pillghaatun pimalghii.
Mulunghituq yugem nulighha aqsangumalghii.
Ighniyalghiimi mekelghiighhaghmeng.
Aghnam atiimakanga Aghnalqwaaghmeng.
Mekelghiighhaq qavaghhinaghqun angliiq.
Qenwat mekelghiighhaq aaghwtuq.
Qavaghluteng taghtughyalghiimeng mekelghiighhaq piyugyaaghsimalghii.
Allameng qavaghluteng taghtughyalghiimeng mekelghiighhaq akuziyagusimalghii.
Mekelghiighhaq sukalluni angliiq.
Aatgha Aghnalqwaaq.
Qenwat qawaagsagutuq.
Yaywaalingiighhaankuk taamllu yugem ighnegha mughutaqelghiik.
Mughunneghmegni unangaqelghiik.
Llaaghanwha mekelghiighhaak ivaghiniightengughtuk.
Puuru yuuk mughunnanightuq.
Ama pinitun kiyaghsagusimalghiit.
Tefaay!
Taawa ungipaghaghtunga.”
Nanevgaq ungipaghaneghmeng taaqsan yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Enta neghelta!
Neqnilghiimeng neqmeng itghuten!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq neqmeng neqnilghiimeng allaghhinaghmeng itghusimalghii.
Taagken neghumalghiit.
Neneghmeng taaqsata aghnalghwaaghhaqlu nanevgaghhaqlu aanleghaasimalghiik.
Aglaamalghiikmengteghameggnun.
Unugyagu aghnam allighat saagsimakangi.
Ingaghquulluteng qavaasimalghiit.
Unaami taghtughyamengaghnamkalngani itghusimakanga.
Itghusamigupiluguget maalghugneghet nusugumakangi ilangi agham pilugugi, ilangi yugem pilugugi.
Taagken mekelghiighhaqlu aghnaghaghhaqlu pilugugluni aanumalghiik.
Enngaatall yaywaalingiighhaak pinitun lliightuk ama anglimalghiik.
Angliyata yugem mekelghiighhaq aghnaghaghmeng ineqsunapiglleghhiimeng nulightughtesimakanga.
Aghnaghaq yuukegtepiglleghhiimeng ugiightesimakanga.
Taawa piitim kiyaghsagusimalghiit.
Qamagtuq Tefaay!
Ungipaghaan Yaqellengetaq
Iimnanguq yaqellengetaak naakullghiik.
Nunam asinganilnguuk yugestun ayuqelghiik.
Ighnegha alignalghii.
Aghneq tamaghhaan ilagaghaqelghii.
Ilaganeghmeng taaqneghmini aneghtaqelghii, “Iiyhii-hii-hi-hiiy, Tengagergentuq (1) nulighhighyaghtuqegka!”
Naangan akisimakanga, “Tengagergen aangeghllagtuq nagaqughlleqaaten.
Nepiighi!
Ellngan ulimaaqiinkut whangkuta.
Naagumi ikiwan qaaynganilnguum nateghqameggnun angighhutaqegkanginkut.”
Ighneghan akisimakanga, “Gaymaangi nuliighhighnaqaqa.”
Ayumiq aapghaqaat angeghllalghii ighaleqetaaghllak aghtaghaam tunganganilnguq aatgha Tengagergen.
Ayumiq waamseghaghtet yuguniiqaat.
Whangkutanguq Tengagergem ulimaaqeftiinkut.
Maaten ilangani yaqellengetaq aanluni mengtegham saaghwani vegtaamalghii.
Vegtaghluni vegaaghet ratamiiragnekun qantaghluki itghusimakangi.
Itghulluki piighhumakangi.
Apeghiighyamiki akmagumakangi.
Akmagluki aghulaqumsimakangi.
Tengagergemun mayuumalghii.
Mayuumalghii mayuumalghii mayuumalghii.
Payegnun kaasimalghii.
Kaalluni uugsimalghii.
Uugsalghiimi mengteghat esghaamakangi.
Esghaghluki takumakangi.
Taagken kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Aagram ilanganeng aapsimakangat, “Kinangaawa?”
Yaqellengetaam akisimakangi, “Whangangunga.”
“Kina elpek?”
“Yaqellengetaq.”
Tengagergem aapsimakanga, “Saquzin?”
Yaqellengetaam pimakanga, “Nulighhighyaghtughamken!”
“Ukaku nalleghiituten!
Enta iitghi!”
Llaaghanwha yaqellengetaq iitghumalghii.
Tengagergemnulighqekmaalghuguftuk, ataasiq unugempaniga, ilanga siqinghem paniga.
Yaqellengetaq siqinghem panigan saaghwanun ineqsunallghakun aqumumalghii.
Tengagergem nuliini pimakanga, “Enta ugikaghqan neqlightughhu!”
Siqinghem paniga sagleghegneng tugulluni nateghmun aatghumalghii.
Aghnaq siinumi kavlegtaghtuq.
Kavlegtaghluni iteghtuq.
Iteghluni sagneghek kanaghtaak.
“Taawa sagneghek.”
Yaqellengetaam sagneghek esghaghyaqegni melngumeng imaqefuk.
Yaqellengetaam tugulukek meghumakek.
Taagken Tengagergen ilagaghnaqumalghii.
Unugyagu naniq awisimakanga.
Taagken Tengagergen ilagaamalghii.
Tughneghani qagit tuqluumakangi.
Tughneghii qagit tagimalghiit.
Kaalluteng amigkun iitghumalghiit.
Aagrangat meghughteghllagumalghii.
Taagken aanumalghiit.
Aanyata Tengagergen pimalghii, “Enta nighugutaghtek.
Imatuqlu yaqellengetaam yaqukek nevuutakek.”
Llaaghanwha nighugusimalghiit.
Yaqellengetaq qavaghaqeftuq.
Taagken ilagaghlaataghtuq.
Tughneghani nanuq tuqluumakanga.
Tagiyalghiimi aglukek mengqughtaamalghiik.
Mengqughtaghlutek nanuq aanumalghii.
Tengagergen pilaataghtuq, “Allameng kumaqaghtek.”
Kumaghsalghiimeng yaqellengetaq qavaghaqeftuq, nanuum neghumangisimakanga.
Taagken yaqellengetaq aqumumalghii ama pimalghii, “Enta whangallu ilagaqaghlanga.”
Taagken allameng kumaghsalghiimeng Tengagergen pilugugaqeftuq.
Yaqellengetaqlu pilugugumalghii.
Taagken Tengagergen aanumalghii.
Aanyan yaqellengetaam siqinghem paniga pilugugesqumakanga.
Taagken aanumalghiik.
Yaqellengetaam siqinghem paniga payegnun aglaasimakanga.
Kaatulluku vegaaghmeng piighhamineng uyatiimakanga.
Asitmun ukigsimakanga.
Taagken ellngallu ukigumalghii.
Taagken yaqellengetaq nulightughtuq.
Taagken qavaamalghiit.
Unanguluku taghtuumalghiit.
Yaqellengetaq pimalghii, “Tengagergen nuliilegnun taginaquq.”
Taagken neghumalghiit.
Neneghmeng taaqluteng yaqellengetaq aanumalghii eslamun.
Aanluni anigu aghnangllaamakanga.
Aghnaq taaqluku siinumun kanaghsimakanga.
Pimakanga, “Iiwen Tengagergen tagikan tuqluqumken neqmeng itghullghaaten.”
Llaaghanwha Tengagergen ukigumalghii.
Ukigluni yaqellengetaghmun kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aapsimakangat, “Kinangaawa?”
Tengagergem akisimakanga, “Whangangunga.”
Yaqellengetaam aapsimakanga, “Kina elpek?”
“Tengagergen!”
“Iitqaalten!”
Taagken Tengagergen iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan yaqellengetaq pimalghii, “Saamyuq neqmeng tagiten!”
Llaaghanwha anigu aghnaq neqmeng iitghusimalghii.
Taagken neghumalghiit.
Tengagergem aghnaq esghayaqenni nuliighmineng pinighataghalghii.
Yaqellengetaampimakanga, “Nulighhen aglaasunghiisaquvgu nayaka tugunayaghan.
Iiwen nulighhen aglaasukuvgu aglaatigu umyugaghpetun.”
Llaaghanwha Tengagergem anigukuvinghaq aghnaq aglaannaqaa.
Neneghmeng taaqluteng Tengagergem anigukuvinghaq aghnaq aglaasimakanga.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay!
Vuvallanga Ayapeghyugem
Vuvallam sanqutangi sivuliq qalik, signeghet, qaltaghwaaghek, aghqusighhaak tughneghaghnun, saguyak, tagnelghii nanighhaq kumangalghii.
Vuvallam yuga unanguluku pingayumi kellaagegni nekegtaqaat vuvalla.
Taaqneghmegteggu vuvallam yuga aanaquq eslamun.
Kiyaghtalleghmun kelgutaquq mumeghmeng tugumiighluni nalighmeng aquutameng.
Araghaquq, “Wu-huu-huu-huu-uu, wu-huu-huu-huu-uu, wu-huu-uu, wu-huu-uu!”
Taagken vuvallam yuga aatghaquq nateghmun.
Nuliini piiqaa, “Enta saguyagka tagivaghqek!”
Nulighhan tuunaqaak.
Kaagtuusimagkenka uzivaquq ilagaghaquq uzivutkelluku.
Ilaganeghmeng taaqneghmini mekelghiighhaat piiqii, “Qaagna nanevgaq ungipaaqughteggu.
Legan whaten pinakesi, ‘Wu-wuu-u-huu-uu, wu-wu-u-huu-uu, neghsaghyaghiitusi, pugneghyaghiitusi, iqallugyaghiitusi, tengugyaghiitusi, akutaghyaghiitusi.
Ayapeghyuk vuvallaaq.”
Llaaghanwha mekelghiighhaat aviiyaghtughaqut mengteghanun tamaghhanun nanevgaat aghnalqwaaghet.
Aaptaqiit, “Navek?”
Piiqut, “Ayapeghyugmun!”
Nanevgaat aglaghtuutaqut vuvallalghiinun neghnaluteng qetustaaghhaghmeng.
Tawani ungipamsugutaqut ungipaghaataqut kayalqiiraaghutaqut saama ilagaataqut vuvallamaluki allanun neqmeng sanqutaaghmeng tuuninaanghilnguut.
Aghtaghanghagu nanevgaat aanleghaataqut aghnalqwaaghet unegtaqut.
Vuvallalghiit ateghaataqut nateghmun aghnalqwaaghetlu iiwen kinkut tawavek ilatkat.
Ilannaqneghmeggni mengteghameggneng tugutaqut tawaqameng allaghhiinaghmeng neqmeng ivalumeng inqun vuvallalghiit mengteghiit qilleghfiknaluki.
Unanguluku ungipaghaataqut ungipamsugutaqut ilagaataqut neghutaqut siqinghem piitellghanun kenlenganun.
Siqineq piinneghani nanevgaat aanleghaataqut aghnalqwaaghet unegtaqut.
Nateghmun ateghaataqut aghnalqwaaghetlu vuvallalghiitlu.
Ateghaanneghmeggni quyngiiraateng tugulaghaqiit allaghhiinaghmeng neqmeng ikuquutaqut.
Eslamun aanaqneghmeggni quyngiiraateng llivikughaqiit.
Aanleghaalluteng miluqutaghaqut tughneghaghnun kiyaghtaalleghmun meghem yuganun.
Taqneghmeggni iteghaataqut.
Iteghalluteng aghnalqwaaghet uyegtaqii ataasim aghnalqwaaghem.
Taaqneghatki vuvallaleknuliighminun saguyagni tungsighaqaak.
Nulighhan saguyak tuunaqaak.
Vuvallalegtaq uzivaquq.
Iiwen vuvallayaghtuqat iiwen avaqutii.
Ellnga vuvallalegtaq saguyagtuumaghmi uzivaquq.
Nanevgaam ilagaataqaa utuqameng ilagaatameng.
Vuvallalegtaq aviigaquq, “Wuhuuuu, wuhuuuu, wuhuuuu!”
Ilagaan naangenghani uzivelghiit aghuliighaqut.
Aghuliinghata vuvallalegtam kallagutaqii.
Aghnat putuughutaqut iiwen kitum atanga naten piiqa yuga.
Taana aghulasiqaqaat.
Qamagtuq.
Tungtughllak Enkaam Kavengenghaghhaq
Iimnanguq, tungtughllak esnamun piyaamalghii.
Esghaamakanga kayengenghaghhaq.
Kayengenghaghhaamaghivamakanga, “Tungtu paagna aqsavalluq, tungtu paagna sighuneghpalluq, ighukek amestaghhaak, tallikek amestaghhaak.”
Tungtughllagem pimakanga, “Kayengenghaghhaay, kayengenghaaghhaay ukapighqaaghi!
Whanga nagaqunghitunga.”
Kayengeghaghhaq ukapighqaaghumalghii.
Tungtughllagem ipugaghsimakanga sighuneghmineng enkaam eglleghsimakanga esnamun.
Kayengenghaghhaq araamalghii, “Uvinka tukrugtaa, papasquqa tukrugtaa, qaanqa tukrugtaa, metengtanka tukrugtii!”
Itagnatun tungtughllagem kayengenghaghhaq meghmun ateghsimakanga.
Kayengenghaghhaam tungtughllak aghivalaataghaa, “Tungtu paagna aqsavalluq, tungtu paagna sighuneghpalluq, ighukek amestaghhaak, tallikek amestaghhaak.”
Tungtughllagem pilataghaa, “Kayengenghaghhaay, kayengenghaaghhaay ukapighqaaghi!
Whanga nagaqunghitunga.”
Kayengeghaghhaq ukapighqaaghumalghii.
Tungtughllagem ipugaghsimakanga sighuneghmineng enkaam eglleghsimakanga esnamun.
Kayengenghaghhaq araghlaataamalghii, “Uvinka tukrugtaa, papasquqa tukrugtaa qaanqa tukrugtaa, metengtanka tukrugtii!”
Tuqumalghii tukruughqwaayaqenni.
Tukruughq waayan tungtughllagem neghumakanga.
Tungtughllak pimalghii, “Kayengenghaghhaq taana neqnirkapiggaq.”
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Nunameng Uzivikaq Paallghunkuk Ama Qetngalleghyankuk
Iimnanguq, kiyaghsimaaq kumak umiilek qamarilakayuk.
Ilangani kiigem kumagem nunalgutni pimakangi paallghunkut, qetngalleghyankut apayepayiighenkut ama melngunkut.
Pimakangi, “Qamarilanaqunga!
Qemgughutek!”
Llaaghanwha aglaghtuusimalghiit kumagem mengteghaan saaghwanun.
Taagken qamarilam ayaviigha kingutalek napaghsimakanga.
Kumagem pimakangi, “Elpetek qetngalleghyaqlu paallghullu nuna uziviteggu.
Elpetek melngullu apayepayiiqlu naayghaq uziviteggu!”
Llaaghanwha aga kilgaquusimalghiik qetngalleghyankuk paallghunkuk.
Pengughqameng talughsamek meghnaalimalghiik.
Meghnaaliyamek taana pengughqaq uzivluku tagimalghiik.
Legan kaasamek aneghsimalghiik pekaghniqutek.
Apayepayiighenkuk melngunkuk uzivumakangat naayghaq.
Qesiqun paallghunkuk qetngalleghyankuk uyghalqusighhaq uzivumakangat.
Ama apayepayiighenkuk melngunkuk uzivumakangat uyghagrukutaaghllak.
Llaaghanwha kumagem paallghu tuunumakanga avaqutami atkuganeng qatelghiimeng, enraq qetngalleghyaq tuunumakanga ayaviighmeng.
Apayepayiiq tuunumakanga negaghpagmeng enraq melngu aghyuughumakanga sumeghneqluku.
Ellnga kumak aklungimsuggiighusimalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Tungtu Aqanga
Iimnanguq, kiyaghsimaaq aghnaaneq tungtu.
Maaten ilangani ighninaqumalghii.
Ighninaqumaluku amaaghllagek maalghuk kaasimalghiik.
Amaaghllagem aallghan aleni pimakanga, “Yeqay una tuqutelteggu!”
Legan pimakanga, “Wiin ighniighlli!”
Llaaghanwha ighnimalghii.
Ighniyan aghnaq taana tungtu tuqulluku neghumakangat qamaglluku.
Qamagsatgu aallghan aleni pimakanga, “Yeqay una taghnughhaa tuqulluku neghelteggu!”
Aallghan aleni pimakanga, “Wiin wetku anglikan neghnakefut.
Salin maaten kemgituq.”
Atimaftaat Aqangameng.
Taagken aga tungtuquyaamalghiik amaak taakuk.
Aga taluqaghsaagta Aqangangiighhaq nekevluni tana naayghaq mayuumakanga pegnem.
Qaygeghsamigu ukigluni inglunganun mayuumalghii.
Tawaten aghnelqusiq ulapumalghii.
Nasiqulluku tagiyaghqaaghhneghan nemineng aglaghluni ungleghumalghii.
Iiwenllu palaghhaghmeng kiyaqaatangaa tagimalghhk amaak taakuk.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghiik.
Aghneqwaaqun aghulaqenghegkeni ulapaqelghii.
Tawaten kiyaghsimalghiik amaak ama taanallu tungtu tawaten kiyaghsimalghii.
Qenwat anglighllagumalghii.
Aallghan amaam aleni pimakanga, “Yeqay una tuqulluku neghelteggu!”
Aallghan aangghumakanga.
Iwemga Aqangam pimakangi, “Egyugtusi.
Wiin whangallu nanghiiqwaaghtengnga kayaalqiiraaghmeng.”
Taagken Aqangayeng amaak malighqughtaamakangak.
Sivukluni Aqanga temngi nalumsimeng qimagumalghii.
Qaygeghsami ukigluni naaygham inglunganun tawaten qimagumalghii.
Amaak malighquneghmeng pekaghllaglutek aghuliighusimakangat.
Ilanga amaa pimalghii, “Taamengwha Aqanga qugilingigatuq!”
Taagken ilangan pimakanga, “Tawa ellnga alla kitum qinuyuggnaanghitaa!”
Aqanga tawani kiyaghsimalghii.
Uksumi ilangani teghigaq tamagghaghmi qemguumalghii Aqanga naanghiighnaluku.
Legan kaynget piiqsaqangat.
Aqangam sighuneghmineng egsimaaqegkangi.
Tamana teghigaq qamaglluku tuququmakanga.
Ungleghtaghaqelghii.
Legan kaynget esghaghluku temngi quyngiiniluku takwaaqsaqangat.
Liigikneghmegteggu negughaqegkangat aleghquumaghmeng, “Aqangangiighhaq qavaghsighaghaqelghii.”
Aqanga miiwenllu qavaghaqelghii.
Qamagtuq Tefaay.
Mekelghiighhaak Iikusimaak
Kiyaghsimaaq Ungazimi aghnaq ugilek enkaam taghnughhallgaak.
Ilangani ugingighaamalghii.
Sighinegmiim yugem nulighhilnguum nagaqughluku Ungazimun tagimalghii.
Kaasami aghnaq tugumakanga.
Llaaghanwha Sighinegmun aghviisimakanga.
Naqam taana Sighinegmii yuuk aklungilnguq.
Kaasami taakuk mekelghiighhaak atangan ighlekaqegkek piiqegkek, “Qaagkut amyuqetaghllagtut.
Amyuutkelleqiisi.”
Llaaghanwha aaneghmegni naayghanun aghulaqaqelghiik.
Tespagani ulapumalghnk inqun iknaqughinalutek.
Atangita waamsimakek ighneghegni inqun iknaqughisqellukek.
Llaaghanwha iknaqughimalghiik saama anglimalghiik.
Ilangani uksum unanguluku tungtuquyaamalghiik.
Tagiyamek nagneghlutek esavghaallghiinun maligusimalghiik.
Tamana yuuk naghughqughluku awalighpigaalutek ketfaghaqelghiik.
Llaaghanwha ayveghaghlutek taglaghaqelghiik.
Tamana taglaghtuullghii naghughqughluku kaataqelghiit mengteghameggnun.
Tawaten kiyaghsimalghiit uksulqusiq.
Ilangani unanguluku tungtuquyaasimalghiik.
Tungtunglutek atghaamalghiik aghneghtughllagluku.
Kaasamek tungtukegkateng lliluki nagneghlutek yuuk tamana maliglluku esavghaamalghiik.
Naqam atangita piiqsaqangit inqun awalightaghwaaghpenaki pisqelluki.
Taagken aaghtuumalghiik taanʼgani.
Tamana ilanga ayveghaghluni qamaglluni taglaghtuusimalghii.
Elkekayveghaghnaqumalghiik.
Qenwat ighivgaamakanga.
Llaaghanwha ayveghaamalghiik.
Iiwenllu yataghqaqaat uyughaa kelutmun qiivyalghiimi puyughllaguftuq.
Anengani pimakanga, “Ii-I, iikutiinkut!”
Anengaan ayveq peglluku kelutmun kilgaquumalghiiknuugem esnenganun sikum kaasalghiimeknutem ameltughqaaluni.
Naqam iiwleng taanʼgavek siku saagrukegtaq.
Tamana saagrukegtaq siku anuqmi qateghmi legan meghem tevyaghqaqaa.
Taagken ketmun qimagumalghiik meghem tevyagu siku anuqliimakanga uvlugughsimakanga, umegneghughsimakanga qanigtuumaghmi.
Ketmun qimagumalghiik.
Uyavaghllaglutek siku kaasimakangat aangepiglleghhii.
Tawavek mayughlutek tespamagun laagluku kiyaghsimalghiik.
Uyughaan pimakanga anengani, “Weni tuqusiighnaqngunghilkumta sanaqaghten!”
Taagken mekelghiiq nuyekliq tuunaghmineng maghuyighluki ilagaamalghii.
Ilagaamaluku uyuqliimmekelghiighemnagaqumakanga uyavaghpaneng meteghlluk qalghilghii.
Mekelghiighem nuyekliim ilagaan qamagsamigu uyughani aapsimakanga, “Sameng nagaquutaghhneghisin?”
Uyuqliim nagaqughngaaghmigu akisimakanga, “Waniwanllu nagaquutaghhneghitunga!”
Alla nuyekliq ilagaamalghii.
Meteghlluk qalghighlaataamalghii uyavaghpaneng iwernga maateghniineng qantaghanlluni.
Aaplaataamakanga iwernga nagaquumalghii nagaqughngaaghmigu ama nuyekliimllu.
Alla ilagaamalghii tuunagmineng saguyaqluni.
Ilagaamaluku alla meteghlluk qalghilghii nagaquumakangak qantaghanlliighaghluni.
Ilagaan qamagsamigu uyughani pimakanga, “Nagaqunghisigu?”
“Nagaqunghitaqa!”
Iwerngangam nagaquumalghiik uyughaanllu ama anengaanllu.
Alla ilagaamalghii.
Qenwat qakma uqeghhmi qalghiimalghii, quqquqquqquqquq.
Anengaan pimakanga, “Awi, whanganginaakuma pinaanghitunga.”
Uyughaan pimakanga anengani, “Samengpiiqa?”
“Piiqaaten whanganginaghma taglaannalunga.”
Alla qakma qalghiimalghii meteghlluk, quqquqquqquqquq.
Anengaa aleghquumalghii, “A-aa-aa, nanghiiqunaqi!”
Uyughaan aapsimakanga, “Sameng piiqa meteghlluk?”
“Whaten piiquq nanghiiqunaluta maalghuguluta.
Taawanginaq uka tumemi ataasiq siku uusqalghii.”
Anengaan uyughani aanesqumakanga.
Aanumalghiik qemgaagmek.
Aanlutek anengaan uyughani neveghtesqumakanga.
Uyughaa neveghsimalghii.
Neveghsan aqumumakanga.
Aqumluku gginaa kenimineng saapumakanga.
Saapsamigu ghhataamalghiit, igleghsimalghiit quulvaqun.
Mululuteng aghuliighumalghiit.
Sivugsalghiimeng sikumi aghuliighumalghiit.
Tawani meghnaaliluteng alla anengaan uyughani neveghtesqumakanga.
Tawaten aqumluku anengaan gginaa saapumakanga kenimineng.
Palaghhaghmeng aqumgaaghlluteng ghhataghlaataamalghiit igleghsimalghiit.
Mululuteng aghuliighumalghiit.
Esghaghyalghiimeng meteghllugem meghnaalivigmi temngi naayghami alungutelleghmi uyghagmi.
Tawani aghuliighumalghiit.
Taawanginaq mayughvigiteftuq.
Anengaan ellmi tughneghani tuqluumakanga amiqluk.
Amiqluk qalghiimalghii.
Anengaa aleghquumalghii, “Whanganginaakuma pinaanghitunga!”
Uyughaan pimakanga, “Sameng piiqa?”
“Uum piiqaanga whanganginaghma mayuunnalunga.”
“Wetkuqun whanga sivuklunga mayuuskuninga tungangighhaani elpek mayuulliten.”
Llaaghanwha uyughaa mayuumalghii tungangighhaani anengaa mayuumalghii.
Mengteghaghmiingit ilagaanneqegsaataqut.
Qagum nunalgutmeng alignalghiingiighhaat ilagaqayuggaat ilagaataqut.
Ilangita piiqegkangat unʼga tuqumaniluki, ilangita piiqegkangit salin unguvanniluki, tamana ilanga ilagaataquq temngi.
Ellngit aglaamalghiit.
Kaalluteng iiyamun mayuumalghiit, nagasimalghiit.
Atangat kingulighpigaaluni ilagaamalghii.
Sagaqestaghngaaghmi aghuliiqaghluni aleghquumalghii, “Llangaqa whaa sikum ilunganillunga ilagaghtunga.
Iqlengiqunga weni!”
Alla ilagaamalghii.
Nepiiqaghluni akuzimalghii, “Ilagaamalunga sikum ilungani meteghllugem qalghillgha nagaqughaqa!”
Ilagaghaqelghii.
Nepiiqaghluni akuzilaataghtuq, “Ilagaqestaghngaaghma nepiighlunga meteghllugem piinga, ellmi ghhataannalunga, aygumun aghulaqunga.
Igleghtunga sikukun aghuliighlunga meghnaalilunga.
Meghnaalineghmeng taaqsama aghulaqlaataghtunga.
Igleghtunga.
Aghuliightunga ingani meteghllugem meghnaalivigani.
Weni iqlengiqunga.”
Mekelghiighek nagasimalghiik iiyakun qineghllutek.
Qama ilagaamalghii.
Ilagaghaqluni nepiighaqluni aleghquumalghii, “Taagken meghnaalilunga mayughtunga.
Mayughlunga taginga.
Kaasama iiyamun mayughtunga!”
Nepiighumalghii ilaganeghmeng nukalpigaat pimakangit, “Enta qakmavek iiyamun esghaghyaghtuqaghtek.”
Nukalpigaat aanyalghiimeng avangiteftut.
Iteghluteng ungipaasimakangat.
Qayughllak mayughnaqsata awatmun ullghiitamaat.
Uteghlluteng aglaamalghiit nenglum saaghwanun.
Atangat ellmineng aanumalghii.
Aanluni esghaamakangi.
Esghaghyamiki iitghesqumakangi.
Iitghumalghiit.
Quyakumakangit.
Atangita pimakegket, “Salusimi uullghestek?”
Akisimakangat, “Taanegken ima takaghpagllelguftuq.
Yulleghpagmun taaggun taglaghtukut.”
Atangita akisimakangit, “Anightaqun takaghnallghaguusi!”
Uyuqliim akisimakanga, “Anightaqun elpek iyeghllaguuten!”
Taam kenlanganeng awavaghllagnaniimalghiik.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Aymangaawen
Kiyaghsimaat esnaghmiit taawanginaq Quyillget maalghuk nulighqullghiik maalghuk avaqutagket mekelghiighek.
Allgha mekelghiighem nuyekliq, aallgha uyuqliq.
Taawanginaq atangan taana nuyekliq amyuutkaqegkanga.
Ilangani maaten quyngighqwaaghluni quyngiq uzimun kilgaaqumakanga.
Llaaghanwha sukaghimalghii saama iknaqughimalghii.
Atghaghluni iitghumalghii naqam qaviigalnguq.
Repall atangan qavaghtesigalkanga saama neghesigalkanga.
Nutaan neghnaqsaghtuq ighlegutaa.
Ighlegusatni ingaghlluni qavaamalghii.
Atangan qavalghii esghaghluku akin iptagaghsimakanga.
Mekelghiiq upuutkelluku maketqaghsalghiimi akin ayemlluku.
Atanga sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Una mekelghiiq qavngaq iknaqughii?”
Atangan pimakanga nuliini, “Pilugugkameng ulimatigu taawanginaq pinipiglleghhiimeng!”
Llaaghanwha ulimasimakanga.
Atangan ighneni pimakanga, “Aga, naalkesaghtughhu pinighqaq Aymangaawen.
Aymangaawetem sakimaganun sukalluten qavaghyaghtaa.
Tawaten aghulaqelghaaten!”
Apaasimakanga tuumkaghqameng.
Unaami unaanguluku mekelghiiq ghhataamalghii.
Qemimeng tevyalghiimi esghaghii piluguget seghlepestaaghet.
Aasimakangi mekelghiighem taagken igleghsimalghii.
Qemimeng tevyalghiimi esghaghii mengteghat.
Uqeghhmi nanevgaq qayugtughaqeftuq.
Amenam mekelghiiq igleghtuq naaghteghllagaqluni.
Nanevgaam nenglaqumakanga.
Kaasan aaptaa, “Saam yukaten?”
Akisimakanga mekelghiighem, “Esnam yukanga!”
Aaplaataghaa nanevgaam, “Natum esnam?”
“Maakunmi naayvaaghaam esnengi aatqaqii tamakut esnat.
Maaten whangkuta kiyaghtaqukut samani meghem esnami.
Nagaqughsiin?”
“Nagaqughtunga.”
Nanevgaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “I-i-i, esnam esnam esnam!”
Taagken pimakanga, “A-a, iitghi neghyaghtaa!”
“Kangsughllequnga, iteghnaqegkuma.”
“Tawateteghngaaghpek iitghi!”
“Aa-a, naqam iteghlanga!”
Pegnem iteghtuq.
Nanevgaam nuliini pimakanga, “Gaaghutigu quyngimeng una esnam yuga.”
Llaaghanwha gaaghulluku quyngit ugusimakangi.
Neghusimalghiit.
Taaqluteng iitghesqumayaqanga aagramun.
Ighsaamalghii nateghmi qavaamalghii.
Unaami unaanguluku aghulaqumalghii.
Nanevgaankuk aghnalqwaaghenkuk nenglaqumakangat.
Talughsami kilgaaqumeng aghulaqumalghii.
Qemimun kaallaataghtuq.
Kaalluni tevlaataghtuq.
Atghaghtuq mengteghanun.
Esghaghaa nanevgaq qayugtulghii.
Nanevgaam esghaghpenaan avelghaqiinaamakanga.
Sumeghtaghaamalghii tughneghaaniluku.
Sivugutkelluku aapsimakanga, “Saamyukaten?”
“Esnamyukanga!”
“Naten esnam?”
“Maakunmi naayvaaghem esnengi aatqii esnat.
Enkaam whangkuta kiyaghtaqukut meghem esnengani.
Aa-a!”
Nanevgaq sumeghtaghaghtuq, “Iik, esnam esnam esnam esnam.”
“Naqam iitghi, neghyaghtaa.”
Mekelghiiq ighsaamalghii inqunamen kangsughnayukami.
Tawateteghngaan iitghesqumakanga.
Llaaghanwha kangsughngaaghmi iitghumalghii.
Neghumalghii nateghmi.
Taaqluni nanevgaam iitghesqumayaqanga ingleghmun.
Mekelghiighem pimakanga, “Itagnaghtunga whani qavaghllequnga.”
Llaaghanwha qavaamalghii.
Unaami aghulaqumalghii.
Uusneghwaaghmun mayuumalghii naaghtaqluni.
Nanevgaq nulighqullghiik nenglaanneqegsaamalghiik.
Mekelghiiq uusneghwaaghmun talughsami kilgaaqumeng aghulaqumalghii.
Hanganun uusneghwaaghmun tevyami esghaamakangi mengteghaat ataasit.
Taagken uusneghwaaghmeng atghaamalghii naaghtaqluni.
Llaaghanwha nanevgaq enngaatall nenglaamalghii.
Kaasan nanevgaam aaplaataghaa, “Saamyukaten?”
Mekelghiighemakisimakanga, “Esnamyukanga.”
“Naten esnam?”
“Maakunmi naayvaghaaghem esnengi tamakut aatqaqii esnat.”
“Aa, navek igleghtaazin?”
“Taamavek nunivagmun igleghtaagunga.
Aapghaqegkangat Aymangaawen tuguyaghtughaqaqa.”
Nanevgaam pii nenglaqumaan, “O-ho-hooghh, kayngusaghallequten!
Elpetun pinightutkaanghituq!”
“Aa-a, itagnaghtunga!”
“Naqam iitghi.
Neghyaghtaa.”
Mekelghiiq iitghumalghii amiknaafqevzighluku.
Nanevgaampimakanga, “Iik saqrugtatuq taana!”
Mekelghiiq neghumalghii.
Taaqluni itegherkineghmeng tawani ingaghtaaghumalghii.
Wetku unugyagu qavaamalghii.
Unaami ghhataghlaataghtuq.
Uusneghwaaghmun tevyami kilgaaqumeng aghulaqumalghii.
Uusneghwaaq kaallaataghaa.
Tevyami piyugmeng atghaamalghii naaghtaqluni kayaannaqepiglluni.
Mekelghiighem esghaamakanga nanevgaq qayugtuqestalghii.
Kaasan nanevgaam aapsimakanga, “Saam yukaten?”
“Esnam yukanga!”
“Naten esnam?”
“Maakunmi naayvaaghem esnengi aatqii esnat.
Enkaam whangkuta kiyaghtaqukut meghem esnengani.
Aa-a!”
Nanevgaq sumeghtaghaghtuq, “Iik, esnam esnam esnam esnam.”
“Aa-a, naqam iitghi!
Neghyaghtaa.” 
Mekelghiiq iteghnaqsalghiimi kangsughtuq.
Iwemga pegnem iteghtuq.
Iteghluni neghumalghii.
Neghumaluku aapsimakanga nanevgaam, “Navek igleghtaazin?”
“Nunivagmelnguq paamna Aymangaawen tuguyaghtughaqaqa.”
“Upupeng nepiighelten.
Kayngusaghallequten!
Iiteklu ungipaannaqamken.
Whakenwhaa ghhataquvek mengteghat ataasit kaalleqaten.
Mengteghaneng taagken alla igleghtekuvek kaalleqaten taawa Aymangaawenkut.
Taawa qamagtuq.
Nagaqughsiin?”
“Nagaqughtunga!”
Taaqluteng neneghmeng ingaghtaaghumalghii mekelghiiq.
Unugyagu qavaamalghii.
Unaami aghsagu aghulaqlaataamalghii.
Nenglaqumakangat sukanginniluku.
Talughsami kilgaaqumeng aghulaqumalghii.
Allameng uusneghwaaq kaallaataghaa.
Kaasami uusneghwaaghmun piyugmeng igleghsimalghii.
Uusneghwaaq tevluku atghiiyami sukangitesighwaaghumalghii.
Nanevgaam esghaamakanga.
Kaasan aapsimakanga, “Saam yukaten?”
“Esnam yukanga!”
“Naten esnam?”
“Maakunmi naayvaaghem esnengi aatqii esnat.
Enkaam whangkuta kiyaghtaqukut meghem esnengani.
Aa-a!”
Nanevgaq sumeghtaghaghtuq, “Iik, esnam esnam esnam esnam.”
“Naqam iitghi.
Neghyaghtaa!”
Mekelghiiq iitghumalghii.
Neghumalghii.
Taaqluni qavaamalghii.
Unaami unaanguluku aghulaqumalghii.
Sivukluni piyuwhaghmeng aghulaqumalghii.
Wetku talughsami uusneghwaaghmeng kilgaaqumalghii.
Alla esghaghlaataghaa uusneghwaaq akugaaghniineng aangleghii.
Tawavek uusneghwaaghem qaaynganun mayughyalghiimi saama esghaghii maalghukmengteghaak.
Ketliq aangelghii.
Kelutanganilnguq mengteghaq mekestaaghhaq.
Uyavani esghaghaa quyngiq uglapiglleghhii.
Quyngim uvitangani yugyagllak.
Tamana yuuk Aymangaawem ugikaqeftaa.
Iwernga qaviigalnguut ellngani.
Mengteghaam taam uuqghaani nanevgaq esghaghaa qayugtaalghii.
Mekelghiiq atghaamalghii naaghtaqluni.
Iwernga iqlengiqaqelghii.
Taagken uusneghwaaghmeng ukigumalghii.
Kaalluni aangelghiikun mengteghanun uuqghitni aghuliighumalghii.
Nanevgaam avelghaqiinaamakanga qayughllak tughneghaaniluku.
Naqam atkuga aangepiglleghhii.
Nanevgaq tununneghani maligtaqegkanga.
Qenwat nanevgaam aghuliighulluku aapsimakanga, “Saam yukaten?”
“Esnam yukanga!”
“Navek igleghtaazin?”
“Aymangaawen aapghaqegkangat.
Tuguyaghtughaqaqa.”
Sunanguq nanevgaq taana agiglluni mekestaaghhaghmun mengteghamun aleghqughta, “Qamay nengaawaq tawa!”
Sunanguq taana aghnaghaq qineghta.
Ineqsunapiglleghhii pinipiglleghhii.
Pimakanga aghnaghaam, “Ugiknaanghitaqa.
Seghlepestaaghuuq.”
Aghnaghaq uteghpagsimalghii.
“Iiteklu kuuvistenguluten!”
Mekelghiiq aglaamalghii mengteghamun.
Iteghyalghiimi esghaghii yugyagllaget.
Qesiqun Aymangaawem ugikaqeftii.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, “Iitghi qullugek kuuvyaghtughqek!”
Mekelghiiq iteghluni taakuk tugumakek.
Tugulukek ugatmiighsimalghii pegnem uullghaghtevzighaqluni.
Maaten alla amllughnaqsalghiimi kuuvumakek taagavek ugatanganilngughnun sanqutnun.
Allameng igleqaghluni inglunganun enraq kuuvumakanga.
Amigmun amllughluni aanaqsalghimi manughakun qamagllukek kuuvumakek.
Aymangaawen tapghaghmeng eslegalghiimeng tugulluni kagsagpagataamakanga mekelghiiq.
Mekelghiiq aqninghituq qayughllak atkuga umupiglleghhii.
Ighivgaghyagu iteghaatut.
Neghluteng qavaasimalghiit.
Ellnga mekelghiiq nateghmi qavaamalghii.
Unaami yuuk tamana kilgaaqunaluni anqaghtaasimalghii mekelghiiq taana tutqaghtaqluku.
Mekelghiighem akinaqumakangi naghughhnaqenghata ighumineng itegmikaneghminiki naghteghllagaqelghiit.
Yuuk tamana kilgaaqusimalghii Aymangaawenllu maligulluni yuuk taanallu mekelghiiq.
Ghhataamalghiit mekelghiiq taana sivukluni piyuggaghmeng.
Yugem tamatum nenglaqumaan naghughtaqegkanga.
Mekelghiiq uusneghwaaghmun talughsami piluguni mataghlluki kilgaaquumalghii qevuulluni.
Tamana yuuknaghughquumakanga.
Taana naayghaq uzivluku tagimalghii.
Tagimun esghaamakanga aghnaghaq.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, “Aagyuq utaqanga!”
Mekelghiighem pimakanga, “Utaqanaanghitamken!”
Mekelghiighem avelghaghluku kaasimalghii.
Aghnaghaam kaalluni tuguluku itghusimakanga.
Llaaghanwha tugumakanga.
Yuuk tamana aglaghtuusimalghii ellmeng mengteghameggnun.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghii mekelghiiq.
Maaten ilangani atangan aghnaghaampimakanga, “Siingenllu aghnaq aftakayuguuq.”
Llaaghanwha mengteghameng aavgulluteng aglaamalghiit mekelghiighem nunanganun.
Kaalluteng mekelghiighem atangan mengteghaan kelutanganun mengteghaamalghiit.
Mekleghiighem naanga aanumalghii.
Aanluni kelutmun esghaghyalghiimi esghaghii mengteghat, mengtegham saaghwani quyngit.
Aghnaq quyngineng alingluni iitghumalghii.
Aghnamugini ungipaasimakanga.
Mekelghiighhaq aanluni takumakangi.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Aghnaghaam ugiminun aapghumakanga, “Mekelghiighhaq sama tagiiq!”
Ugingan pimakanga, “Neghesqigu!”
Aghnaghaam nuugluni neghesqesaghaa.
Mekelghiighhaam aghnaghaq esghaghluku uullghaghsimalghii.
Aghnaghaam iteghluni ungipaasimakanga mekelghiiq.
Mekelghiighhaq taana unaanguluku aghneghem qukaanun tuqumalghii.
Mekelghiighhaq wetku aghneghem qukaani unguvaamalghii.
Makelluni aatghaamalghii.
Kaasan atangan pimakanga, “Sangavek muluughsin?”
Mekelghiighhaam akisimakanga, “Qayughllak aghnaghaq ineqsunapigtuq.
Enkaam whanga tazingani tuqumayaghtunga.”
Atangan akisimakanga, “Enta whanga tuquyaghlanga!”
Atanga aanluni taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni meghsingllaamalghii, “Qamay, meghsiightengnga.”
Aghnaghaam meghun imighluku tallighhiinaghmineng tuunumakanga.
Yugem paatgumakanga meghun.
Aghnaghaam itagnatun imiimakanga.
Naqam aghnaghaq sungaghaghqwaaluni nuugluni tuunumakanga.
Yugem esghaghluku aghnaghaq tuqumalghii.
Wetku unugyan unguvaghluni atghaamalghii.
Qavaghluni unaami yugem mekeghiighhaq kevgaaqumakanga mekelghiighmeng ankunameng (1) mughutelgutnguluku.
Mekelghiiq aangghumalghii.
Llaaghanwha atani mughullghii maligsimakanga.
Unaangumalghiit.
Atangan aghilluni inglupigaq meghmun egsimakanga aksaqluni.
Atanga pimalghii, “Uuk aghilluka meghmun atqaghtuq.”
Mekelghiighem akisimakanga, “Sanguluku enan allaneng aghillighhaaten!”
Wanlegi atangan pimakanga, “Qayughllak nuliighma ukinikaqaa.”
Llaaghanwha mekelghiiq qukamikun qaamqaghlluni ugmestaaghhaghmun sikumun ateghtuq aqfaghiiq aghillugmeng.
Whaa aga ateghyan tapghaa nengpagsaqenni meghmun atqaghtesluku atangan sayugluku sikumeng maligsimakanga.
Maliglluku kaapumakanga tuqulluku.
Tuqusamigu mengteghanun taglaamalghii.
(1) Ruuseghmiit mumigtellghani qemgaghmenguuniit;
Uuzagem pillghani atkunnaanii, atkuusiighegnguq qaliiraaghestun ayuqelghiik.
Kaallimi iitghumalghii.
Aymangaawen pimakanga, “Ugin tuqumaaq qayughllak ighlekeghngaamni aghilluka aqfaamaa.
Wasiinmi whanga ugikelleqegkevnga.”
Aghnaghaam nanit qaamlluki ilagaamalghii.
Yuuk masisu iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aghnaghaam esghapagumakanga.
Yuuk qulligiimalghii.
Qulligiighluni uka ellnganun tagimalghii aleghquumalghii, “Ugin elpek tuqumaaq, qayughllak iglekeghngaamni naaminun aghilluk ulimaaqniluku.
Aqfanaqsaqenni kalevuq.
Wasiinmi whanga ugikelleqegkevnga.”
Aghnaghaam nanit qaamlluki ilagaaghnaqumaluku yugem taam akughtuumaan qinunaghqumaghmi takumakanga ellnga.
Aghnaghaq ilagaaghyalghiimi yuuk taana qavaamalghii.
Qayughllak aghnaghaq nunanighllagpetuq ilagaqaaluni.
Aghnaghaq taana atghaghataamalghii2.
Atghaghataghluni ugimi tumanga tuumsimakanga.
Aatghumalghii sikugnun.
Ateghyalghiimi esghaghaa ugini savilighluni angvaneghmikun.
Legan saviga amuluku uiluumakanga.
Llaaghanwha unguvaamalghn.
Mekelghiiq piyugmeng taglaamalghii.
Aghnaghaq atghaghataghluni.
Aghnaghaq ingleghqun aanumalghii.
Aanyalghimi yuuk esghaghaa.
Akugteghatalghii elqemsighaghmeng.(?) Tawani palaghhaghmeng kiyaghtaalluteng mekelghiiq nateghmun iitghumalghii.
Qiighwumalghii.
Atangan qiilghwii nagaqughluku qulligegni aasimayaqek.
Aasimakanga inglupigaq temkam ighunga inglunganun aasimakanga ilepghaaghem ighunga.
Repall atanga aaghhweregaghmeng aanumalghii, llangaqa pingayuneng ighukelghii.
Mekelghiighem aanesnaaniimakanga unegtesqelluku.
Atanga aanumalghii.
Aymangaawenkuk ugikullghiik aghulaqumalghiik nemeggnun.
Qamagtuq Tefaay.
Qayaqsighvik
Iimnanguq, kiyaghsimaaq nimaaq Qayaqsighvik.
Whaa salin taana kiyaghtuq nuna.
Tawani nunaami kiyaghsimalghii yuuk avaqutaghtuqaq.
Taawanginaq avaqutii yugem qayaghtuuluteng tuqulaghaatkat qamaglluteng.
Taagken uksumi ilangi yugemnulighha aqsangumalghii.
Llaaghanwha ighnimalghii.
Piyaqeseng taana taghnughhaq mekelghiighuftuq.
Atiimakangat Qayaqsighvigmeng.
Taagken anglitaatnga maliglluku quunpeng angalqataasimeng petugluku.
Kiyaghusimakanga inqunamen anglegutangitun tuqunayukan.
Qenwat anglighllagumalghii.
Maaten ilangani aapusimalghii Qayaqsighvik qayaghtughnaluni.
Atangan ighlekumakanga saama pimakanga, “Qayiituten avangituten.”
Taagken Qayaqsighvik aangghumalghii.
Qayaqsighvik esnamun piyaamalghii.
Esnami naalkumakanga qayam sivuyaga.
Qakaqsighvigem taglaasimakanga.
Kaalluni atani aapsimakanga, “Sangawa taana?”
Atangan akisimakanga, “Taana qayam sivuyakaa.”
Taagken Qayaqsighvigem atani pilaataamakanga, “Qayameng ulimatinga whanga.”
Atangan pimakanga, “Sangan ulimannaanghitamken.”
Qayaqsighvigem pilaataamakanga, “Ulimatinga whanga qayameng!”
Taagken atangan aangghumakanga.
Atanga llaaghanwha ulimasimalghii.
Qayaq atangan taaqumakanga.
Taaqluku sivuyagakun ama angyalgakun ukisimakanga qayaa.
Unaami Qayaqsighvik aapusimalghii ataminun qayaghtughnaluni.
Atangan ighlekumakanga.
Qayaqsighvik sagiqumalghii.
Atangan aanghumakanga.
Taagken atangan angalqataasiq saagsimakanga.
Saaglluku qayam sivuyagakun qepusimakanga iqukruga angalqataasimeng.
Llaaghanwha Qayaqsighvik kesimalghii.
Atangan tapghaq aaghhesimakanga.
Qenwat naayghamun talughsimalghii.
Taagken atangan amumakanga wetku aaghsan.
Tamlagumalghii.
Tamlagyalghiimi unaangughtaamalghii neghsameng.
Taagken taglaasimakangit mengteghameggnun neghsat.
Unaami Qayaqsighvik aapusimalghii ataminun alla qayaghtughnaluni.
Atangan ighlekumakanga.
Qayaqsighvik sagiqumalghii.
Atangan aangghumakanga.
Qayaqsighvikkesimalghii.
Alla atangan aaghheslaataamakanga.
Qayaqsighvik temngi taagavek ketmiighsimalghii.
Qenwat taluqaghsimalghii.
Qayaqsighvigem esghaamakanga puugzaq qavalghii meghem qaayngani.
Qayaqsighvigem takuyaghaa.
Aga atghaamalghii.
Mululuni uyavaqun puugumalghii.
Puugyan takuyaghaa.
Aga atghaamalghii.
Mululuni uyavaqun puugumalghii.
Puugyan takuyaghaa.
Aga atghaghlaataamalghii.
Mululuni puuglaataghtuq.
Takukestaghngaaghmigu sumeghtaghaamalghii uyavannaqniluku.
Taagken taglaamalghii.
Taglaamaluku sukilpaq savinaakun qayam nalugtuq.
Nalugluni qaanghanun itqaghtesimakek sugrugegni.
Qayaqsighvikggiistusimakanga.
Taagken taglaragkiighumalghii.
Ighleghutkelluku aglukek meghnuumalghiik.
Meghnughyayek naallghunnaqsaghaak sukilpaq wata iitghataghaamalghii.
Qayaqsighvigem ggiistullaataamakanga inqunamen iteghnayukan.
Taglaamalghii.
Igleghutkelluku aglukek meghnuumalghiik.
Naallghunnalukek aglugni naallghunnaqsaghaak sukilpaq iitghataghaamalghii, taawanginaq papasqwa aliilluni unegsimalghii.
Taagken tamlagumalghii.
Tamlagyan atangan taana sukilpaq nusugumakanga.
Qavaamalghiit unugyagu.
Unaami Qayaqsighvik aapusimalghii ataminun, “Nunivagmun piyaakaghlanga?”
Atangan ighlekumakanga.
Qayaqsighvik sagiqumalghii.
Atangan llaaghanwha aangghumakanga.
Llaaghanwha Qayaqsighvik aghulaqumalghii.
Igleghutkelluku meghnaaliyugumalghii.
Llaaghanwha pennam asingakun aqumumalghii.
Aqumgamaluku kaasimalghii yuuk savikenghaaghmeng pilugukelghii.
Qayaqsighvik naqam naatghillelek.
Yugem savikenghaaghneng pilugukelghiim esghaghyaqenni itegani qaneq Qayaqsighvigem agitaghpagtaghii.
Yugem savikenghaaghneng pilugukelghiim pimakanga Qayaqsighvik, “Taana sangwaa agitaghpagtaghta?”
Qayaqsighvigem ighuni ellnganun qapragsaqenni yuuk uullghaghsimalghii.
Yugem pimakanga, “Pigpenanga pilugugenka ukut pilleqaten!”
Qayaqsighvigem taaqumakanga.
Taagken yugem piluguni tuunumakangi.
Qayaqsighvigem aalluki nekevyalghiimi aga penniiq pangalgaqeftuq.
Qesiqun taana yuuk savikenghaaghmeng pilugukelghii penniighwaaquq.
Qayaqsighvik tawavek mayuumalghii pennamun.
Uugsalghiimi saama pennam asingani esghaamakanga negaghpak.
Qayaqsighvik ukigumalghii.
Ukigumaluku pika pennam qaayngani yuuk esghaamakanga savikenghaaghneng pilugukelghii taawanginaq aangepiglleghhii.
Taam yugrukutaaghem aapsimakanga, “Naten ukigsin?”
“Legan ukiglunga.”
Nutaan yugrukutaaghllak ukignaqsaghtuq.
Ifkaamalghii neghqwaani ayemqughluku tuquluni.
Taagken Qayaqsighvik ukigumalghii.
Naapsimalghii negaghpagkun.
Qayaqsighvik awiinnaqsaghtuq.
Aghtuumalghii.
Tawani aghneghsimalghii.
Iiwenllu unugyaghtughaa Qayaqsighvigem nanevgaghhaq esghaamakanga.
Saama nanevgaghhaq aleghqughwaaqeftuq, “Kiiiiii, unaangumaanga neghsameng!”
Nanevgaghhaam naaptighluku taglaasimakanga Qayaqsighvikneghsaq.
Ellmini maani yupik taawanginaq tuqusighwaalghii.
Taglaatkelluku itegani Qayaqsighvigem uqfigkun eltughtesaqenni nanevgaghhaq sivutmun iqumalghii qevuulluni.
Qayaqsighvigem itegani awitqaghsaqenni nanevgaghhaq naghteghllagumalghii repall gginani esnegtighllagluku.
Nanevgaghhaq ighyaghqelluni sivugsimalghii.
Taglaasimakanga alla Qayaqsighvik.
Enraq ama uqfigkun nuqneghyalghii alla nanevgaghhaq sagiqumalghii sivutmun.
Qayaqsighvigem peghqaghyaqenni nanevgaghhaq naghllaataamalghii repall gginani esnightighluku.
Nanevgaghhaq nekevluni taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyannulighhan quyakumakanga.
Nanevgaghhaqneghsaq ilunganun itghusimakanga.
Itghulluku ughugsiimakanga.
Qayughllaktaakut sumeghtaghaalghiit kumlamanniluku.
Ellmini maani taakut pilugugita savikenghaaghet llangaqa kumlamalghiistun.
Nanevgaghhaam nulighhan aftayugumakanga.
Nutaan ulaani tuguluku aftanaqsaghaa.
Qayaqsighvik estequmalghii.
Llaaghanwha nanevgaghhaam nuliini pimakanga, “Salin kumlamaaq.
Enan unaami aftanaken.”
Llaaghanwha qavaamalghiit.
Nanevgaghhaq qavaghpenam taghtuumaamalghii inqunamen neghsaq unguvaghnayukan.
Qavaghniyami nanevgaghhaq anaamalghii kelengakistekaghqameng.
Ananeghmeng taaqluni ellmi anani pimakanga, “Anamni whani kelengaknakesi neghsaq taana.”
Llaaghanwha nanevgaq qavaamalghii.
Qavaghyan Qayaqsighvik nutaan payugsaghtuq qullugegnilnguq anaq araghllagumalghii.
Nanevgaghhaam makelluni esghaghluku neghsaq anani ellmi pimakanga, “Anaqa una iqlengaasapiwaa!”
Nanevgaghhaq ingaghlluni qavaamalghii.
Qavaghyan Qayaqsighvik maketqaghlluni ghhukaghameng kuuvyaqenni anam iqukruga siipsimalghii.
Qayaqsighvik ingaghaghsimalghii.
Mululuni nutaan Qayaqsighvik payugsaghtuq anaq araghyalghimi llangaqa sakun ukimalleghqun qineghlluni alla Qayaqsighvigem ghhukaghameng kuuvyaqenni taluqaghsimalghii.
Qayaqsighvik makelluni tuququghluki aanumalghii.
Aanluni temngi tespagavek aghulaqumalghii.
Qemimeng tevyalghiimi esghaamakangi, kiiiiii mengteghalghuteghllaget.
Ataasinun mengteghanun iteghyalghiimi esghaamakangi yulghuteghllaget taawanginaq ataasiq aghnaghaq.
Qesiqun taam aghnaghaam kuugkaqeitii.
Aghnam taam pimakanga, “Tugulaken!”
Naqam tamakut yungestaghhaat.
Qayaqsighvigem aangghumakanga.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghiit.
Ilangani aghneghmi qaga eslami arasimalghiit, “Nanughyaghtuq nanughyaghtuuuuq!”
Llaaghanwha tama yuuk aanleghasimalghii qamaglluni.
Qayaqsighvik nuliighminun aapusaghtuq.
Nulighhan ighlekumakanga.
Qayaqsighvikaanumalghii.
Aanyalghiimi esghaamakanga esnami agigpeghwaaghutaqeftuq yulghuteghllak.
Ellngallu esnamun pimalghii.
Kaasalghiimi saama esghaamakanga kana nanughllak sikum esnengani.
Nutaan naasquni ipuggneghagu arataqelghiit, “Uuuuuy, uuuuuy, uuuuuy, uuuuuy!”
Ilangit aleghquumalghemng, “Nanuq, nanuq, tanem, tanem!”
Qesiqun taana siku sikungunghituq, naayvam puglluga ama taana nanuq nanuunghituq, ugugnaghaaguq.
Qayaqsighvik teskanavek ketfaghluni ugugnaghaq tuusaqenni siftaghqumakanga.
Tamatum aangenghita tamana yuuk araamakanga, “Nengaawaq nanughaghtuq tutqaghlluku!”
Taagken aglaasimakangat.
Kaatulluku itghusimakangat.
Aghnam aftamakanga.
Aftaluku gaaghumakangat.
Unugyan neghusimalghiit.
Qayaqsighvigem esghaghyaqenni ugugnaghaam tulimaa yugem ataasimkepsuutkaqegkanga.
Aghnam llilaamakanga, “Qayaqsighvikneghi.”
Qayaqsighvik neghumalghii.
Maalghuk ighuk ugugnaghaam ighukek neghumakek.
Taagken aghnam pimakanga, aqsanga kenegraamaan, “Kaay aqsan aafkaghllequq.”
Unugumakanga qavaghluteng.
Unaami aghsagu Qayaqsighvigem nagaqumakangi eslami araallghiit, “Tungtuvak esghaghaghput!”
Taagken aanleghaalluteng aghulaqumalghiit naayghanun.
Ama Qayaqsighviklu aghulaqumalghii.
Kaasalghiimi esghaamakangi yuget iighaghtuullghiit.
Legan maketekestanghani alingaqelghiit.
Esghaghyaqenni Qayaqsighvigem taana tungtu tungtungunghituq, kuuniisanguftuq.
Qayaqsighvigem tuutqaghsimakanga tuqulluku.
Araasimalghii yuuk tamana, “Tungtuvak tuqutaa nengaawaam tuutqaghlluku!
Yuuk tamana atghaamalghii mengteghaminun.
Ama Qayaqsighviklu atghaamalghii.
Naqam Qayaqsighvik ighnengegkaalghii.
Unaami aghsagu aanyalghiimi tamana yuuk aga tenguusimalghii.
Esghaghyaqenni aqergiighuftuq.
Aghulaqumalghiit nunamun ighnequllghiit.
Taagken kaasalghiimeng Qayaqsighvigmun paaghqiteftuq.
Esghaamakanga nanevgaq.
Mekelghiighem aapsimakanga, “Saam yukaten sanguzin?”
“Imanguuuuq, ayumiq anengaqa Qayaqsighvik yuqaqaaftuq.
Whanga whaa atiimaftaatnga taameng ateghmeng.
Saama ataput naaput neghipiglluteng tuqukaagut.
Qamagtuq Tefaay.
Qayuutam Kayusiqaa Aghnaq
Iinmanguq kiyaghsimaaq yuuk nuliikek avaqutaghtuqaq.
Uksunghagu yuuk mughunniighaqelghii.
Maaten ilangani kiigyagu qayaghtuneghmini aghtuumalghii unangneghmeng ama ilanganeng aghneghneng palaghhaaluku unangaqelghii.
Uksughyagu amalleqa unangneghmeng aghtuumalghii.
Hangani neqangit palaghhaaghsata nuliini pimakanga, “Whaa pirughsaghtughnaqunga amavek qantaghanlengughnun Quyillegnun!”
Aghnam aangghumakanga.
Llaaghanwha qamiyegneng qamughluni aghulaqumalghii.
Kaasan yugem upughasimakanga, Neghesimaan alla gaaghusimaan quyngimeng.
Taaqsami aghulaqnaqumayalghii yugem Quyillgem ighlekumakanga.
Sagiqumalghii ighlekuughsimakanga.
Qavaamalghiit.
Tawa yuggaq aghtuumalghii qavaneghmeng qayughllagʼqun avaqutii neqngilnguut.
Ima qavaamalghii pegnem.
Unaami taghtughyalghiimeng umegneghllak tawani aghneghsimalghii.
Amenam taam yuggaam mengteghaghmiinga tawani kiyaghsimalghii.
Unugaqaa iiwenllu samakavlegusimalghii.
Qelaamakanga aghnam qalghighyalghiimi tughneghaaftuq.
Nuugumalghii.
Esghaghyaqenni amigkun teflimi ayuqeftuq.
Aghnam upughasimakanga neghesqelluku.
Tughneghaam pimakanga, “Igleghtaagunga neghnalunga taakuneng avaqutaghpeneng aghuliightunga.”
Aghnam pimakanga, “Utaqiigi, tuunaqamken.”
Aghnaq atqaghlluni uughqanun sinumun ivaghiluni tiguynga1 tuguluku pimakanga, “Enngaatall elpek sumeghneghpetun salukimi anigu qaanghaniteghngaan nusugraghaqsigu?”
Iitghumalghii.
Saama tughneghaq tungsighwaaghaquq avaqutii neghnaluki.
Tiguynga aanqusalghiimi ilagaatmeng imani nunanighllagtuq.
Llaaghanwha qavaamalghii tughneghaq.
Tamaani ilagaamalghii iwemgaqun ilagaatngi qamagsimakangi.
Qamagsamiki tughneghaq taghtuumalghii.
Taghtughluni tungsighwaaghumalghii.
Aghnampimakanga, “Utaqiigi tuunaqamken.”
Atqaghlluni aywaanun sinumun ivgaghiluni tuguluki neqmun iguquusiq quyngim kelpanga napaghsimakanga.
Aleghquumaan, “Enngaatall elpek sumeghneghpetun salukimi uguqnam ilunganilnguut nusugraghaqsiki?”
Mululuni taama ilagaamalghii.
Tughneghaq nunakiluni qavaamalghii.
Ilagaamaluku unaghsiq anightuusimakanga.
Anighqwaamalghii iiwenllu nepiighaquq tughneghaq taghtuumalghii.
Taghtuneghmini tungsighwaaghaqelghii taghnughhamengneghnaluni.
Nuugluni anighqutni tuguluku napaghsimakanga.
Anighqutni pimakanga, “Anighqutmi whani sumeghneghpegun salukimi sangwaat gaaghaqsiki kukilamaghngata.”
Anighqun ilagaghyalghiimi imani wata nunanighllagtuq.
Talwa tughneghaq qavaamalghii umuluku.
Aghnaq atqaghlluni vegaaghet uyguqulluki tughneghaq amigmun qepusimakanga.
Anighqun naangyalghiimi taghtuumalghii.
Taghtughluni qapragnaqsalghiimi aghtuumalghii.
Aghnaq tughneghaam pimakanga, “Itemutinga!
Pinaanghitamken!”
Aghnam pimakanga, “Itemunnaanghitamken.
Ugika utaqanaqaqa tuqutesqelluten.”
Whaken tuunaqamken.”
“Enta esghaqaghlakun!”
Tughneghaam kelgusimakanga qayuutani saama pimakanga, “Enngaatall aghtuusiqenghinnayaqen sangwaa neghyukegkan tugunayaqen.”
“Enta esghapaglaken.
Piighten.”
Tughneghaampimakanga, “Taawanginaq quunpeng aaghlluku kiyaghtaaghutaqigu saama whaten piyaghqaaguten.”
Legan maketutkelluku qayuutani pimakanga, “Qayuutami uumi quyngighyugtunga!”
Uqigtughusimalghii, lliyaqenni quyngiq.
“Tawa tawaten piiqi.”
Llaaghanwha itemusimakanga.
Aghulaqumalghii.
Aghnaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Agum waamtaanga!”
Qayuutani nusugumakanga.
Nusugluku qayuutani pimakanga, “Qayuutami uumi tughneghaq aagna esghaghyugaqa!”
Uqigtughusimalghii.
Tughneghaq uteghtesimakanga.
Tughneghaam pimakanga, “Whangamnun pinguluku tuunumangitaqa!”
Aanluni aghulaqumalghii.
Aghnam meghmun nengugulluku qayuutani pimalghii, “Qayuutami uumi neghsaghyugtunga!”
Uqigtughusimalghii.
Ukigsaqenni neghsameng.
Allameng pilaataamalghii, “Qayuutami uumi maklagyugtunga!”
Uqigtughusimalghii.
Ugigsaqenni, maklagmeng.
Aftaluku sinumun llimakanga.
Unaami aghsagu yuggaq quyngimeng qamiyegni usilukek tagimalghii mengteghaminun.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Pimakanga nuliini, “Kayusiqaghnga!”
Aghnaq aatqaghlluni kayusimakanga.
Taaqsamigu aghnaq sinumun ivgaghluni siqlugighumalghii kuyagaghmeng.
Yuggaam nuliini pimakanga, “Naqam sameng siqlugighaqsin, avangitaqluta.”
“Kakakakaka, nepiighelten!”
Yuggaq iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan uyuqlighpigaam igheghan pimakanga, “Aghnaq sama qayuutaghalguuq.”
Yuuk legan uqengaghyugsimalghii yuukumalghii quyamalghii.
Aghnam iteghyami ungipaasimakanga.
Yugem pimakanga, “Enta mangunayukaa.”
Llaaghanwha aghnam qayuutani nengugulluku meghem tunganganun aleghquumalghii, “Qayuutami uumi mangunayugtunga!”
Uqigtughusimalghii.
Ukigsaqenni mangunalguftuq.
Ugingan pilaataamakanga, “Aghveghyugigatepigsin.”
Aghnam meghmun qayuutani nengugulluku aleghquumalghii, “Qayuutami uumi mangtagyugtunga!”
Katagusimakangi mangtagllak.
Taagken tawani pinitun kiyaghsimalghiit.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Yughqutaam Ighnegha Kiighwyaaghtekaq
Kiyaghsimaa nalighmeng kiyaghsimangita, maalghuk nulighqullghiik yugek avaqutiilnguuk.
Ilangani yuuk kiwatmeggnun pimaluku esghaamakanga aghnaq ighninaqelghii.
Ighniyalghiimi mekelghiighmeng qesiqun tuusimakanga yughqutaq pinaaqa.
Taana taghnughhaq anglimalghii atghaasaqenni.
Taagken kiyaghneghmun mayuumalghii.
Kiyaghneghem pimakanga nuliini, “Saam una pikagu?”
“Unami yughqutaam ighniigha.”
Kiyaghneghempimakanga taghnughhaq, “Aa ingavek aglaa kiighwyanun.”
Taghnughhaq aglaghyalghiimi kiighwyaaghsimalghii.
Qamagtuq. Tefaay.
Kiighwyaq
Iimnanguq yuuk nuliilek avaqutiilnguq salin.
Mughunniighaqelghii naqamunangaqelghii.
Ilangani maaten mughulluni aghtuumalghii.
Qenwat unugumakanga.
Quulmun esghaghyalghiimi kiighwyaq esghaamakanga.
Esghaghyaqenni kiighwyaneng mengteghiitnim aga ifkaghtuq kenghhaq.
Legan nekevluni taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghyalghnmi nulighha aqsangumalghii.
Neghulluteng qavaamalghiit.
Unaami yuuk mughusimalghii.
Unangluni neghsameng tagiyalghiimi nulighha ighniimalghii mekelghiighmeng.
Ugingan aghnam atiimakanga, Kiighwyameng.
Qavaghhiinaghqun anglimalghii.
Aghnaghaq aqsanglaataamalghii.
Ighniyalghiimi aghnaghaghmeng.
Taagken kenlanga alla aghnaq aqsangnaniimalghii taaqumalghii.
Tawani nunaami kiyaghsimalghiit.
Qenwat aghnaghaq anglighllagumalghii ama mekelghiiqlu taana.
Maaten ilangani atangat mughulluni iikusimakanga.
Ima tuqumalghii.
Naangatugiminengnagaquulluni tuqusimalghii ellmineng.
Mekelghiighem nayani pimakanga, “Atanka naanka tuqulaghaatut.
Sumeghtaghaghaquten entaqun temngi nunamenniluki.
Whaa uum kenlenganeng aqnighpenani tuqukaq kaapluni kanaghluni meghqulluni taana kiighwyamun mayughaquq.
Aga ataput naaput mayumaat.”
Mekelghiiq unugyagu aanluni tapghaq quulmun miluusaqenni kiighwyakun agaamalghii.
Taaggun tapghaghqun mayuumalghii.
Kaasami aghqutaallghiinun1 ilasimalghii repall teghigniqem puyguluku nayani.
Qesiqun uksughqughaquq.
Tamakut kiighwyat taana mekelghiiq umiilgughtesimakangat.
Qesiqun aanyan mengteghamineng salin nunamelluku yuget ilangita qemisimaat.
Llaaghanwha mayuumalghii.
Ama yuuk kaapegkaq, qemitkaq, suflugaqaq sangami tuqurakegtaqa?
Qayughllagʼqun kiighwyani aghqutaallghiini teghigniqem puywaaqelghiit yuget unguvalleghqateng.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Neghsam Vuvallanga
Iimnanguq kiyaghsimaaq yuuk nuliilek saama nunalgutetuqat.
Naqam mughunniighaqelghii taana yuuk unaaqunneghagu unangegpenani.
Talwa ataasighhaghmeng akuraasigalnguq.
Ilangi unanguutaqelghiit.
Ilangam yuuk taana mughusimalghii.
Mughulluni anglu kaasimakanga.
Kaalluku saaghwakun aqumumalghii.
Tawansimaluku neghsaq nuugumalghii.
Nuugluni yuukpimakanga, “Ramkelasap!” Legan taaqluni mughyugaghsimalghii.
Yuuktaana sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Sameng aagna pii?”
Taagken yugem kengagni tengluglukek kakeghqughyami itegami asingi kanuughqumakangi.
Sumeghtaghaamalghii nuliini waamnnaluku.
Llaaghanwha taglaghyami nuliini pimakanga, “Unangumayaghtunga ima sefkaasimaaq.”
Llaaghnawha nulighhan ugpequmakanga ugini.
Taagken qavaamalghiik.
Unaami unangupiglluku taghtughluni neghluni mughusimalghii.
Mughusalghiimi anglu kaasimakanga.
Kaasamigu saaghwakun aqumumalghii.
Mululuni neghsaq nuugumalghii.
Yugem piyaqenni, ighivgaghniimnanguftuq.
Neghsam taam pilataamakanga, “Ramkelasap!”
Aga mughyugaghsimalghii.
Taagken yuuk nekevluni maligusimalghii neghsamun.
Meghmun ateghyalghiimi teghhanun pesughyukanghituq.
Masisu esghaamakanga aga yuggaq tallileklu ighuleklu takestaaghhaghmeng naqam yugusii aangepiglleghhii.
Qesiqun neghsaaguq.
Yugem taana yuggaq maligsimakanganenglumun.
Iteghyan iteghviganun qineghsalghiimi esghaamakanga yugem taam neghsat vuvallalghiit.
Tesqamaken neghsat nanevgiita yuuk taana pimakanga, “Iitghi esghapagyaghtaa!”
Llaaghanwha yuuk iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni esghapagumakangi.
Nanevgaam neghsam nuliini pimakanga, “Saguyagka tagivaghqek!
Ilagaghnaqunga.”
Nulighhan saguyak tugulukek tuunumakek ugiminun.
Ugingan tugulukek ilagaamalghii, “Qulighhamtaanguq paaaa-aamkut, qulighhaamtaanguq paaaa-aamut, Iyngighhaput mesiighpallaallukii neqniqaqiit!”
Qalghiimalghii, “Qagisavisavisavii, qagisavisavisavii!”
Taagken nanevgaat neghsat aghnaghaat pimakangi, “Aghnaghaat putughutek!”
Llaaghanwha nanevgaq neghsaq aanqusimalghii, “Iquyelqutaa iyaaaa, qaghpalukaa iyaa-aa, manuqelleghaaqaa iyaa-aa!”
Tawa vuvalla qamagsimalghii.
Nanevgaam pimakanga nuliini, “Una yuuk elqwaaghmeng tuunigu.”
Nulighhan yuuk elqwaaghmeng tuunumakanga.
Nanevgaam neghsam yuuk pimakanga, “Qaa uggnaqegkuvek quunqaamaghpek qesiiqaamaghpek uuglleghhaaten.
Ima naten pinaaghtut elqwaaghet.”
Llaaghanwha yuuk aanluni mayuumalghii.
Uggnaqsami quunqaamaghmi uugsimalghii saama elqwaaghet llimakangi.
Esghaamakangi neghsalghutet.
Yugem nuliini ungipaalluku angaghquumakangit qamaglluki.
Taawa taam kenlenganeng yuuk taana unangyughighllagumalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Meteghlluk Nulightuqaq Ayuqlit Aghniitneng
Iimnanguq, kiyaghsimaat tallimat mengteghat.
Taakut mengteghat yugi anglegutkullghiit.
Naqam kelulighneghhitni kiyaghlleghhiik meteghllugenkuk nengyuqutalghiik.
Ilangani nuyekliimpaniga meghtaamalghii.
Imighimaluku meteghlluk kaasimalghii.
Meteghllugempimakanga, “Meqpakpayay, meqpakpayay!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaam meghsimakanga.
Meteghlluk meghnaqsalghiimi meq nunamun kuuvumakanga.
Aghnaghaampimakanga, paatgumaan, “Saa una meq imighutaa piqpigutaa.”
Meteghllugem akisimakanga, “Piyaqtaqpenguyoy, piyaqtelqen taana miqiitiguu!”
Aghnaghaam akisimakanga, “Miqiningilak, taskwigu.”
Aghnaghaq atghaamalghii ama meteghlluk ellmeggnun taglaamalghii.
Meteghlluk kaalluni nengyuni pimakanga, “Ukaanguten ukaaghen aqfaqughhu.”
Aghnalqwaaghhaq aanluni mengteghanun sivulighpigaghnun kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aapsimakangat, “Saaqsin?”
Aghnalqwaaghem akisimakanga, “Eltughaghma ukaangnilunga piyaghaanga.”
Yugem llilasimakanga ngepeghakun savigmeng pilagesqelluku.
Pilagumakangat.
Aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Unaami uyuqliim yugem paniga meghtaamalghii.
Imighimaluku kaasimalghii megheghlluk ighivgaghtaq.
Meteghllugem pimakanga, “Meqpakpayay, meqpakpayay!”
Llaaghanwha meghsimakanga.
Taawanginaq kuuvumakanga.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, paatgumaan, “Saa una meq imnghuta piqpigutaa.”
“Piyaqtaqpenguyoy, piyaqtelqen taana miqiitiguu!”
“Miqinningilaqa taskwigu!”
Aghnaghaq atghaamalghii.
Metelghlluk taglaamalghii ellmeggnun.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni nengyuni pimakanga, “Ukaanguten ukaaghen aqfaqugu.”
Aghnalqwaaghhaq atghaamalghii.
Tunglighhiitgun manteghanun kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan aapsimakangat, “Saaqsin sangavek tagizin?”
Aghnalqwaaghhaam akisimakangi, “Eltughaghma ukaangnilunga piyaghaanga.”
Akisimakangat, “Uquklukuughaquq, anaqlukaguq mekesitaghaguq.”
Saama savigmeng nepeghhakek pilagumagkek, saama ketngikek pilagumakegket.
Qiyamaghmi aghnalqwaaq taglaamalghii.
Qenwat aghnalqwaaghhaam qengakekpuuvumakek.
Unaami enraq pingayiita mengteghaat aghnaghaat meghtaghta.
Imighimaluku meteghlluk kaasimalghii.
Kaalluni meghsingllaamalghii, “Meqpakpayay, meqpakpayay!”
Llaaghanwha meghsimakanga.
Taawanginaq kuuvumakanga.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, paatgumaan, “Saa una meq imighutaa piqpigutaa.”
“Piyaqtaqpenguyoy, piyaqtelqen taana miqiitiguu!”
“Miqinningilaqa taskwigu!”
Aghnaghaq atghaamalghii.
Meteghlluk taglaamalghii ellmeggnun.
Iteghluni aghnalqwaaq pimakanga, “Ukaanguten ukaaghen aqfaqugu.”
Ighsamalghii.
Meteghllugem sagiqusimakanga.
Aghnalqwaaghhaq pingayiitnun mengteghanun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni uyatuluni amigmeng pimakangi, “Eltughaghma ukaangnilunga piyaghaanga.”
Anqaghlluteng savigmeng qengakek pilagumakegket.
Aghnalqwaaghhaq qiyamaghmi aglaamalghii.
Taagken unugyagu qavaamalghiik.
Unaami estamiita mengteghaat aghnaghaq meghtaamalghii.
Imighimaluku meteghlluk kaasimalghii.
Kaalluni meghsingllaamalghii, “Meqpakpayay, meqpakpayay!”
Llaaghanwha meghsimakanga.
Taawanginaq kuuvumakanga.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, paatgumaan, “Saa una meq imighutaa piqpigutaa.”
“Piyaqtaqpenguyoy, piyaqtelqen taana miqiitiguu!”
“Miqinningilaqa taskwigu!”
Aghnaghaq atghaamalghii.
Meteghlluk taglaamalghii ellmeggnun.
Iteghluni aghnalqwaaq pimakanga, “Ukaanguten ukaaghen aqfaqugu.”
Ighsamalghii.
Meteghllugem sagiqusimakanga.
Llaaghanwha aghnalqwaaghhaq aglaamalghii estamiitnun mengteghanun.
Kaalluni uyatuluni pimakangi, “Eltughaghma ukaangnilunga piyaghaanga.”
Taakut malighqaghluku qengakek savigmeng pilagumakegket.
Aghnalqwaaghhaq qiyamaghmi aglaamalghii.
Unugumakanga.
Qavaamalghiik.
Unaami taghtuumalghiit taam nunam yugi.
Taagken enraq tallimiita mengteghaat aghnaghaq meghtaamalghii.
Imighimaluku meteghlluk kaasimalghii.
Kaalluni meghsingllaamalghii, “Meqpakpayay, meqpakpayay!”
Llaaghanwha meghsimakanga.
Taawanginaq kuuvumakanga.
Aghnaghaam pimakanga, paatgumaan, “Saa una meq imighutaa piiqpigutaa.”
“Piyaqtaqpenguyoy, piyaqtelqen taana miqiitiguu!”
“Miqinningilaqa taskwigu!”
Aghnaghaq atghaamalghii.
Meteghlluk taglaamalghii ellmeggnun.
Iteghluni aghnalqwaaq pimakanga, “Ukaanguten ukaaghen aqfaqugu.”
Ighsamalghii.
Meteghllugem sagiqusimakanga.
Llaaghanwha atghaamalghii.
Kaalluni amigmeng uyatupiglluni pimakangi, “Eltughaghma ukaangnilunga piyaghaanga.”
Talwa akuzimaghmi qimagumalghii.
Iwernga aghnaghaam atangan panini aangghumakanga.
Aghnaghaq taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghyalghiimi kagpestaaghhaaftut.
Taagken aghnaghaq qiyamalghii.
Aghaghaq qavaamalghii.
Aghnalqwaaghhaam aghnaghaq qiyalghii esghaghluku atuumaghmi aghulayalghiimi mengteghani anglisimakanga saama iqangitesimakanga.
Taana eltughaa yupigughsimalghii ama taanallu aghnalqwaaq.
Aghnaghaq unaami taghtughyalghiimi imani enngaatall pinipigtut.
Taagken aghnalqwaaghhaam awalightiisqumakanga quyngimeng.
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaq awalightuumalghii.
Tuuneghminiki aghnaghaat ilangi piiqelghiit, “Ipa whanga piksaghaqa.”
Llaaghanwha aklungighimalghiit saama yupigughsimalghiit.
Qamagtuq, Tefaay.
Naayghami Kiyaghtaaq Quurkeli Meteghlluk
Iimnanguq kiyaghsimalghii Tannget umiilgat quyngightupiglleghhii.
Quyngii uglapiglleghhii.
Naqam taana umiilek ighnelek.
Maaten ilangani umiilgem quyngii avegluni iilaamalghii naqam umegneghughsimalghii qevuutepiglluni.
Naayghami kiyaghsimalghii Quurkeli ighnelek maalghugegneng, nuyekliq ighnegha aghnaasiq, uyughaa itagnalghii.
Maaten ilangani aanyalghiimi nuyekliq esghaasimalghii quyngimeng uglapiglleghhiimeng.
Iteghluni atani Quurkeli pimakanga, “Saam qakemna quyngiqagu?”
“Enta amigmun aliightaghtigu.”
Atani piyatni nuyekliim igheghan ivgaasimakanga.
Atangan pimakanga, “Aa, Tannget umiilgita quyngiqaat.”
Uyuqliq ighneni pimakanga, “Aa, naqam Tengagergemun pii, whaten pinaken, ‘saamnguq una quyngiqagu?’
Ungipaaskangaten ukiggaaten.”
Llaaghanwha uyuqliq mayuumalghii mayuumalghii.
Qaygeghsamigu tamana mengteghaam kiwatangitni neghniighumalghii.
Tengagergem panini pimakanga, “Weni esghapakaghaqluten sangwaat tagiyaaghtut.”
Aghnaghaq aanluni esghaamakanga meteghlluk.
Aghnaghaq iteghluni Tengagergen pimakanga, “Taawanginaq inga esghaghaqa meteghlluk.”
“Aqfagu tagilinguq.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaam aqfamakanga.
Kaalluni aghnaghaam meteghlluk pimakanga, “Atama whanga agliisqaaten.”
Meteghllugem quulmun esghaqaghluku uuglluni neghumalghii.
Aghnaghaq aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghluni atani pimakanga, “Avelghaqinaghaanga.”
Atangan pimakanga, “Kevgaangukuninguq tagili sukalluni!”
Aghnaghaam takuluku pimakanga meteghlluk, “Kevgaangukuvegnguq aglaa sukalluten!”
“Whaten pigu saamnanguq saam quyngiqagu.”
Aghnaghaq aglaghluni pimakanga atani, “Piiten whaten, saamnanguq saam quyngiqagu.”
Atangan panini pimakanga, “Wanlegi whaten pigu, tagilinguq ellmineng.”
Aghnaghaam aglaghluni meteghlluk pimakanga, “Aglanguq sukalluten!”
Meteghlluk aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghyan Kiyaghneghem Tengagergem pimakanga, “Sangwaami piiqsigu?”
“Saam saamna quyngiqagu.”
Tengagergem naniq awilluku esghaghyalghiimi meteghlluk asitmun esghaamakangi mengtegham saaghwani quyngit ama Tannget.
Tengagergem pimakanga, “Esgha taakusta Tannget taana quyngiqaat.”
Meteghlluk neneghmeng taaqluni aanluni ukigumalghii.
Uuglluni ellmegteggun, pimakanga atani, “Whangkutanguq pikaghput.”
Atangita pimakanga, “Naqam tuqutiightek!”
Uyughaqullghiik aanlutek tuqutiighumalghiik.
Tuqusimakegket angepaaghrugllagek.
Itghulluki neghumakangat.
Taaqsamek uyughaqullghiik aanumalghiik.
Aanlutek quyngimi nayughimalghiik.
Tannget qemguumalghiit.
Qaghlughimalghiit sughuginaluteng.
Taaqsameng Tannget ghhataamalghiit.
Ivaghimalghiit.
Taawanginaq taananginaghhaq mayiigalkangat.
Umiilek mayuumalghii tumiighaqluni.
Uuglluni aglaamalghii.
Umiilgem quyngit esghaghnaqutnginaq liisuqumakangi.
Esghaallutek mekelghiighek uyughaqullghiik atayeng pimakangat, “Aqelqaq qakma!”
“Weni iitghesqiiteggu!”
Aanyagʼta Tannget umiilgita aapsimakangi, “Saam una quyngiqagu?”
“Whangkuta!”
Alla aaplaataamakangi, “Waniwanllu, esghaataghtaqiten quyngimeng?”
“Waniwanllu!”
Tannget aga qiivluteng ukigyalghiimeng aga quyngighteng ukigusiimakangat qamagaghlluku.
Taawanginaq ellngita quyngigket siipsimalghiik.
Mekelghiighek taakuk amigughimalghiik iwernga paninang ukigusimakangi.
Uyuqliq iitghaghlluni ilagaamalghii.
Qukaghsamigu atghaghaataghaamalghii.
Atghaghaataghluni anuqa tuqluumakanga qanigpagtuumaghmi umegneghtuumaan.
Tannget naqam umegneghughsagu quyngiteng sighunghitgun qepumakangit.
Mekelghiighem Quurkelim ighneghan taana quyngiq mayuusimakanga naaygham nangaghutellghanun.
Uuggusamigu tuqluumakanga anuqa umegneghtuumaan qanigilnguq.
Anuqlighyaqenni taana nangaghtelleq anigu suupumakanga.
Tannget umiilgita ilagaghluni taana naayghaq kaavesimakanga.
Kaavyan quynighteng veghsimakangat.
Veghhneghmeng taaqsamigu taana naayghaq naallghutesimakanga nekegneghatun.
Ima Quurkelinkut avangiisimalghiit quyngiighusimalghiit.
Quurkeli ungipaasimakangat, “Quyngighput aga ukigusimaat!”
Quurkeli nuugluni Tengagergen Kiyaghneq tuqluumakanga.
Ukigumalghii.
Quurkelim pimakaanga, “Saamkut sama quyngighput ellngita pinaqaat.
Kayusiqaghkut.”
“Kayusighnaanghitamsi.
Tawaten pinghitamsi elpenun quyngiqniluku!”
Aga ima mayuumalghii.
Legan Quurkeli pilugugtuq.
Ukigumalghii.
Taawa yugtuftut.
Umiilgem llilasimakangat piigiisqelluku.
Llaaghanwha piiguqaqumakangat iwernga tuqutegpenaan.
Legan taaqsatni taghnughhaq qavalghii puvugyaqenni tuqulluku.
Umiilgem esghaghluku tuqulghii taghnughhani Quurkeli pimakanga, “Ilagaa maamestigu.”
“Pinaanghitunga.”
“Tuqutinnayaghamken.”
“Wetku quyngighsi avegluku tagivaqufsigu taawa unguvaghlleqaqa.”
Pimakangat, “Yeghrat tawaatesigatut alignaghngaaghmeng!”
Quurkeli aangghumalghii.
“Aaaa, naqam ilagaghlanga.”
Ilagaamalghii.
Ilagaghluni atghaghaataghaamalghii.
Atghaghaataghluni mayuumalghii.
Mayughluni iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni ighneni pimakanga, “Sama quyngimatiinkut.”
Aanlutek ukiglutek esghaghyaqeseng quyngiq avegluni ayuqeftuq palaghhaq ilanga, ilanga uglalghii.
Uyuqliim pimakanga nuyekliq, “Uglallgha tugulteggu!”
Aangghumalghii.
Naqam paghqiteftut.
Yugiteftuq.
Legan mayuusimakangat.
Mayuumaluki umiilgem ighneghan malighqaamakangi.
Meteghllugek utaqamakangat.
Kaasan tuqusimakangat.
Umiilgem esghaghluku ighneni tuqulghii yuni pimakangi, “Aagkuk wayaghtekek!”
Llaaghanwha kaalluki wayaghluki quyngiteng piigughtamakangat tuqutegpenaki.
Naqam anuqliimakanga umegneghughsimalghii qevuulluni.
Mayughnaqsalghiimek aghtuumalghiik.
Mayuneghmegni, nagneghaqelghiik amavek naaygham awatanganun mengteghaghteng naghughlluku.
Tawaten kiyaghsimalghiik.
Ivganeghmegni nagneghaqluteng.
Iwemga pegnem uugsimalghiik.
Nuyekliim atanillu uyughanillu pimakangek, “Yeghrat elpesineng naafqestaghpesinga!”
Llaaghanwha nuyekliq tuqumalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay!
Afsengaghhaq
Iimnanguq, afsengaghhaq meqsaghtuumalghii naayvam qukaanun.
Meghumalghii anglaaghhaq ukilluku.
Meneghmeng taaqluni aqumumalghii anglaaghem saaghwani.
Meghnaalimalghii tawani.
Meghnaalimaluku paapga kumlatusimakanga.
Ilagaamalghii inqunamen papeni ghhataghtesqelluku, “Kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, ukigem talatanga!
Kiyayuvaghluktungaaaa!
Amiqluk pikrungaaaaaa, taymanalukaa, kalalikaaaa, taymanalukaa, kalalikaaaa.”
Taaqumalghii ilaganeghmeng.
Sunanguq taana amiqluggaq ketfaghaghta.
Afsengaghhaam pimakanga, “Awiiten!
Uuynituten!”
Amiqluggaq aghulaqumalghii.
Allameng ilagaghlaataamalghii, “Kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, ukigem talatanga!
Kiyayuvaghluktungaaaa, sikik pikrungaaaaaa, taymanalukaa, kalalikaaaa.”
Sunanguq taana sikiggaq ketfaghta.
Afsengaghhaam pimakanga, “Awiiten!
Papegtuuten!”
Sikiggaq aghulaqumalghii.
Allameng ilagaghlaataghtuq, “Kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, ukigem talatanga!
Kiyayuvaghluktungaaaa, ukaziq pikrungaaaaaa, taymanalukaa, kalalikaaaa.”
Sunanguq taana ukazighhaq ketfaghta.
Afsengaghhaam pimakanga, “Awiiten!
Paapgen mekestaaghhaaguq!”
Ukazighhaq aghulaqumalghii.
Allameng ilagaghlaataghtuq, “Kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, kanakiii, ukigem talatanga!
Kiyayuvaghluktungaaaa, kaynga pikrungaaaaaa, taymanalukaa, kalalikaaaa.”
Sunanguq taana kayngeghllak ketfaghaghta.
Ketfaatkelluku afsengaghhaq paatgumakanga.
Paapga kepkaamakanga.
Tawaten kayngem afsengaghhaq kayusiimakanga.
Qamagtuq tefaay.
Mayeraaghpak
Aghnaghaghhaat tallimat aghulaghquumalghiit.
Mayeraaghpagem esghaghluki takumakangi.
Kaalluki ratamiiregnun kanaghquusimakangi.
Unaghsighllagmun petugumakangi.
Taaqluki piyaqenni, “Unaqekaa!”
Unaghsiq taklaaghaghsimalghii.
Unilluku aglaamalghii.
Tawaten kiyaghsimaluki aga kayngeghllak naghughsimalghii.
“Kayngeghllak aagyuq llaghan yuggayengaalghiiten itemuteqaghtikut!”
“Neghniimsugumaluta yugpesi unaknaqaqiinkut.”
“Saqrugtaquq aagna!”
Aganguq meteghlluruk naghughsimalghii.
“Meteghlluruk aagyuq llaghanyuggayengaalghiiten, itemuteqaghtikut.”
“Itemuteqaghhnaanghitamsi.
Aantani neghniimsunemta milughpagaataghaqaghpesikut.”
Aga kaviighhaq naghughsimalghii.
“Kaviighhaq aagyuq llaaghan yuggayengaalghiiten itemuteqaghtikut!”
“Itemuteqaghhnaaqamsi.”
Takuluki aapsimakangi, “Naten piiqisi?”
Aghnaghaghhaat apeghtuumakanga, “Pigu uqfik, unaqekaa!”
Kaviighhaam pimakanga, “Unaqekaa!”
Unaghsighllak agughaghsimalghii.
Itemusimakangi.
Aanleghaasimalghiit.
Tallimaghteng taghsaneghemng aghtughluku alininguq unisimakangat.
Taakuk ratamiirek qilevrimeng kevighlukek qimagusimalghiit.
Mayeraaghpagem ulaani ipegsaghluku takumakangi.
Kaalluni aliin inglunga pilagumakanga.
Pagunghaat ifaquusimalghiit.
“Iyeruuget, iyeruuget!”
Inglunga pilagyaqenni aghnaghaghhaam iqelqwa kepqaghsimakanga.
Enkaam qiyamalghii, “Keka keka kumaghqughtekelleqaghpenga!”
“Sangan uveglluten ungipannaaghsinga.”
Aglaalluku itghusimakanga.
“Apay, aanaghllanga.”
“Samengqun kamegluten atkugluten?”
“Kamegllagegken atkugllagen aallukek.”
Aanesimakanga uqeghhmun uyatiighluku.
Aanluni tawansimaluku yuggaak tapghami esghaamakek.
Aghnaghaghhaq pimalghii, “Yuggagka aliighhaghtuk aaaa tapghameng aaaa aliqaghtuq aaaa aallgha panalek aallgha pitegsitalek!”
“Panikellemaay sameng piiqsin?”
“Aatak naghuyaqellaankuk meteghlluglliqellaankuk piiqagka!”
Taagken yugek kaallutek itemlluku qimagusimakangat aghnaghaghhaq.
Mayeraaghpagem tuqluumakanga, “Panikellemaay, panikellemaay.”
Qaalkaamangituq.
Aanyalghiimi aga uyavaatusimakangat aghnaghaghhaq.
Taagken malighqaamakangi.
“Iitegʼqun kaaskumsi neghelleqegkemsi!”
Qimaginaamaluki kaasaghtumakangi.
“Aghnaghaghhaaghmi siingenllu tughneghaaghtekalghiiten sanaqi!”
Uyghagmeng tugulluni napaghsaqenni naayghaghllak taaqaa aghvighvigilnguq avangilnguq.
Pegnem mayeraaghpagem mayughluku malighqaatakangi kaasaghtughyateng, “Aghnaghaghhaq siingenllu tughneghaaghtekaaguten, sanaqi!”
Iqelqughhani tawekenga qiipumalghii suupumaan nuna tereghyaqenni kiiwhllagek taaqumakek.
“Panikellemaay naten aghvighlagngek?”
“Meghlukek!”
Meghyaqegni meghyaqegni pimakanga, “Iitek tawa naangsaghtughagken!”
Qamagllukek nekevumalghii aqsaghllani qamuqluku esleqem angtalanganeng.
Pimakanga aghnaghaghhaam, “Apay sangan pikavek uusneghwaaghem qaaynganun putughyanghisin?”
Mayeraaghpak mayughluni nutaan talligni quulmun nengugusaghaak aqsanga quupaghaghsimaaq.
Quupaghaghsalghiimi qayungllaasiq, qayusiq, signeghwaaq, qaltaq legan allaghhiinaq sanqutraaq.
Qamagtuq.
Tallimat Ngelqat
Kiyaghsimalghiik yugenkuk nulighqullghiik.
Taghnughhiilnguuk avangilnguuk.
Uginga quyngini esghapagyaghtughaqegkanga.
Ilangani maaten piyaamalghii quyngiminun.
Tallimat ngelqat esghaamakangi.
Takuyaqenni tengenghitut.
Kaalluki tuguluki atghaamalghii.
Kaasan nulighha quyamalghii.
Itghusimakangi.
Uginga esnamun pimalghii kinguvzeghanun iqalluganun.
Llaaghanwha taglaghyalghiimi saghnaamalghii.
Llaaghanwha neghusimalghiit ngelqat.
Unaami taghtughluteng unilluki ngelqateng aanumalghiik.
Nulighha esnamun pimalghii kinguvzeghanun iqalluganun.
Taglaamalghii.
Iiwenllu mengteghamun kaasaghtughaquq atughllagmeng nagaquusimalghii.
“Pagellegraay, pagellegraay, singtseraay, niquraangaangaaaa aangaa iyaanangaa.”
Iitqestaghluni iiyakun qineghsalghiimi mekelghiighet estamat atughaqeftut ataasiq aghulaaqeftuq amiirateng mataghlluki.
Itqaghlluni amiiriitgun aqumqaghsimalghii.
Pngighsiimakangi.
Llaaghanwha uginga taaqumalghii quyngimun pineghmeng.
Taakut mekelghiighet ellngita taghnughhaqumakangit.
Yuggaq Unangyiilnguq Enkaam Nanuq
Iimnanguq yuggaq kiyaghsimalghii nunaaghmi enngaatall unangyiitepiglleghhii.
Ilangi mughutalgutangi unangaqelghiit ellnga mughulluni taglaneghmini avangunani.
Nulighha qagani nunalgutmeggnun tungsighniighaqelghii.
Nunalgutangita unangkaqegkangat neghsaq, maklak, ayveq, nanuq.
Ellnga yuggaq sakengigalnguq.
Maaten ilangani mughulluteng taanʼganlluki anuqliisimakangi.
Mughutat nanughaghluteng amiiriqiinaghluku anuqliisisteng taglaamalghiit.
Enraq alla yuggaq unangyiitalghii iikusimakanga.
Aghtughluni aghvighnaqneghmeng inglunganun tungemeggnun ellmeng, ketmun anagumalghii iighwillghaanun.
Kaasami angalghunun aglaghluni tawani nenglungllaghluni iitghumalghii.
Tesqamani aqumgaamaluku nagaquusimalghii uka alighumalghii ghhuunaqeghllak sangwaa.
Yuggaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Uuk, enraq alla iflamayalghiinga.
Sangwaa uukna tagii?”
Ukanguq legan piiquq, “Ghuutaanga ghuutepigtaanga!”
Iiwen yuggaq qineghhnaqaquq suna taana nanughllak amiiriilnguq, enngaatall ghhuunaqaqeftuq.
Nanuq pimalghii, “Yuggaq uyuq navghitaghtinga pilugugpeneng ghhuutepigtaanga.”
Yuggaam pimakanga, “Samengqun navghillaken?”
“Esghaataakuk atkugken” “Ukuuk?”
“Nakaa ilanga!”
“Ukuuk?”
Keniimakek atkuggaagni iluklighpigaghhaak aliitalghiik nanuum amiiraaneng ulimaaghek.
Nanuum aanghumakanga.
Yuggaam mataghllukek tuunumakek.
Nanuum pimakanga, “Tagi maligtinga!”
Yuggaam maligsimakanga.
Quuputegnun kaallutek yuggaam atuquvinghaakek nanuum meghmun neplukek nusugyaqegni ellngaatmeng maaqumalghnk mesiighllugmeng nuyiilleq maligulluni.
Nanuum pimakanga, “Qayughllak unangaqi nulighhen ukiniiqelghii ellngaasiimaghmi nuyiighumaghmi llaaghanwha ukiniiq taaqegkanga nukeggnaq maligulluku.”
Qafsinaneng neptaghllukek ukmangiisagtaa alla neplukek nusugyaqegni nanuum amiiraghllaga nusugumakanga.
Taagken nanuum pimakanga, “Wiin mengteghamnun maligtinga!
Enan taglaannaaghamken.”
Nanuum amiiraghllak aalluku yuggaankuk aghulaqumalghiik.
Ketmiighsimalghiik.
Quuputet kaanneghmegteki nanuum yuggaq amaghluku aghviitaqegkanga.
Iiwen maamlegtaqaa nanuum nenganun kaasimalghiik.
Nanuum pimakanga, “Tawa kaatukut iitghaaten.”
Iteghlutek neneghmeng taaqlutek qavaamalghiik.
Unaami qakma tenglugtuumakangit, “Naagu qaamna?”
“Taawa” “Aaam aanelghaaten.”
“Qaywa aanaqunga.”
Yuggaq nanuum pimakanga, “Enngaatall esgha qakmun amyuutkaqegkanganga aqnighqughlunga.
Maamestegpenanga itagnatun aqfaqegkanganga tughumghalgutngulunga.”
Yuggaam aanaqsan ipegsalleghmeng igaamakanga qenleghwaaghakun.
Nanuq aanumalghii.
Tagigpenani muluyan yuggaq agipaneghqun qineghsimalghii.
Maalghuk nanuuk enngaatall tugutaqeftuk.
Nutem aallgha pekaamalghii igaqaa aqumluni lliighumalghii.
Aallghan pategpagataghaqeftaa.
Yuggaam ughlufghani yataghqelluku pitegsaqenni unakumakanga aallgha.
Nanuq pategmikestaghngaaghmi ullghaghsimalghii.
Uullghaghsan aallghan esghapagtuumakanga.
“Saa una?”
Esghapagtuqestaghngaaghmigu esghaamakek aaygum taghrughhakek uunghaneng aliillutek.
Aagtuqaqeftuqlu kiimineng.
Yuggaq aanluni tazingavek aglaamalghii.
Kaasan nanuum tukaan aapsimakanga yuggaq, “Sazigu?”
“Sanghitaqa!”
“Taawa amyuqetaghteka unakan.
Whaken kenlanga pinitun kiyaghsagunnaqunga.
Maamegkuma nunavnun aglaalleqamken saama unangyughisleqamken.”
Nanughllak nekevluni pegnem aglaamalghii.
Yuggaam maligsimakanga.
Iteghyan tamakut amiiraan makregaghtallghi saghnaamakangi.
Yuggaam mategtaqluki ukinighteghumakangi.
Apeghiighyamigu aanluni yuggaam tuqutkani nanuq aftamakanga.
Neqanganeng neqekumalghii maamneghsiitkelluku tukuni.
Llaaghanwha maamyami nanuum yuggaq taglaasimakanga.
Aghvighyat kaanneghmegteki nanuum amaghaqegkanga yuggaq.
Yugaam nunanganun quutmun kaasaghtughyamek ununeghsimakangat.
Wetku unugyagu nanuum yuggaq quutmun maallgusimakanga.
Uugsan yuggaq nanuq qiivluni ketmiighsimalghii.
Yuggaq mengteghaminun taglaamalghii.
Taagken kenlanga yuggaq unangyiitkuvinghaaq unangyughqaamakanga.
Qamagtuq.
Yuuk Napaqutaghhmii
Yuuk Napaqutaghhmii qayaghtuumalghii pennam tunganganun.
Igleghutkelluku esghaamakangi angyat kaalgulghiit aghveghmeng.
Kaalluki esghaghsaqsaghtuq.
Esghanghitaat.
Yuggaq sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Naguntuq aghveghteng maallgunnaqatgu?
Esgha maligsaqumki.”
Yuggaam kaalgulghiit kingungitneng maligsimakangi.
Esnamun kaalluteng yuggaq esghapagyalghiimi nunaq allaq nunakenghilkaminun tamlagtuq.
Esnamun uuglluni qayani sayugluku esghapagyalghiimi atghaghtuullghiit yuget nutaan esghaghii.
Aghveq pilagumakangat.
Qepghalghiit akulangitni yuuk esghapagumalghii.
Kituraaggaam kiimsiqigalkaanga.
Aaguteghngaaghmegteggu esghiigalkangat.
Aghnam taghnughhalgem ugini tuqlughluku pimakanga, “Panigen atalughaataghtigu.”
Llaaghanwha yugem panmi atalughaalluku atalughat miluusimakangi nuliighmi manunganun.
Atalughat tuusata yugem tuusimakangi.
Aghnam iiliigii atalughat.
Ivaamakangi uvitmini.
Maaten agavek sayan isekiyugesqelluku aghnaq yugem, atalughat tuguluki ggatmeghruganun lliyaghii.
Aga atalughat amighreganun kiighisimalghiit.
Aghnaq araamalghii agrepeniluni ggatmeghrugmikun.
Ugingan tagiluni qamiyegnegun qaakluku taglaasimakanga.
Kingungitneng yuuk maligulluni taglaamalghii.
Tumangani kaasimakanga aghnaq qamiyegnegun mangtagmeng usiluni qamumeng taglaghaqeftuq.
Yugem kaasamigu aqumumalghii qamiyegnegun.
Aghnaq igleghhneghmeng aghtughyagusimalghii.
Piiq aghnaq, “Sangamek qamuqagka qamiyek sangyaghqwaagakek?
Agnepa meghnughyingalghiinga.”
Aghnaq aghuliighluni meghnaalimalghii.
Yuuk qamiyegneng nekevluni taglaamalghii.
Mengteghanun kaalluni qineghsalghiimi aghnaq gaaghaqeftuqneqmeng.
Taawa saaghwani qayutam qaayngani ugket ugimneghhat.
Yuukpimalghii, “Aghnaq uyuq ugkevneng tuunaghtinga.
Igatapigtunga.”
“Kaay aviigaanga,” aghnaq pimalghii.
Uraamra ugkemeng tungsilghii.
Yuuk pimalghii, “Tawani aviigi!”
Qayutameng tugusimalghii ugkemeng.
Aghnaq pilaataghtuq, “Kaaaay sullevnaghhalek aviilaataghaanga aleghqupigmeng!
Weni ugkeka aga tenguq ima aga aanuq!
Kaaaay entaqun imgaghtunga!”
Yugem ugka aanulluku uqeghhmi neghumakanga.
Ugka qamagsamigu ilangitnun mengteghanun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni aqumumalghii amigem iiqngaakun.
Maalghuk aghnaghaak neqmeng inglugtaalghiik esnameng kaallutek mengteghamun neqa itghututkelluku aghnaghaak kangsughaataamalghiik amigmi.
Pimalghiik, “Sangami amigput kagpellighaghta?”
Yuuk esghaghsaqneghmeng mataawiiq.
Taagken mengteghaneng aglaamalghii aqnightelget mengteghiitnun.
Kaalluni uuqghitni nagasimalghii paninang aghnaq qama enngaatall ngillegtaqeftuq.
Alignalghiit qanemsukayuget mataawisimakangat naallghunneghmeng.
Qama yuukpimalghii, “Enta enraq iigna aqfaaghtigu.
Enannguq akilighnaghaqa ellngan nakmikegkaneng.”
Yuuk uqeghhmi nekevghalghii naghughtam kiimsiqiigalkanga qayughllagʼqun esghiigalkangat.
Tawani uqeghhmi nekevghaamaluku yugem kinguliiluku aqfastekaa uka tagimalghii.
Yuuk tiigmeraaghmeng pilugukelghii kaasaghtuutni maliglluku yugmun uqeghhmi nekevghalghiimun ayuqluni tagimalghii.
Kaasami pimakanga, “Saam yukaten nakuminguzin sangavek iitghigasin?”
Yugem akisimakanga, “Aghveghmeng kaalgulghiitgun maligullunga tagikaagunga.
Whanga Napaqutaghhmiinguunga.
Nallukaqa naansinga.
Esghaghsaqneghmeng aghtughtunga.
Esghiigataatnga.
Ellngiinaghhaghpek whaa esghaghaghpenga.
Aghneq esnami esghaallunga isekiyukuni aghnam ggatmeghruganun llimayaghanka atalughat.
Taakut esgha agrepesiiqegkangi.”
“Tagi maligtinga qamavek iitgheltung!”
Llaaghanwha iitghumalghiik.
Iteghyan yuuknutaan esghaamakangat.
Yuuk aqfastekaat pimalghii, “Esgha taana aqelqaq maamestineghmeng aghtiigalnguq.
Wetku enraq nunanganun Napaqutamun aglaasaghqaqegkufsigu temeghhneghyaghqaaguq.”
Aqnilghiim aghnam ugina pimalghii, “Ametall aglaatepestaaghlleqaghput.
Nulighqa ikfiqepigtuq.
Temeghhnaqaghlligu.”
Katam taananguftuq aghvengegkat angyalgat.
Yuuk aqelqaq aghnamun aqnilghiimun aglaghluni tunutesluku atalughat aghneq llikani agham ggatmeghruganun amighregaan kiighaneng nusugluki nanim manungakun llimakangi.
Aghnaq igighiyagumalghii.
Mengteghalegtaam yugem aghneq atalughaqani liisuqumakangi.
Unaami yugem tukaan yuni kelgughluki angyaghteng kelluku mangtagmeng usiluku yuuklu aqelqaq qaakluku aglaasimakangat nunanganun qayaa qamuqluku.
Kaatulluku Napaqutamun yuuk esnamun uugsan angyaghteng usingighluku kesimalghiit.
Yuuk kelutmun esghaghluni ketmun qiivluni angyat esghaghnaqsaqenni aviitut.
Katam mesungesaget esghaamakangi.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay!
Meteghllugenkuk Qatelghiinkuk
Kiyaghsimalghiik qemgaagmek meteghllugenkuk qatelghiingiighhaankuk.
Maaten ilangani igaatiqumalghiik.
Unugmi qatelghii aqumluni piluguglum aanumalghii.
Manaatngi tuguluki managhyaamalghii.
Anglaaghmun kaalluni manaatngi ateghlluki manaamalghii.
Manaamaluku manaatngi sama eltughpagusimalghiit.
Qatelghiingiighhaam amumakangi manaatngi.
Ukanguq qiyalghii amumakanga, whaten pimaghmi, “Engaaenga, aqsaka seggiguu!”
Qatelghiingiighhaam qaygeghsaqenni taghnughhaghrukutaaghllak.
Naqam aqsaghllaga.
Savini nusugluku aqsanga segsaqenni iqallugaghllak aqsanganisimalghii.
Akmagtani tuguluku iqallugameng imiimakanga eslemkaghaghlluku.
Imighineghmeng apeghiighyami taghnughhaq ateghlluku meghmun manaatngi imegluki akmagaataghluni taglaamalghn.
Kaalluni iteghyami meteghlluk taghsaghluku neghumalghiik.
Unaami aghneghllutek unugluku qatelghiingiighhaq qavaghyan meteghllugem qatelghiingiighhaam manaatngi teglegluki aanluni managhyaamalghii.
Manaamaluku manaatangi sama eltughpagusimalghiit. 
Amumakangi.
Amumaluki ukanguq taghnughhaq qiyalghii nagaquumakanga.
Meteghllugem manaatngi peglluki qimagumalghii.
Ilangani qatelghiingiighhaq managhyaghnaqsalghiimi manaatangi ima aviitut.
Meteghlluk aapsaqenni kalefsimaniluki pimakangi.
Qatelghiingiighhaq tapghamun piyaamalghii.
Esghaasimalghii mengteghaneng.
Kaalluni mengteghamun, mayughluni iiyakun qineghsalghiimi qama quyngiq uzivaqeftuq.
Nughaghhaq qesighyaqenni uullghaghsimalghii.
Aghnam tuguluku nughaghhaq eslatmun egsimakanga.
Qatelghiingiighhaam ukigluni akmagluku aglaasimakanga.
Unaami enraq meteghlluk tapghamim piyaamalghii.
Mengteghameng esghaalluni aglaghluni iiyaanun mayughluni qineghsalghiimi quyngiq uzivelghii esghaamakanga.
Aangelghiighllak qesighyaqenni uullghaghsimalghii.
Aghnam aanesimakanga.
Meteghlluk ukigluni mengteghameng akmagnaqsaqenni tapghiiteftuq.
Quyngim qilegyingi nusugluki akmagitengllaghnaqsaghtuq enraq amawha kepqaghtut.
Aghtughluni akmaneghmeng qineghlluni mengteghamun tungsiimayalghii aghnamun akmagitkaghaghhaghmeng.
Yaghlegi aghnam yaqiiraagni akuqaghlukek aanluni meteghlluk anaguleghtaamakanga pimaghmi, “Uumlleqa quyngighhaanka tuququghaqegkangi.”
Meteghlluk avangunani aglaamalghii.
Qatelghiingiighhaam pimakanga meteghlluk, “Kii saluten esnegtiqughtaazin?”
Meteghllugem akisimakanga, “Aghnamun akmagitkaghqaghniighnaqlunga quyngiqegkaqa taginnaluku yaghlegi aanqaghlluni anaguleghtaagaanga.”
“Uum nangllekistengiighhaanka seghleghqaqii.”
Neqseng naangyan qatelghiingiighhaq piyaamalghii pennam tunganganun.
Taagani mengteghaq kaalluku iteghyalghiimi yuuk esghaamakanga nuliilek.
Nulighqullghiik amelengestaaghhaak.
Yugem upughasimakanga, “Uuk enankinam aqelqaq!
Nateghmun tawavek iitghi!”
Yugemnuliini pimakanga, “Gaaghutigu aqelqaq qallallukuneghnaqelghii.”
Llaaghanwha qatelghiingiighhaam atkuni mataghlluku iitghumalghiik tukuqullghiik.
Ugket ugusata aghnam itghulluki neghumalghiit.
Neneghmeng taaqsameng pimalghii tukuq, “Aanaghhnaqunga qakmavek.
Sukallunga iteghnaaghtunga.”
Llaaghanwha aga aanumalghii.
Maateqwaaqun sama pimalghii, “Qamay aqelqaq ukavek nuukaa!”
Qatelghiingiighhaq nuugyalghiimi atkuga aasimakanga tukaan.
Llangaqanguq atkuga unaghsiighwaaghmeng nuuvegkaq.
Qatelghiingiighhaampimakanga, “Uukpiiglleqan!
Sangan aasigu?
Sagiqestepigtan!
Esleqaghaghtan!”
Taakut tukii qatelghiingiighhaam sikughwaaghwaaqeftut.
Llaaghanwha sikughwaam yuukumaghmi atkuga aqelqam mataghsimakanga.
Sikughwaaghemnuliini pimakanga, “Aqelqaq aghulaqnaqegkan pirughtinnaken iwerngam kepsullghanun.”
Qavaghluteng unaami qatelghiingiighhaq aghulaqnaqsan sikughwaam nulighhan pirughtisimakanga aqelqaghtengneqmeng iwerngamkepsullghanun.
Qatelghiihgiighhaq akmagaataghluni aglaamalghii.
Kaasan mengteghamun meteghllugem ungipaghsuumakanga, “Kii-i, naken pimghqughtazin?”
“Aagken pennam tunganganeng.”
Unaami meteghlluk piyaamalghii taagavek.
Mengteghaq kaalluku iteghyalghiimi yuuk esghaghaa nuliilek amelengestaaghhaak.
Qesiqun kaataqeftuq sikughwaankunun.
Sikughwaam tukaan upughasimakanga iitghesqumaan ilunganun.
Asanut atkuni unilluku nateghmi, nuliini gaaghesqumaan.
Ugket ugusata neghumalghiit.
Taaqluteng sikughwaaq aanumalghii.
Maateqwaaqun meteghllugem atkuga aalluku sama pimalghii, “Qamay aqelqaq ukaveknuukaa!”
Meteghlluknuugumalghii.
Esghaghluku sikughwaaq nenglaghqwaamalghii, “Hahaha, llangaqa elpekkanaqaruk!”
Sikughwaam aqelqami atkuga mataghlluku nuliini pimakanga, “Taana aqelqaq aanestigu!
Aglaghli!
Pirughtitaghtegpenaan pinaken!”
Llaaghanwha aghnam meteghlluk aanesimakanga.
Aglaamalghii avangunani pirughtangunani.
Taagken kenlanga qatelghiim unisimakanga meteghlluk alla kiyaghtelgutesaghqaagpenaan.
Qamagtuq.
Egeghaghmii
Yuuk Egeghaghmii nukaghalek.
Nuliipiga avaqutiilnguq nukaghaa maalghugneng mekelghiistaghhiinaghneng avaqutalek.
Nukaghaa taana Angetequghhmii.
Angyaghtughaqelghii yuuk nuliipini kelqelluku.
Yuuk angyaneghmini aghvengaqelghii.
Aghvengneghmini nukaghani miitistekaqegkanga.
Aghvengneghmini ataasit pilakat tuunaqegkangi neghyaghqaaluki nukaghaghminun.
Elkek nuliipikullghiik neghaqelghiik quyngimeng.
Maaten ilangani angyaghyata aghnam ighneni nuyekliq pimakanga, “Angyaput taglaghyaghqat esghapagki.
Uka aliiqata ungipinnakevnga.”
Aghnam siighnam aqeftaghaa imiimakanga meghmeng.
Ilanga mangtagmeng avegtuulluku saama ugimi ilangan nuliipigan iighaaneng quyngimeng tugulluni avegtughluni ilamakangi mangtaget avegtughani.
Enkaam uyuqliim taghnughhaghmi ilanga makanga imiimakanga peqameng tukrulghiimeng siimiitnguluku.
Iiwen unugyaghtughaqaa ighneghan nuyekliim ungipaasimakanga uka taglaghniluki angyat.
Iitghesqumakanga ighneni.
Iteghyan neghesluku taagken atghiisqumakanga esnamun.
Angyat tamlagyalghiimeng aghvengumalghiit.
Angyalgita yuni llilamakanga nukaghani aqfasqelluku, “Aghvengumakunnguq, miitiyaghtughlinguq.”
Kevgaaq taglaghluni ungipaasimakanga uginganun aqfasniluku miitiyaghtiisqelluku.
“Aaa atghaghnaqunga.”
Utaqamakangat.
Naagu?
Atghanghituq.
Itagnatun yugem aqfasimakanga, “Sukalluninguq atghaghli.
Ghhuutiinguq.”
Kevgaaq taglaghluni ungipaasikaanga aghnaq.
Aghnam pimakanga kevgaaq, “Enraq taghnughhaqa qiyaaquq, atghaghaqnayaghtunga.”
Kevgaaq atghaghluni angyalek ungipaasimakanga.
Angyalgem nulipigan ugini pimakanga, “Whanga puughtisaghtughlakun miitiyaghtughnaqelghii.”
Aangghumakanga.
Aghnaq taglaamalghii.
Nukaghaam aksaqluni esghapagumakanga taglalghii.
Kaalluni nutaan qineghsan anaguumakanga naasqwakun tuqulluku.
Tuqusamigu angyaatani akmagluki avaqutani tuguluku qimagumalghii Mayeghagnekun.
Qaygeghsami uyghagem akulanganun iighumalghii.
Siingenllu unukanga.
Aghvengegkat utaqiiyaghluteng esnami utaqakaghteng aviisan yuuk taglaghyalghiimi nuliipini esghaamakanga tuquluni amigmi naqam nukaghaa aviituq.
Yuuk atghaghluni yuni llilamakangi ivaghiyaghtiisqelluki.
Ivaghyaqeseng mamlegmi esghanghitaat.
Aviituq.
Aviisan uteghqaasimalghiit.
Aghnaq angyataghqelluni apeghiighyami ukigumalghii esnamun.
Esnamun kaalluni meghnaalitkelluku tulughaamalghii.
Tulughaatkelluku nagaquumakangi suqsughtalghiit.
Enkaam kana nallangakun qenaaghtallasimalghiit.
Pimalghiit, “Piiksuq!
Saaqsin tawani?”
Aghnam akisimakangi, “Angetequmun aglaghyugaqsaghtunga, iwemganaten aglaghlanga.”
“Tagi uugten!
Angetequghhmiinguukut, aglaannaqamken.”
Aghnaq angyamun uugsimalghii.
“Quneghlleghhaaten!”
Taagken itagnatun suqsughtameng aghnaq nagasimalghii.
Maateqwaaqun pilataghaat, “Aaam esghaghhaaten aga uugten!”
Aghnaq uuglluni piyalghiimi Angetequunghilnguq allaq nuna.
Maaten angyaqfini uteghmun esghaghyaqenni aga mesungesaget puugleghaataqeftut.
Taagken aghnaq kelutmun esghaghyalghiimi nenglughrukutaaq pika esghaamakanga tunuqliqluku nenglusqughhaq.
Nenglughllagem qaayngani nekevghaaqeftuq yuuk kapesegaghluni.
Kapesegakek ghhuughllaglutek nasani, alini, kenini tughqughluki.
Aghnamun esnamelngughmun ayuqluku tallini, alin inglunga ilemaghaqsaqenni anuqlighllagumakanga eslallugpagtuumaghmi.
Aghnaq taghnughhaghtuumaan tengsimakanga qagit tunutangitgun tuutesluku.
Naqam anuqa alpagumalghii.
Iiwen itagnatun uugtaquq.
Yugem enraq inglunga alimi ilemaghaghsaqenni itagnatun anuqlighllaglaataghaa eslallugpagtuumaghmi.
Aghnaq tengtaqegkanga qagit tungangitgun tuutesluku.
Tawatestaghhiinaq alpanghani anuqeghllak uugneghani yugem nasani enkaam kenini itemqughyaqenni aghnaq itagnatun tengtaqluku qenwat taghnughhaqullghiik aghnaankuk mataghquk pilugugiituk.
Wetku yuuk ukigluni nenglumineng uka atghaamalghii pilugugmeng tugumiighluni.
Aghnamun kaalluni pimakanga yugem, “Taawa pilugugmeng tagitamtek qayughllak pilugusi nukeggnapigtut.
Whanga elpek aqfastaqamken nangllegyagulluten.
Pilugugtek.
Apeghiiqufsi taglaghhaakut.”
Llaaghanwha piluguneghmeng taaqsagʼta taglaamalghiit nenglunganun.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghiit.
Yuuk tungtuquyaghaqelghii, aghnam aftaqegkangi.
Qenwat mekelghiighhaq angliiq aghnam ighnegha.
Ellmineng igleghsaaghtuq.
Mekelghiighhaq aaneghmini aghnelqusiq aviitaqelghii.
Tespamani aghneghtaqelghii nenglusqughhaghmi.
Ighivgaamaan tagineghmini igaghtupiglleghhiimeng pilugugluni.
Kiyaghtaallghem tagtalangani aghnaq ighnimalghii mekelghiighhaghmeng.
Taanallu anglimalghii qenwat.
Taanallu uyuqliq ellmineng igleghsagusimalghii.
Anengaqullghiik aaneghmegm aghneghtaqelghiik nenglungiighhaghmi.
Tagineghmegni allaghhiinaghmeng piluguglutek igaghtupiglleghiimeng.
Tagineghmegni legan neghegpenatek ingaghquullutek qavaataqelghiik.
Yugem piiqegkanga aghnaq, “Asanutelpek espamavek tunuqlighhamnnun aglaghpenang piiqi!”
Maaten ilangani tungtuquyaghyan aghnaq pimalghii, “Sanganllaam pamavek pisnaanighaqanga.
Enta esghaghyaghtuqaghlakun.”
Aghnaq aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni nenglusqughhaghmun iiyaakun qineghsalghiimi ilutmun avaqutakek quulqitem qaayngakun aqumlutek ighuteng aghulasimiita naghaghutaqeftuk.
Taawa aghnaghhaq quupneghhaq gaaghumaghmi ukinimaghmi pellugtuumaghmi enngaatall aveniqaqeftuq.
Aghnam iiyameng esqamavek kayaghumayaqaanga.
Aghnaghhaq quupneghhaq uullghaghsimalghii.
Avaqutakek ullghaghsan qiyaghwaasimalghiik.
Aghnaq iiwen nekevaquq yuuk uka aliighaquq qefliqumaghmi, “Kiii aghnaq pineghllugllapiwaa.
Imamta ineghtaqsiikun!”
Nenglumun iteghluni saguyagni tugulukek aglaghluni tespamavek aghnaghhaq quupneghhaq kallagaghyaqenni saguyagmineng unguvaghsimakanga.
Taagken kenlanga aghnaq aglaneghmeng taaqumalghii.
Enraq nenglum tekerkaanitaqelghiik maalghuk kalngasngwaaghaghhaak ilanga aywaan tunganani ilanga uughqan.
Taakuklu kalngasngaaghaghhaak yugem iinghutaqegkek saaftesqegpenakek.
Kiyaghlluteng maaten tungtuquyaghyan aghnaq sumeghtaghaghyalghiimi, “Sanganllaam kalngaggaak ukuk iinghutaqakek?
Enta ilanga esghaqaghlakun!”
Ketfaghluku aghnam nusugraghyaqenni awergham amiiraa uglapiglleghhii nusugraghaa.
Saaghwamikun mayughteghllagaa.
Iiwen wata asinganun kaawaquq, uguqaamalghii.
Asinga kalngagem kenghuftuq.
Iiwen tallini sayuwaghtaqaa yuuk qefliqumaghmi qakma kaataquq.
“Uguminaghhalek aghnaqsa qaamnapineghllugllapiwaa!”
Iitghutkelluku saguyagni tugulukek kallagaghyaqenni uteghlluni umyugaghmineng awergha kanaghquusimalghii kalngaggaghmun.
Taanallu aghnam tallii kallagaghyaqenni saguyagmineng uguqellghiisiimakanga.
Taagken kenlanga aghnaq nagalluni yugmeng lliightuq.
Pineghlliqnaanightuq.
Kiyaghsimalghiit pinitun.
Ilangani yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Aghyuqigasin?”
“Aghyuqeghngaaghmaqun naten pilanga!”
Yugem pilataghaa, “Whavegʼqun tagiighten!”
Yugem nenglum qukaanilnguq sagleghaq pakigumakanga.
Aghnaq agigsalghiimi sama Egeghaq esghaamakanga enkaam mengteghaq nayuquvinghaani masisu allighat taawa mengtegham qaayngakun mateghqughluteng.
Ighnegha aghnam nuyekliq aanumalghii mengteghameng.
Atkuga negilleghllak saama iqaghllak.
Aghnaq qiyayaghtuq.
Sama pimalghiit, “Eslallugughtaa.
Allighat iteghqughtekii!”
Yugem aghnaq tuuyngakun pakigumakanga, “Tawatenngam!”
Enkaam sagleghaq nenganun llimakanga.
Yugem aghnaq pimakanga, “Aanluten yughqutameng ghhiitaghluten ighneghpenun pamavek aglaatesqennaketen uyguquutesqelluki.
Uyguquunneghmeng apeghiiqaki tagitesqennaketen.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq tawaten pimalghii.
Uyguquulluki tagisimakangit.
Yugem pilaataghaa, “Maalghum quyngim sigutangi paasquutiki.
Enkaam ataasiq allaghhiinam awergham melqwaneng ikulluten imegnaken ilanga tungtum amiineng.
Alighpek inglunga quyngim unguvalghiim melqwaneng ikutaqluku imighnaken.
Enkaam ama inglunga enraq mengteghameng savighhuutaqluku imighnaken.”
Laaghanwha aghnaq tawaten pimalghii.
Apeghiighyan aghnaq yugem sagleghaq awitutkelluku pii, “Taana elpek tagitkan ighneghen kelqennaken.
Una uyughaa whangamni unegllequq.
Ukiglusi nateqliskufsi quneghlluten alighpek inglunga efsugunnaken enkaam inglungallu.
Enkaam mengteghamun iitquvek taakuk maalghuk sigutek paasquutngalghiik ama quneghlluten efsugunnakegken.
Enkaam ighneghen nuyekliq taglaqan uqughutaghqaghhaq esghaghyaghtiisqennaken tekegham awatanganun uyughaqullghiignun anengaa sivuliiluku.”
Taagken yugem naakullghiik ukigsimakek.
Tuusimalghiit Egegham kelutangani.
Tuusameng aghnam qimeghlluni aligni efsugullukek esghaghyalghiimi mengteghaq, ama saaghwitni quyngiq.
Iteghluni qunaghmi paasquutngalghiit quyngim maalghum sigutangi efsugulluki esghaghyalghiimi awerghaghllak allaghhnnaq amighllak minglliquumakanga.
Egeghaghmii yuggaq aanluni unanguluku kelutmun esghaghyalghiimi pika esghaghii Quyillget.
Amenam yuggaq taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghyalghiimi iflakaq nunalgutmi nulighha esghaamakanga.
Iteghyan aghnam ungipaghsuumakanga ighneghmineng nuyeklighmeng enkaam ugimineng.
Yuggaam ungipaasimakanga.
Neghluni aanaqsan quyngimeng tuunumakanga.
Enkaam ighneni lipeghsaamakanga taglaqiisqelluku.
Llaaghanwha ighnegha taglaamalghii.
Naangan neghesluku allaneng pilugugluku nutaghaastaghhiinaghmeng uyughaqullghiik llilaamakek amavek tapgham awatanganun esnighqwiisqellukek asanut anengaq sivuliiluku.
Nagaqughluni uginga aghnam nutaghaq nuliini enngaatall agliisqelluku angayuqiitnun aanesimakanga.
Taagken yuuk taglaamalghii tespikavek utuqamun nuliighminun.
Esnighqwak taglaghyalghiimek aghveghmeng mallungumalghiik.
Nunalguteteng kelgughluki pilagumakangat aghveq.
Taagken aghnam quyngimineng amilighaqluki awerghalighaqluki awalightughii nunalgutni.
Taagken kiyaghsimalghiit iwerngam aghyullghitnun.
Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
Esnaghmii Enkaam Quyillek
Kiyaghsimaaq Qigimi yuuk neqengyuqaq.
Kiigunneghagu qayaghtuneghmini unakaqegkanga masingka uksumi naamatkaghqaq neqa.
Ayumiinneghagu uksaaghmi nutaan sikulinghagu Yagrakenutaghmii Quyillek yuuk pirughsaghtughaqelghii Qigimun.
Aglagnaqenghani Quyilleni esnaghmiingan iwemgam usitutalangatun tuunaqegkanga neqmeng.
Naqam uksaaghmi tuqutiighvik kaanneghani Qigimi yuuk Quyilleggneghani angyani neqmeng usiluku Quyillgan esnaghmiini tuunaqegkanga inglut ataasit amilighluki qallukaghmeng.
Naqam piiqegkanga, “Enan ayumiqun tuqutinnaghamken.”
Ayumiinneghagu tawatestaghhiinaq.
Maaten ilangani Qigimi yuukuksaaghmi Quyillegsan emta Quyillgan tawaten uglaghqakaan tuunluku angyaghhutameng pimakanga, “Sikulighaku pirughsaghtughllequnga elpenun.
Tengutaghhaghmeng yataghqutaghhnakevnga.”
Llaaghanwha esnaghmiingan aangghumakanga.
Qigimun aglaghyami amsakaghtam amiiqaa siiqluku esnenga amiiqam tuughlluku siqlugam paaynganun petugteghuumakanga.
Taagken ayveghem tenguganeng imiimakanga iwemgam esleqaghaghlluku.
Enkaam meq kumlalluni lliighyan siqlugam tengutam paaynga meghmeng kuvughtaamakanga.
Llaaghanwha siqlugaq imaghtuumaan kumlaghqumakanga.
Qigimi yuuk mengteghamesimaluku qakma kaasimalghii Quyillga pirughsaghtuq.
Yugem aanvikumakanga aqelqani atkungunani naqam nasaperaghluni aghillugluni.
Quyillgem aqelqaan esnaghmiini pimakanga, “Aqlaghaghhalek mataghpek saquzin?”
“Sangwaqun aallakun!
Naken atkugkameng amiingigalnguunga.
Elpek amiilitaqegkevnga qallukaghmeng.”
Taagken iteghlutek neneghmeng taqsameng Quyillgem esnaghmii aapsimakanga, “Nagutuq uksaaq tengutightesqelluten piyaqemken?”
“Legan teskana kiyaghtuq.
Ulimasimamken.
Enmis aqfalteggu.”
Llaaghangwha aanlutek siqlugaanun atghaamalghiik.
Siqlugamun kaasamek esnaghmiim pimakanga Quyillek, “Esgha taana saaqsigu nusuggu.”
Siqlugam paaynga ilangqullaq katam amiiqam putungi aliilluteng.
Quyillgem akisimakanga, “Uuk kaku samam!”
Quyillek sivughaamalghii tengutameng nusugunneghmeng.
Sivughaghyan Quyillek esnaghmiim atghilegmineng putungikun amiiqaq kaguluku sayugaghsaqenni siqlugaghtuumaan piiksigaghlluku tengutaq amiiqaq nusugaghsimakanga.
Quyillgem esnaghmii pimakanga, “Uuk kaku nalleghitaquten!”
Taagken Quyillek tengugmeng usilighiluni aghulaqumalghii.
Ayumiqun uksaaghyagu awen Quyillegtelleghmeng kingutaghaghlutek atakullghiik Yagrakenutamun Quyillegsimalghiik.
Kaasalghiimeng Quyillegtaghyagllak qemgughusimalghii.
Quyillgita esnevaghvikluki pimakangi, “Kii nalleghitaqusi!
Sangafsi mulughtaastek?
Utaqaqiimsi.”
Legan tawaten aghneghmi Quyillek tuqutiighumalghii.
Sivulighpigaluku esnaghmiini Qigimii tuqluumakanga.
Pimakanga, “Elpekunguvalghiimeng aghnameng ataasimeng sigutanginnaqamken saama tallimaneng tuqutilleqamken ugmestaaghhaghmeng pilugugkameng amiilighluki.”
Taagken yuuk atakullghiik kellutek aglaamalghiik Qigimun.
Uksughlluteng upenghami quyngim ighnillghan kingunganeng suna taana kaata Quyillgat Qigimun.
Kaalluni ungipaamalghii, “Quyngighhaghsi pama maalghiimaaq.
Whangkuta Quyillegni quyngiput malghugegneng ighninghata aallghi tuqutaqaput.”
Yugem Qigimiim atangan nanevgaghhaampimakanga, “Quyngit malghighngiita whangkunni esnaghmiini avangitut agleghitut qayughllagmi whangkuta qikmit saghligaput ighniiqelghiit uglapiglluku tuquqiigalkeput.
Maaten quyngighhaghput malghighngaan nepighulluku tuqutegpenaan aallgha ighnighngaan.
Elpek quyngiqenghiitan esnaghmiit pikaat.”
Llaaghanwha Quyillek aglaamalghii.
Qigimiit Quyilleggneghmeng taaqumalghiit.
Yuuk Qigimii aghvengyagutuq ukileghyagmeng.
Maaten ilangam uksaaghmi Quyillgat pirughsaghtughluni pimakangi, “Quyngighsi pama nulaaquq sukalluni naqam pinipigtuq ukileghyaperuwaaq.”
Taagken qafsinat uksut atughluki tagilaataamalghii Quyillgat.
Enkaam pimakangi, “Agmangam3 esnametegpenasi.
Quungvaghhasi.
Masingka pama quyngighsi uglaghimaaq.”
Llaaghanwha Qigimiit qamilguumalghiit Yagrakenutam kelutanganun.
Nekegsimalghiit awen Quyillegteng sivuliqluku ellngit esnaghmiikuvinghaat tunuqliiluteng.
Quyngighteng mengteghamun tagisatgu esghaghyaqeseng imaninguq inglaminaghtuq ukileghyaperuwaaq.
Tawani kiyaghsimalghiit.
Maaten ilangani Qigimiikuvinghaam nanevgaa nanevgaghhaam nuliini Dimakanga, “Enta ighneghput pamavek quungvanun tukughqaghhaanun vaghisaghtuulteggu.”
Llaaghanwha nutaghat piluguteng meteghllugmeng qaspiqutighluki yataghqellutek aghulaqumalghiik.
Tespagani quungvani igleghllutekmengteghatmaalghugneghet esghaamakangit.
Sivulighteggun mengteghatgun kaallutek iteghpenatek uughqiitni qavaamalghiik.
Qesiqun kaatfikaqeftaat Quyillek ighnelek panilek.
Taakuk avaqutakek tespamantaqeftuk aallghani mengtegham.
Unaami mekelghiiq quyngimeng atghaghluni atami mengteghaanun aglaamalghii.
Kaalluni uqeghhmi esghaamakek aqelqak maalghuk.
Qavaghaqeftuk.
Pilugukelghiik meteghllugem amighqwaaghaneng.
Qaprakaneghmegni meteghllugem melqwa anuqataghaam tengqataqegkanga.
Iteghluni mekelghiiq atami mengteghaanun ungipasimakanga atani tawaten ayuqelghiineng aqelqaneng.
Atangan mekelghiiq pimakanga, “Iitghesqiki!
Saqungwaat?”
Aanluni mekelghiighem itegamineng taghsaamakek aqelqak.
Iteghtugnguq.
Iteghyata yugem aapsimakangi, “Kiii natmun igleghtaastek?”
“Arekull taawa taawangiinaghhaq whamighput tukughqaghhaanun ivaghitngwaaghput.”
“Uuk legan tawa panilegpigunga.
Tukightughtilleqamsi.”
Yugem ighneni pimakanga, “Aglaatiki elpesinun.
Neghyaghtuutiki.”
Aanluteng aglaamalghiit.
Sivungitni mekelghiiq kaalluni nayani pimakanga, “Enngaatall atamta aanghutaaten seghlepestaaghnun.
Sakighhaghqaghten kaaskata esghaghlleqaten.
Aklumasipigut.
Talwa meteghllugem amighqwaaghaneng pilugukuk.”
Aqelqak kaallutek iteghyagʼta aghnaghaam esghaghyaqenni imani ukuk pilugugllugllagtuk.
Utuqa allighaq saaglluku taaggun aqumesqumakegket.
Neghyaghqameng ketfaasaqmegtekek quyngim nefkuuraa taagkaghtaq tukruughqwaaghllakaq iqlugllutek aghtughlutek neneghmeng taaqusimalghiik.
Qavaghluteng unaami yataghqesata aqelqat mekelghiighem atangan ighneghminun atghaatesqumakangit quyngilegtimeng.
Enkaam yugem panini ighsaghwaaghngaan qiyaghngaan aangghunnaqniluni wanlegi maligutesqumakanga.
Aghtughyamigu ellmineng qaghlughiluni panini qaakluku atghaamalghiit.
Iiwen esnamun tunganganilngughnun Quyillegnun aliighaqut uka quyngilegti paayghi aliighaquq.
Kaasalghiimi imaniguq quyngikek pinightuk ukileghyakegtestaghhiinaak.
Yuga imaninguq atkukegtuq nughaghmeng ukileghyakegtaameng saama mekelghiiq nukalpigaqsa seghleghuqaghta.
Nanevgaghhaq pilugugllugalghii qaakluku aga uteghsimalghii.
Quyillgem panini pimakanga, “Qayugham wasaq ighsaaquten.
Langetaq aagna ugikaghqaqan.”
Panigan akisimakanga iqlighsimaghmi, “Imatuq!”
Quyngimun kaalluteng aghuliighumalghiit.
Quungvam Quyillgita quyngiq esghapagyaqeseng imani uglaghtuq naqam ukileghyaperuwaaghllak.
Nanevgaghhaam ighneni pimakanga, “Mekelghiiq una elpegun kaatesqennaqaqa.
Iitqan allighallugkun aqumesnaaghan.
Enkaam ketfaannaaghan upenghaghtam ayveghem tukighuggneq qasiqam nefkuuraaneng.
Enkaam neneghmeng aghtuqagu pinaken, ‘Wasaq elpek nanevgat neqlightughaqaten ggutangiitkat tukrugllagmeng.
Whangkutallu esnam neqanganeng tukrugsiqayugukut.
Ikiwan elpek gguutkegtaq wha aghtughtuten.’ Wetku kinguvaqun pinitun neghesnaken.
Una atanga panikullghiik whangamninnaaghtuk.”
Llaaghanwha nanevgaghhaam ighnegha tawaten pimalghii atami apeghtuusatun.
Nanevgaghhaam quungvam Quyillga qevuulluku upughasimakanga piniqullghiik.
Unaami aghulaqnaqsata aghnaghaq unegsimalghii enngaatall awen aghnaqluni.
Taakut quungvam Quyillgi usimakangat esnam neqanganeng allaghhiinaghmeng.
Kiyaghsimalghiit iwemgam aghyughinalleghmun.
Tefaay!
Qamagtuq.
Yuuk Enkaam Qateghyiighaghhaq
Yuugnguq iimna aghvengyupiglleghhii.
Maaten ilangani nuliini pimakanga, “Enta tanpeghhmeng akmagutangllaa!”
Llaaghanwha tusaqinaghpenani nulighha akmagutangllaamalghii tanpeghhmeng.
Taaqsakek akmagutak tanpeghhek qateghyiighaghhaq akuqaghluku kanaghlluku tesqamavek pimakanga, “Kevgaqnaqamken anguyamnun sughugisqelluten.”
Taagken tanpeghhek akmagutak miluullukekmeghmun kesimakek.
Anuqem akmagutak tengsimakek iwemgam natmun.
Meghem iteghpenakek uvlugem qapragsaqegni ullghitaghsaqegni akmagutak qateghyiighaghhaq mingughhusimalghii akmagutam nukeggnaanun.
Tagtalmi tepumakanga esnakun.
Qateghyiighaghhaam akmagutam allungaga vuveghqughyaqenni reghighsimakanga.
Taagken aanyalghiimi tepumakanga tapghaghllakun.
Qateghyiighaghhaq taglaghluni tapgham qaaynganun vegaaghqun aviightusimaluku sunanguq taana yuuk.
Yugem kaalluku qateghyiighaghhaq nenglaqumakanga.
Pimakanaga, “Kii, qateghyiighaghhaq nani nukeggnaaghqeghllagsin?”
“Sughuguunga elpenun.”
Yugem nenglaqluku unisimakanga.
Mengteghaminun kaalluni nuliini ungipaasimakanga, “Qateghyiighaghhaq tapgham qaayngani vegaaghqun aviightutaqeftuq.
Legan nukeggnaghllaguuq.
Aapsaqegka whangamnunnguq sughuguftuq.”
Nenglaqlaataamakangat nulighqullghiik.
Unugyagu qavaasata qateghyiighaghhaq taglaghlum ungavigitnun iitghumalghii.
Iteghluni naniita mesiighanun mingughhusimalghii.
Melquni mesiighqeghllagyamigu ungavigneng nateghmun ateghluni sugerngengitgun kavirrakegtatgun aviightuusimalghii.
Iwerngaqun sugemgit mesiighqughtaaluki ugatanganun aglaghluni qavaamalghii.
Unaami yuuk nateghmun ateghluni qefliqumalghii, “Kiii, qamay ungavimta sugerngangi seghleghuut whaa legan mesighllaguut.
Uguminaghnaghhalek enankinam saam yeghrat nukeggnaaghqeghllagumaa.”
Uganguq uwatanganeng aleghquumalghii, “Piyaghamkenta sughuguunga!”
“Uguminaghnaghhalek qateghyiighaghhaq una!” yuuk pimalghii.
Enkaam qateghyiighaghhaq malighqaghataghluku tuguyamigu piigughluku eslatmun egsimakanga, whaten pimaghmi, “Enngaatall aglaa sughuggaaten!”
Unugyagu qavaasata qateghyiighaghhaq iighwiighluni unguvaghyalghiimi jaighqutameng ghhitaghluki uyguquutaamalghii.
Masingka takuyaqminiki yugem mengteghaanun mayughluni qaakgit tapghangllaqamineng yughqutameng kenlengikun qamqaghsimakangi.
Iquga tapghangllaqami qamutighluku aasimakanga.
Enkaam qateghyiighaghhaam unulqusiq mengteghaq quulmun yaqiisimakanga.
Iiwen unugem qukaaneng aghvighaquq kenlengakun mengteghaq mengqughtaghluku llighaqaa.
Qateghyiighaghhaam sagiqusimakanga.
Qenwatlu kenlengakun mengteghaq ghhataghaghsimakanga.
Ghhataghaghsamigu qateghyiighaghhaam mengteghaq atghaasimakanga meghem qulanganun.
Taagken qateghyiighaghhaam mengteghaq meghqun llikestaamakanga.
Qamanguq yugem pimakanga nuliini, “Uuugg naken enraq meghem iteghtinkut?
Enta qiinqaa!”
Llaaghanwha aghnaq atqaghlluni qineghsalghiimi uzimun meghllak esghaghaa.
Ugini pimakanga, “Meghmun llighumakut.
Uzimun meghllaguuq.”
Iiwen aghnaq nepiighaquq qakmanguq kaakeggneng pimalghii, “Piiqsaghamken, sughuguunga!”
Yugem qateghyiighaghhaq naten piligu aanvigilnguq.
Qateghyiighaghhaam lliyaqenni mengteghaq aga kalevumalghii.
Meghmun kaasaghtughyami qateghyiighaghhaq makuggnaqsaghtuq.
Aghtuumalghii.
Ellngallu mengteghamun maligulluni kalevumalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Aghnaghaghhaq Angayuqiilnguq
Aghnaghaghhaghnguq iimna kiyaghsimaaq angayuqiilnguq.
Taawangiinaq apalek enkaam nengyullgaq.
Maaten ilangani nunalgutangita aghnaghaat kelgumakangat aghnaghaghhaq aghulaghqughnaqniluteng.
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaghhaq aapusimalghii nengyughhaghminun.
Aangghumakanga ellngallu maligutesqelluku aghulaghqunun.
Taagken aghulaghquumalghiit aghnaghaghyaget.
Tespagani unataamaluki allaghhiinaghmeng piitkameng tagitugughusimakangi.
Atghamun aghnaghaghhaq piyaqeseng aviituq.
Taagken aghnaghaat alingluteng angayuqameggneng aghnaghaghhaq tuqlughaghaataghyaqeseng akinneghiiti aghnaghaghhaam.
Ima aviituq.
Aghtughluku tuqlughaghaataneghmeng miiwen sivumeggni atghaamanayukan aghnaghaat mengteghamun atghaamalghiit.
Kaalluteng aghnaghaat mengteghaanun aghnaghaghhaam aviituq.
Aghnaghaghhaam ilangi aviilngaghyamiki qiyaaghwaamalghii ivaamayaqangi aviisimalghiit.
Yaghleginguq suna taakuk payek.
Aghnaghaghhaq payem saaghwani qiyakestaghngaaghmi qavaamalghii.
Qavaamaluku iwemga taghsaamakanga.
Taghtughyalghiimi aghnaghaghnguq suna taana nunalgutkenghilkaanga.
Aghnam aghnaghaghhaq aapsimakanga, “Saaqsin tawani?”
Aghnaghaam akisimakanga, “Aghulaghquuyaghlunga tagitughughsagu ilanka iflaamaanka.
Entaqun unillunga atghaamaat.
Iflangwiiqlunga ilanka aghtughluki ivaneghmeng whani qavaamalghiinga.”
Aghnampilaataghaa, “Tagi maligtinga.
Qamavek iitgheltung.”
Llaaghanwha iitghumalghiik.
Iteghyalghiimek imaninguq aghnam nenglunga qetngightuq naqam nenglungan ugatanga allaghhiinaghmeng neqetuuq.
Aghnam aghnaghaghhaq neghesimakanga mangtagmeng enkaam quyngimeng.
Aghnam pimakanga aghnaghaghhaq, “Wiin whani kiyaghten.
Unaaqutaqegkagu aanaqegkuma whani utaqaaqinga.
Igataghaqegkuvek neghyukegkaghpeneng neghaqi utaqagpenanga.”
Qavaghlutek unaami taghtuneghmegni aghnaq aanaqelghii.
Aghnelqusiq aviitaqelghii.
Wetku unugyaghtuumaan tagineghmini itghutaqelghii tungtumeng ilangani pilakameng mangtagmeng.
Aghnaghaghhaq apangan enkaam nunalgutangita ivaghyaghluku aghtughyamegteggu aviisan qenwat wisqaawisimakangat.
Maaten ilangani aghnam aghnaghaghhaq pimakanga, “Elpeknegpenun aghyuqaghsigasiin?”
“Aghyuqeghngaaghmaqun naten aglaghlanga.
Naantat apanka nallukegkenka.”
Aghnam pimakanga, “Whaa qavaghyaghtughtunga.
Qavaquma angatumeng taghtughnaanghitunga.
Qemall elpek aghyuqellequten pellaghyugllequten.
Apagpek sama suumqenneghmeng elpek qavaq palaghhaq atuqaqaat.
Repall iiyngiqaghtiighumaat.
Ighivganghagu qagughmigullutek qavaghnaqutkaquk.”
“Wetkuqun elpek maliggnakevnga.”
Aghnam aangghumakanga.
“Whaa apeghtughnaqamken vuvallami egmightaataskuyeng kayaalqennayukangaten.”
Aghnam saguyak tugulukek ilagaamalghii alignaghtaghumalghii.
Aghnaghaghhaam esghapagumakanga.
Apeghiighyami aghnam aghnaghaghhaq aapsimakanga, “Qayugham liisin?”
“Aaa liitunga.”
“Legan atghaghluten vuvallakufsi tawaten pilghaaten.
Ahaam pilugugi.
Atghannaqamken.”
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaghhaq pilugugumalghii.
Taagken aanyalghiimek nutaan uksaaghaqeftaa.
Atghaamalghiik.
Atghaamalutek unugumakanga.
Kaasaghtughyameng aghnaghaghhaam mengteghaanun aghnam pimakanga, “Uteghhnaqunga whanga.
Ellnginaghpekkaallghaten.”
Aghnaq aga uteghsan aghnaghaghhaam uteghmun qiivyaqenni kaynga aga maaten tumangitgun pangalgaqeftuq.
Aghnaghaghhaq kaalluni amigem reghillghakun qineghsalghiimi qama apakek qagughmigullutek qavaataqeftuk.
Aghnaghaghhaam tenglugtuumaan amik qamayaghmighyaqenni taghtughsimakek.
Qama pimalghiik, “Kaay llangaqa eltughaghhamta menga!”
“Aaqun whangangunga taginga.
Enmis sukalluku qalpeghutengnga!”
“Kaay eltughaghput taguq!”
Qalpeghusimakangat.
Iteghyalghiimi apangita iiyngit qavaghlaaghigallgjiem iqeghtiighluteng.
Eltughaghteng neghesluku qavaamalghiit.
Unaami aapqughaghyaghaat apagkenkallu enkaam aghnaghaatlu tagiluteng aghulaghqulgutangita, naken pitanga.Aghnaghaghhaq aksaqngwaaghumalghii.
Taagken aghnaghaghaam apanga vuvallamalghii.
Sughukaq tagilaghaalluni neghunneghmeng taaqsameng ungipaghaasimalghiit.
Taagken aghnaghaghhaam apanga vuvallamalghii.
Taagken alla neghulluteng enraq egmiightataasimalghiit alignaghtaaghusimalghiit.
Ilangita sungat kagimlluki saguyameggnun qaakluki saguyateng kallagneghmegteki sungat iighwighaqut.
Enraq ilangita tugutangi ayveghem mengqutun ulqaghtaaghaqegkangit.
Aghnaghaghhaam nengyughhani pimakanga, “Whangallutuq egmightaataqalghiinga.”
Nutemnguq apanga pimalghii, “Sameng piiqa?
Sanaqaqa?”
Aghnaghaghhaam nengyughhaa pimalghii, “Ellngallutughnguq egmightaataqalghii.”
“Leganmi saaqa!”
Nutemnguq ilangi sughukam aghnalqwaaghit pimalghiit yakuqluteng, “Aghnaghaqraaggaq agghiyugnepiwaa!
Kimaawistiinaquq ilangitneng alignaghtaaghnaqelghiineng.”
Aghnaghaghhaq ketfaghluni saguyak tugulukek ilagaamalghii.
Ilagaamaluku ukanguq suksugllak aliighumalghii.
Iiwen piiqut amigkun uga qagit kasugusimalghiit ilutmun nateghmun.
Aghnaghaghhaam saguyagni kallagaghyaqenni qagit ighhusalghiimeng nateghmi siipsimalghii tepaq allaghhiinaq.
Aghnaghaghhaq nekevluni signeghegneng tugulluni tamaken tepameng imighlukek signeghegneng sughukaq tunquumakanga.
Qamagsamigu tunquneghmeng enraq siklameng tungsimalghii.
Tuunyatni uwatanganun aglaghluni mingla siklaghyaqenni allaghhiinaq tangiqaq peksigaghsimakanga.
Itagnatun signeghek tugulukek imighaqlukek tamaken tangiqameng sughukaq uyegsimakanga.
Qamagsamigu mumeq tuguluku aghnaghaghhaam mingla kenuqaghyaqenni meq meghrakegtepiglleghhii maaqumalghii minglenganeng.
Meghutmeng tugulluni meqsilaamakanga tamaghhaan sughukaq.
Taagken kenlanga aghnaghaghhaq ugpeqsalitaat.
Vuvallaneghmeggni aqfaqegkangat nunalgutangita.
Qamagtuq.
Qatelghiinkuk Amaankuk
Qatelghii tapgham qukaani mallungluni ayveghmeng neghumaluku sunanguq taana amaa.
Kaalluni amaam qatelghii pimakanga, “Whangallu neqaghlanga.
Igatapigtunga.”
“Legan neghi.
Uglaghllagtuq.
Whangangingaghma naangnnaanghitaqa.”
Llaaghanwha amaallu neghumalghii.
Iwemgaqun kepsughlutek neghlutek tapgham kelutanganilngughmun uusneghwaaghmun mayuumalghiik.
Qaygeghsamek qatelghiim amaa pimakanga, “Whani yeqay meghnaaliltung.
Wiin qavaaltung.”
Llaaghanwha amaa aanghumalghii.
Tawani uusneghwaaghem qaayngani ingaghquusimalghiik.
Qatelghii qavaghpenani teghhumaamalghii.
Amaa qavaghyan whaa tungunghaqasan qatelghii nekevluni tamaani qemgughtimalghii ayveghem kuyapegaaneng.
Qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii nuuvulluki amaam paapgakun qilleghsimakangi.
Enkaam amaa taghsaamakaanga.
Qatelghiim pimakanga, “Anguyaget sughuget whaa kaasaghtuungestaamiikung.
Uusneghwaaghmun mayiigaqut.
Whanga qimagnaqunga.
Elpek saaqsin?”
Amaa qaviinamaatkun nekefqaghlluni pangalegyalghiimi kelutmun uka tunganganeng kavleggalek.
Naqam paapga aqniimaghmi.
Amaa sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Seghleghhalekkaannaqaatnga anguyaget.
Tuqunnaqaatnga.
Awitwuwaqlu papemkun kiitegtaatnga.
Sangami paapka aqnighaqa?”
Amaa iwemgaqun qevuulluni qimakaq tuqunnayukangatni.
Qimaguqestaghngaaghmi kinguminilnguq kavlek almesiqngiinaghyagu saama pekapigsami amaa sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Qaywaam tuqulanga.”
Aghuliighutkelluku uteghmun qiivyalghiimi sughumeng esghaanneghituq.
Katam taawa paapgakun qilleghlluteng qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii.
Amaa pimalghii, “Uguminaghnaghhalek qatelghiipenaaq pekaghtepigtaanga.
Kergam taawa esghaqaghtekumken unguvallequten.”
Qatelghiim kiiwek kaallukek akimun ayuqelghiik maligsimakek iwemgam esnamun.
Tawani esnami tepameng neghemsuglimi taglaamalghii esnam kelutanganun.
Pengughaghhaghmun kaalluni tawani qavaghnaqsami iyegni nusugraghlukek saaghwmikun llilukek qavaamalghii.
Taagken amaam ugumiyagulluku qatelghii tamaghhaani ivaghtaayaqenni.
Qenwatlu naalkeqaghsimakanga.
Qatelghii qavaghaqeftuq enngaatall umuluku naqam saaghwani iyek.
Amaamtaghsaghpenaan iiskekqatelghiimtutmaghtaalukek qageghqughlukek unisimakanga.
Kingunganeng amaam qatelghiim iwemgaqun qavagni nusuglukek taghtughyami iyegni tugunaqsaqegni aviituk.
Katamnaalkumakekqageghqughlleraaghinaak.
Qatelghii ayaaluni paneghluni tuqumalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Aghnaghaq Uyughalek
Aghnaghaq kiyaghsimalghii uyughalek.
Mekelghiiq aanigalnguq quunpeng itghumaghllak.
Nayaga quyngighqwaaghaqelghii.
Atghaneghmini gaaghluni uyughaqullghiik neghaqelghiik.
Aghnaghaq quyngimun aghulaqneghmini quyngighqwaaghutkelluku ulapaqelghii.
Atghaneghmini gaaghniighaqelghii saama pilugugmeng ukiniiqelghii.
Uyughani qelghaqsaqanga waran uughqaghmun aanaghtaqluku pisqelluku.
Iwerngallu mekelghiiq aanigalgnuq.
Maaten ilangani aghaghaam uyughani pimakanga, “Whaa uninnaqamken.
Miitalgii seghleghulghiiten.
Taawa whaa sinumiggaan iflanaqnguuq.
Saama elpek langetaq mengteghiighunnaquten.
Aatagʼqun tukughqaghhanun i vaghiyaghnaqunga.
Qavaghluteng unaami aghnaghaq aghulaqumalghii.
Igleghsimalghii qafsinat aghneghet.
Ununghagu aghuliighluni ayaviini napaghlluku angyataghqelluni qavaghaqelghii.
Unaami taghtughluni ayaviini esghaneghminigu iqunighsimaaqelghii.
Tawaten iqunighlleghamun aghnaghaq aghulaqaqelghii.
Maaten ilangani iiwen siqineq tevighyaghtughaquq qemimeng agigsalghiimi kana neghllak esghaamakanga.
Nem akulangani aangqateghllagaqeftuq taam nunam yuga.
Aghnaq kilgaaqumeng ukigumalghii qemimeng.
Aangqaallghiit qungangitgun aagumalghii enkaam nagneghumalghii ingavek sivulighpigaghnun mengteghaminun.
Kaasami nagneghluni nateghmun iitghumalghii.
Taawa esghaamakangi malghugneghet ungaviget aywaan tunganganilnguut meketaghalghiit.
Tawavek ungavignun aywaan tunganganilngughnun iitghumalghii.
Aangqaallghiit lengaaghmeng nagaquusimalghiit taagken alingyugluteng taaqusimalghiit.
Nunam amatum sukatelleghpigaa aghnaghaq talwa nukalpiganeng aglaamalghii mengteghaminun.
Taana sukalnguq aghnaghaq tugunaqutkaqsaqangat aghtughaqegkangat.
Aghnaghaam kayalqiiraghmi kayalqaqegkangi nukalpigaat.
Wetku kina kayalqiilghii taana nulightughyaghqaq sukalngughmeng aghnaghaghmeng.
Aghnaghaq mengteghaminun kaalluni iitghumalghii.
Ungavigminun aglaghluni suugemgeni ikighsaqenni kelutangani iggasightaghaqeftuq nukalpigaqsa seghleghuqaghta.
Aghnaghaam naani tuqlughluku pimakanga,
“Yeqay whanga gaaghlanga!”
Naangan pimakanga, “Imukun sangavek gaaghyugllagsin?”
Panigan akisimakanga, “Iwemgallu whangamneng gaaghyugtunga!”
Taana aghnaghaq gaaghigasalghii.
Naanga gaaghtengwaaqsalghii.
Aghnaghaq ugkellimalghii tunughtullghinaaneng quyngimeng.
Ugusami angayuqani manisfikluki ugkemeng ellmi allakaghmi taagken iitghumalghii.
Aqelqaqullghiik neghlutek taaqsamek ungipamsugusimalghiik.
Tukaan aghnaghaam uygumalgutkennaluku atkugiisqughaghaqegkanga.
Aqelqaan piiqegkanga, “Aglaghlunga alla tagikuma wetku tawani mataghhnaaghtunga.”
Qayughllagʼqun kaynguyugaqelghii mataghhneghmeng.
Ellngallu aghnaalghii.
Qenwat pilugugtuumalghii ingaghsimalghii aqelqaq, qavaghnipiggnilimi.
Unaami aghnaghaam tukaan nunalgutangita nagaqughluku aqelqaq kaasimaniluku kelgumakangat aqelqaghniighnaqniiluku.
Llaaghanwha aghnaghaankuk aqelqaqullghiik aglaamalghiik aqelqaghniighnaqelghiinun.
Taagken kilgaaquusimalghiit.
Kelgusimakangat naayghaq sungaghyuggiinaq aliilnguq.
Taana naayghaq uzivluku uteghsaghqaat.
Taagken aghulaqusimalghiit.
Aqelqaq aghnaghaq igleghsimalghii aqfaalaameng.
Leganqun aga sivungani kilgaaqulghiinun ugleghutaquq sivulighpigaluni tukaa aghnaghaq.
Naayghaq aliighwaaghyamegteggu qevuullighaamalghii.
Taakwna kilgaaqullghii aghnaghaam naghughquumakanga.
Iiwen naayghamun kaataquq sivulighpigaq tukuni kaasimakanga.
Taagken qerngaagmek aghnaghaam tukuni sivuliqluku naayghaq uzivluku uteghsimalghiik.
Igleghsimalghiik.
Whaa mengteghat aliighwaaghyayegteki aghnaghaam tukuni pimakanga, “Enta ingavek mengteghanun kaarragkiighutaghlluteng!”
Aghnaghaam tukuni naghughlluku qevuulluni kilgaaquumalghii.
Kaalluni aqelqaq uteghmun esghaghyalghiimi taam nunaaghem sukallgha tukuni naghughlluku qevuulluni kilgaaquumalghii.
Kaalluni aqelqaq uteghmun esghaghyalghiimi taam nunaaghem sukallgha tukuni aghnaghaq uniteghllagumakanga, Nutemnguq tamakut esghapalghiit aapsimakangat, “Naken uteghsin?”
Aqelqaam akisimakanga, “Enan kingulighhaghma kaaskuyeng ungipaannaaghiisi.”
Tukaa aghnaghaq kaalluni pimakangi esghapalghiit nunalgutni, “Aqelqaq piyaqangiitaghsi.
Matum nunaaghem yuga kayalqughtaagaa.
Sukateghllapigtuq.
Kitum ingluknaanghitaa.
Qemgaamtung naayghaq uzivaghpung.
Tagimun uniteghllagaanga.”
Kilgaaquutkaq kaatquusan qamaglluni qemgughusan enraq tughumghannaaqumalghiit.
Taagken yuget mataghlluteng tughumghasimalghiit.
Aqelqaq ketfaghyan atkugtuumaghmi pimakangat tawaten tughumghanaanghinniluku mataghtesqelluku.
Aqelqaam akisimakangi, “Whangkuta ima sivimemnneng kenlanga nunaaghnun nutaan piyuggaanemta mataghsigatukut.
Wetku alghighluku tawavek nunaaghmun pinemta taawa mataghsaghqaaghtaqiinkut.
Aglaghlunga alla tagikuma esghaghlleqaghsi uvinka.
Enngaatall tawani mataghllequnga.”
Laaghanwha ugpeghsimakangi aqelqaam tamakut yuget mataghtesqughwaalghiit.
Tughumghamakangat yuget aqelqaat atkugtuumaghngaan.
Aqelqaq imani iknaqeghllagtuq.
Ilangi tunuvanghata ilangita atghaqluku mataawitaat iqunneghmeng.
Aqelqaam kayalqughtagaa nunaaghem tamatum yuga iknaqellgha.
Aqelqaghniineghmeng taaqsameng aglaghtuusimalghiit.
Aqelqaq tukughminun aglaamalghii.
Iteghyan tukaan aghnaghaam qevuulluku upughasimakanga iitghesqumaan ungaviget ilungitnun.
Neneghmeng taaqsameng aghnaghaam tukaa iteghluni atkugiisqughaaghumakanga aqelqani.
Aqelqaan pimakanga, “Ungipaatamken leganiitek sagiqutaghpenga.
Mataghhnaanghitunga.
Aglaghlunga tagikuma yugusiqa esghaghlleqannatetulnga.”
Aqelqaq tukughmi uygumalqiinaghnaqenghatni piiqegkanga, “Qavaghnipigtaanga.
Ingaghhnaqunga.”
Atkugtuumaghmi ingaghutkelluku qavaasighwaaghaqelghii qavanghiteghngaaghmi.
Unaami tukuni pimakanga, “Aglaghnaqunga.
Sukallungatagillequnga.
Utaqanakevnga.”
Aghulaqumalghii aqelqaq.
Igleghutkelluku aghnaghaq sumeghtaghaghaqelghii, “Miiwen inga quyngighhaghput uglafquq.
Naagu inga uyughaqa ighsanitalghii, paneghluni tuquuq.”
Uusneghwaaq quyngighqwaaghvikumtaani kaalluku agigsaqenni iitekkana quynighteng esghaamakanga.
Quyngim awatangani guughngaghmi yuuk kaamgegni piginghi sivughtughaqeftii.
Aghnaghaam igkaghaghluku kaasaghtughyamigu upughhnaqepiglluku waakestegpenaan teskanavek metngeqaghviksaqenni iiwennguq ama quyngim awatangani.
Taagken aghnaghaam piyaqenni uyughani liisuqumakanga.
Piyugmeng takuluku nayagan uyughani pimakanga, “Tawaten pisqelluten piiqsaghamken.
Ahaam atghaghluten neghyaghtuultung.”
“Inga qantagham tungtuusimakanga.
Taana aagvikelteggu.”
Llaaghanwha tungtutamikun uyughaan nayani aagusimakanga.
Mekelghiighem tungtutaani iisqaghmiigumakanga.
Nayagan pimakanga, “Gaaghusaghtughnaqamken.
Sivullgaaghnaqamken.”
Aghnaghaq uuvganeng taagken kilgaaqumeng ghhataamalghii.
Mengteghamim kaasaghtughyami uteghmun uyughani iisqaghmilek tungtumeng esghaghyaqenni tungtunganeng maligsaaghaqeftaa uyughaan.
Aghnaghaq piyugumalghii enkaam uyughani pimakanga, “Enankin yugulghiiten.
Inglukusagusaghqaaghsimaaten yulgutevnun.”
Kaallutek aghnaghaq aftaatkelluku tungtumeng gaaghumalghii.
Ugusami neghutkelluku uyughani ungipamsugusimakanga aqelqaghniilleghmineng ataasimi nunaaghmi.
Pimakanga uyughani, “Iitek tazinga aghnangusimayaghamken.
Miitalgi mengteghaat sivulighpigaaguq.
Ayumiini kaaskuvek wiin iteghpenang.
Uqeghhmi mataghhnaaghtuten.
Atkugiquvek upagullghiit pinaghaaten, ‘Atkugiisqughaghaqaghpesinga.
Taawa yugusiqa esghaghteggu!’
Enkaam mengteghamun iitquvek esghaghnaaghan aghnaghqan.
Ungaviganun iitquftek aghnaghaq pinaken, ‘Amsikaghtesqughaghaqegkevnga.
Enngaatall amsikaghhnaqunga.’ Naqamllu aqelqaghniighnaanghitaaten.
Whanga apeghiiqaqaatnga.
Ikiwan whanga aghnaq kayalqesimangitunga.”
Qavaghluteng unaami mekelghiighem nayagmi ayaviigha wanitalek tuguluku nayagmi apaatellghatun aghulaqumalghii.
Wata palaghhaat qavat atughluki qemiq agigsaghqani kaasimakanga.
Agigsaqenni neghllak esghaamakanga.
Tawani aghuliighumalghii.
Whanikuneghsiimakanga.
Iiwen siqineq ikaliiqaa, akulmi nunaaghem yuga qemgughuteghllagumalghii.
Taagken aangqaasimalghiit.
Katam siqineq tevighyan mekelghiiq qemimeng ukigumalghii kilgaaqumeng.
Angqaallghiit akulangitgun igleghaamalghii ingavek sivulighpigaanun mengteghanun.
Kaasami mengteghamun uqeghhmi aghuliighumalghii.
Aangqaallghiit lengaghmeng nagaquusameng taaqusimalghiit.
Pimalghiit, “Awituwaq aqelqaq akuwaaghniimna kaatuq.”
Enkaam tazingavek sivulighnun mengteghanun aglaghtuusimalghiit.
Aqelqaq kaallghii upagumakangat.
Upagut tagilaghaasata mekelghiighem aqelqam pimakangi, “Atkugiisqaqaghpesinga.
Taawa yugusiqa esghaghteggu.”
Atkuni mataghsimakanga.
Upagut whaten pinginaghii, “Ahaam aghulaqutek.”
Uvinʼganeng esghaalluteng nukalpigat aghulaqusimalghiit.
Aghulaqusata mekelghiiq atkugluni iitghumalghii nateghmun.
Iteghyalghiimi nateghmun esghaamakanga aghnaghaq gaaghaqeftuq neqmeng.
Imamnguq ineqsunaghtuq.
“Kaay tagizin?”
aghnaghaam pimakanga.
“Qamavek ungavignun iitghi.
Gaaghaqunga.
Sukalluteng ugulleqii ugket.”
Llaaghanwha mekelghiiq iitghumalghii ungavigmun.
Ugusami aghnaghaam angayuqani ugkemeng manisfikluki iitghumalghii ungavigmun.
Iteghyan mekelghiighem aghnaghaq pimakanga, “Amsikaghtesqughaghaqegkevnga enngaatall amsikaghhnaqunga.”
Amsikaghhneghmeng taaqsan mekelghiiq, neghumalghiik aleghquusimaghmek aghnaghaankuk.
Qavaghluteng unaami aghnelqusiq yataghqumalghiik.
Unaami aghulaqsaghqak.
Naqamllu naagu aqelqaghniighyunghiitaat aqelqaq.
Llaaghanwha qavaghluteng unaami quyngilegtimeng atghaamalghiik mekelghiighem mengteghaanun.
Kaallutek mekelghiighem nayagan upughasimakanga ukaani.
Aghnaghaam ukuk esghapagyaqegni nayakullghiik gginiik ataasiistukanik.
Taagken kiyaghsimalghiit.
Aghnaq aqsangluni ighniyalghiimi mekelghiighhaghmeng.
Maaten ilangani yugat aviilluku nayaga qulilluni qulitusiini kuuvluku eslamun, iitghumalghii iqlighaghluni.
Ukaaghan aapsimakanga, “Sameng nunalgutevnengllu waamtilqa.
Igleghsuggaanemta ima sivunemneng mataghsigaanniluta piiqegkemsi.
Naten mataghllanga kaynguyugaqelghiinga mataghhneghmeng, qayughllagʼqun aghnaalghiinga.”
Ukaaghanllu neqangughluku uygumalleni ama mataghtesqughaalleni, qemgaagmek nenglaasimalghiik.
Uyughani tagiyan pimakanga, “Unaami ukavek uughqan tunganganun eslughllequnga.
Yugusiqa ivaghilleqaqa tukughqaghhanun.”
Uyughaan aanghumakanga.
Uyughani pilaataghaa, “Naqamllu whaa elpek pengegniighutaaten.
Masingka nemetwhayaaghtaaten.”
Llaaghanwha unaami angyataghqameng akmagluni aghulaqumalghii uqeghhmun.
Kingunganeng uyughaa taghnughhangughluni kiyaghsimalghii.
Saama quyngit nulamalghiit.
Qamagtuq.
Aghnaghaq Ulghaaghughtekaq
Ungipaghaninguq imani aghnaghaq ugineghmeng ighsatalghii.
Enngaatall angayuqiita aangghutaqsaqangat.
“Aaam, taawa esghaghamken!
Aaningam!”
Ataasimeng qavanghata llaaghanwha aanaqelghiit yuget.
Upupeng ilanga yugem ugiksaqunigu llaaghanwha ilanganeng piyaghaat legan ataasimeng qavanghata piiqelghii, “Aaam, aaningam!
Taawa esghaghamken!”
Qenwat nunaghllak qamagsimakanga.
Taagken qamagsagu piit, “Aaa, upupeng unitelteggu.
Qaagna kelguulteggu.”
Amenam angyaq tamaghhaa kelgughaat kelgughaat.
Apeghiighaat.
Yataghqelluteng aghulaqut angyat tallimat.
Amenam qemallnguq esnamun atghaghluni aghnaghaq ilagaatmeng aanqusalghiimi, “Angyat unegkughsiiii, angyat unegkughsiiii, nalighpesiiii qaakeqaghllitnga!”
“Enngaatall yugusin tespikani yugusingaken.
Akitukitkigu!”
Aga aghulaqut.
Ilangi kellataghtut.
Iiwen ketaqut pilataghtuq, “Angyat unegkughsiiii, angyat unegkughsiiii, nalighpesiiii qaakeqaghllitnga!”
“Enngaatall yugusin tespikani yugusingaken.
Akitukitkigu!”
Aga aghulaqut.
Ilangi pingayii ketut.
Iiwen ketaqut aghnaghaq ilagaghaqelghii, “Angyat unegkughsiiii, angyat unegkughsiiii, nalighpesiiii qaakeqaghllitnga!”
“Enngaatall yugusin tespikani yugusingaken.
Akitukitkigu!”
Aga aghulaqut.
Estamagneghi aga ketaqut.
Iiwen ketaqut ilagaghlataamalghii, “Angyat unegkughsiiii, angyat unegkughsiiii, nalighpesiiii qaakeqaghllitnga!”
“Enngaatall yugusin tespikani yugusingaken.
Akitukitkigu!”
Aga aghulaqut.
Tallimagneghi aga ketaqut.
Ilagaatmeng alla aanqullaataghtuq, “Angyat unegkughsiiii, angyat unegkughsiiii, nalighpesiiii qaakeqaghllitnga!”
“Enngaatall yugusin tespikani yugusingaken.
Akitukitkigu!”
Aga aghulaqut.
Ewen ulghaaghughlluni qetgeghnaqaquq.
Angayuqita piit, “Tagiitagiitagii, panikamken, tagiitagiitagii!”
Qetgeghyalghiimi angyaq tamaghhaghmi aga uveghtuq.
Ellnga masiisu ulghaaghughsimalghii.
Taawanguq ulghaaghughtepigesnaamalghii.
Tefaay!
Qamagtuq.
Ilagaan
Yugem nuliini pimakanga, “Enta saguyaghaagka tagivaqaghqek.
Ilagaqaghlanga.”
Llaaghanwha saguyak tuunaak.
Ilagaatmeng aanqusalghiimi,
“Pamiinayiiyaaaangaangaa
Pamiinayiiyaaaangaangaa
Kanani kanani Sivuqam saaghwaningii
Aaa yugtaa qiyayugtaa
Anenginaqlimii qiyayugtaa
Kanani kanani Sivuqam saaghwaningii
Angaangaa, susuqpiyaaq
Angaangaa, susuqpiyaaq
Kanani kanani Sivuqam saaghwaningii!”
Iiwenllu nepiighaquq.
Tefaay. Qamagtuq.
Talaka
Iiwleng yaywaalengiighhaq mekelghiighhaq quunpeng tukiita neghesigalkangat.
Quunpeng ilaakwaaghmini kiyang neghaqelghii.
Palaseketaghhaghmeng neghaqelghii.
Vuvallanaqeneghmeggni ilagiisqughaghaqsaqangat.
Ighsaghwaaghaqelghii.
Anagulghaqegkangat aghtuneghmegteggu.
Quunpeng yugem anaguleghtaagaqegkanga.
Maaten ilangani uksumi emta tawaten vuvallanaqsata, whaa apeghiighsaghyata, ellngaanguq mekelghiiq unaghhaaneng anʼgiqaq anʼgiqaq anʼgiqaq.
Unugtaaghllagaa.
Qenwat mamleghqwaagaa.
Pimakanga yugem, “Saaqsin tawani?”
“Qayughllak tukuunka vuvallanaqaqut.
Enkaam iwhaniiqunga...
Kagtaghtaghwaaghaqunga.
Ilagiisqughaaghaqsaqangatnga, aghtuneghmegtengnga anaguleghtaagaqegkangatnga.”
“Aa-a, enkaam elpek Talakangulghiiten.”
Kallagutkelluku ilagaghyalghiimi, “Talaka Talaka Talaka, ay!
Talaka-Talaka-Talayaay!
Saguyagka kallagutaghsamkekay!
Mumeghhaqa anagutaghsamkunay!”
Nuna mumeghmineng tenpeyaqenni quupaghteghllagaa.
“Tawaten ilagaghhaaten!
Sivukluni amiigurat uugkuttenpenaketen mumeghpeneng.
Taaqegkuvek taakwavek aywaanun egkwaanun ima kaaten pinaaghtut.
Amenam aglaa.
Tuulleqaaten.”
Llaaghanwha mekelghiiq aglaamalghii.
Aglaghluninguq iteghyan piit, “Kiimnalleghiitaquten!
Naken pizin?”
“Anʼgighaqunga.”
“Utaqaneghmeng aghtughluten qenwat neghutukut.
Neghi!”
Palaseketaghhaghmeng neghesluku taagken unulqusiq mekelghiiq qavaghpenani aghtesimakanga.
Teghhumamalghii unulqusiq.
Llaaghanwha aghsagu vuvallayeng napaghsamegteggu piit, “Sughukaq qaagna kelgughhu!”
Mekelghiighhaam kelgughyaqenni yaywaalengiighhaam aksaqluni ungipaataqluki, “Ilagaquma aksaqlusi aanleghaalleghasi elpesi.”
“Aa-a!”
Iwerngam qamagsamigu tagilaghaalluteng neghulluteng neghulluteng qamagtut.
“Aa-a, mekelghiighhaq saaqsin ilagaa!
“Samengqun ilagaghlanga!
Avangitunga.”
“Weni ilagaa getgeta1 qaagkut ilagatangitneng.”
“Avangitimga.”
“Aa-a ighsaghwaa tawani...”
Nutaan anagunaqsaghaat.
“Aa-a enta talwam ilagaqaghlanga!”
Ketfaghlunmguq saguyak kallagsimakek kallagutkellukek aanqusalghiimi, “Talaka-Talaka-Talaka-ay!
Talaka-Talaka-Talaka-ay!
Saguyagka kallagutaghsamkunay!
Mumeghtaqa anagutaghsamkunay!”
Ugatanga mumeghmineng tenpeyaqenni nenglu ifkaghteghllagaa.
Yuget qimagutut egkwaanun.
“Talaka, Talaka tawatenngam tawatenngam taaqingam taaqingam” Wanlegi ilagaghlaataamalghii, “Talaka-Talaka-Talaka-ay!
Talaka-Talaka Talakaay!
Saguyagka kallagutaghsamkekay!
Mumeghtaqa anagutaghsamkunay!”
Uughqan tungangakun mumeghmineng tenpeyaqenni ifkaaqutesaqenni yugtuumaghmi ellnga iiyakun aanqaghlluni qimagumalghii.
Naagu qimapigesnaamalghii.
Qamagtuq.
Pista
Kiyaghsimalghii ataasiq yuuk nunami tungangani avangilnguq nunalgutangilnguq.
Ellngiinaqeltaghhaq unangniilqegkanga taawangiinaq sikigginaghmun.
Talwallu sikigmeng neqekelghii.
Naqam quunpeng piyaniighaqelghii.
Piyaavigmeng kaanneghmini ellmineng gaaghniighaqelghii.
Gaaghniineghmeng taaqneghmini neghluni neneghmeng taaqneghmini ingliighluni qavaghaqelghii.
Qavaghluni taghtuneghmini piyaagaqelghii.
Unangluni uteghnineghmini unakegkani sikiget aftaluki aymaakengit gaaghaqegkangi amiiriit kinengllaghaqegkangi.
Ingleghqaaluki naliini tanpeghqaaluki.
llangam maaten unanguluku taghtughyami sumeghtaghaamalghii suvukluni esnighqwaghnaluni.
Taagken aanluni esnam tunganganun aghulaqumalghii.
Esnamun kaalluni igleghsimaluni esghaamakanga esnemi unguvalghii tepenghhaq neghnavregaghhaq.
Taana neghnavregaghhaq unguvaan tuguluku mengteghaminun aglaasimakanga.
Taglaghluni kakighani mengtegham putugtaq amiq qepluni ukigsimakanga.
Ukiglluku itemsimakanga.
Itemlluku neghnaavregaghhaq unguvaan qipusimakanga.
Kepluku almesitun petugumakanga kangighaanun.
Taagken piyaalaataamalghii kilgaanun.
Piyaavigmi unangllaataamalghii sikigmeng.
Sikigtani akmighluku uteghniimalghii mengteghaminun.
Kaalluni unakegkani sikik llimakanga egllum saaghwakun.
Lliluku ellnga akitkun aqumumalghii.
Aqumluni iimgutkani neghnavregaq pimakanga, “Enta saaqsin?
Pisteminun unangkaqa aftagu!”
Unangkaa sikik umyugamineng qayuutamun uuglluni ellmineng amiirighumalghii.
Amiirineghmeng taaqluni ellmineng llaagit uglafqusimalghiit ama ighneghiighumalghii.
Uglafquneghmeng taaqsan yuuk pilaataamalghii, “Saaqsin pistemni gaaghutinga!”
Yugem esghapagyaqminigu sikigem ayimsimakanganga ellmineng.
Uughqaghlluni qulmesiitmun kanaghquusimalghiit ellmeggneng, egllum qulangakun agaghsimalghiit.
Llaaghanwha yuuk ugket ugusata neghumalghii.
Neneghmeng taaqluni pilaataamalghii, “Saaqsin pistemni ingleghutinga!
Iteghnaqunga.”
Ellnga yuuk aanumalghii eslamun.
Mulugpenani iitghumalghii.
Iteghyalghiimi ungavik ellmineng apeghiighsaamalghii.
Iteghluni qavaamalghii.
Unaami taghtughyami piyaalaataamalghii.
Iiwennguq qemineng tevaquq meteghlluk esghaamakanga.
Esghaghluku yugem pimakanga, “Uuk aqelqaq!
Natmun igleghtaqsin?”
“Temngi maagun igleghtaqunga.”
Yugem pilaataamakanga, “Uuk weni whanga aqelqaqlaken!
Atghaalta.
Neghyaghtuulta.”
Taagken yugem aqelqani meteghlluk mengteghaminun itghusimakanga.
Kaalluteng iitghumalghiit.
Iteghluteng yugem upughasimakanga alqelqani meteghlluk.
Meteghllukutaqimalghii aqumluni sikigem amiiraakun.
Yuuk pimalghii, “Saaqsin pistemni?
Aqelqaq gaaghutigu.”
Llaaghanwha sikigem neqangit ellmeggneng ketfaghluteng ugkelliiqelghiit.
Ugkelliluteng ellmeggneng qulmesiitmun iteghluteng agaghsimalghiit egllum qulanganun.
Meteghlluk aqumluni qiivaqwaaqelghii uzimun.
Mengtegham ilungani aghtughaqelghii esghaanneghmeng kitum yuuk apeghiighsaataqagu.
Neneghmeng taaqluteng iitghumalghiit.
Qavaghluteng unaami taghtughluteng neghluteng aghulaqumalghiit.
Yugem meteghlluk pimakanga, “Whanga piyaanaqunga kilgaanun.
Elpek navek pinaqsin?”
“Whanga akingan tunganganun ivaghiiqunga nemeng.”
Taagken pellghusimalghiik.
Yuuk aygumim aghulaqumalghii.
Meteghlluk akingan tunganganun aghulaqumalghii.
Meteghlluk pengughqameng talughlluni yuuk iighulluku esghapagumakanga.
Talughhneghsimakanga.
Talughsan qemimeng meteghlluk taayughqumalghii yugem mengteghanun.
Kaalluni mengteghamun iteghluni aqumumalghii.
Yugtun ellngallu pimalghii, “Entapistemni gaaghutinga!
Neghnavregaam avelghaqinaamakanga iwemga wataqun.
Qenwat aghtughluni meteghlluk qeiliqumalghii.
Uzimun mengteghaq ivaghivikumakanga.
Sunanguq taana esghaghaa kangighani petugluni amiq uumwaaqaq.
Meteghllugem ketfaghluku itemsimakanga.
Saaghsaqminigu esghaamakanga neghnavregaghhaq unguvaaqeftuq.
Meteghlluk sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Unangwaaqsengalghii yugem kayutnga.”
Meteghllugem qesugraghluku almesiistun amiq iimgumakanga.
Neghnavregaq qesugraqani iimgusimakanga.
Nengakun petugluku aanluni aghulaqumalghii.
Yuuk unangluni uteghniimalghii.
Kaalluni unangkani egllum saaghwakun lliluku pimalghii, “Saaqsin pistemni?
Gaaghutinga!”
Avelghaqinaamakanga.
Alla pilaataghaa.
Aghtuumakanga.
Mataawisamigu amiq ketfaghluku saagsaqminigu iimguqani esghaamakanga qesugraghluni.
Taagken almesillaataamakanga.
Ellmineng apeghiighsaghluni lliighlaataamalghii.
Tefaay!
